\id JHN - Gwich'in NT -USA 2011 (DBL -2013) 
\h St. John 
\toc1 Saint John Ch'adąąntł'oo 
\toc2 John 
\toc3 Jn 
\mt1 John 
\mt2 Saint John Ch'adąąntł'oo 
\c 1  
\s1 Jii Gwandak Ginjik T'ee Jesus Oaazhii 
\p  
\v 1 Tr'ookit dąį' gwats'an, Ginjik ch'adąį' hee gwandaii, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa haa nilii ts'ą' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa nilii.  
\v 2 Tr'ookit dąį' gwats'an Ginjik, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa haa nilii.  
\v 3 Ginjik k'iighai' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa jidii datthak iłtsąįį, ch'ihłak gaa veentak tr'iłtsąįį kwaa.  
\v 4 Jidii gwandaii dhidlit kwaii datthak vagwandaii ts'an t'igwiizhik, ąįį vagwandaii t'ee juu nąįį datthak eenjit ch'ahdrii nilii.  
\v 5 Ąįį vagwandaii t'ee dinjii nąįį eenjit ch'ahdrii nilii, tǫǫ chan duuyeh yąąhkyaa. 
\p  
\v 6 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ąįį dinjii John oaazhii jii nankat gwats'ą' hił'e',  
\v 7 ąįį dinjii nąįį ts'ą' ąįį Aadrii eegwahaandak eenjit. Juu nąįį datthak jii gaageheendaii ts'ą' gwik'iinjigeheeghit eenjit Ch'aadrii eegavaagwaandak.  
\v 8 Adan ąįį Aadrii t'arahnyąą kwaa; Aadrii eegwahaandak eenjit gwizhrįh ginkhe' t'arahnyąą.  
\v 9 Ąįį Aadrii t'ee łyaa łi'didlii t'arahnyąą, dząą nankat gwats'ą' haazhii ts'ą' juu nąįį datthak ach'ahdrii. 
\p  
\v 10 Ąįį Ginjik vik'iighai' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa nan iłtsąįį, gaa dząą nankat dhidii dąį' dinjii nąįį giiyaandaii kwaa k'it t'iginchy'aa.  
\v 11 Danahkat gwats'ą' haazhii gaa zhat dinjii nąįį giitr'ii'ee.  
\v 12 Goolat nąįį zhrįh eechįį t'ii'in ts'ą' giik'iinjiighit; Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vigii giheelyaa eenjit t'aih goots'an iłtsąįį.  
\v 13 Jii dinjii nąįį łyaa giik'iinjiighit, ts'ą' izhit geh'an chan gooneegahoodlit, dagahan akwat digiti' ts'an nakwaa gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ts'an gooneegahoodlit ts'ą' Gooti' nilii. 
\p  
\v 14 Ginjik ąįį dinjii dhidlit ts'ą' diitee gwinch'į', vich'eegwahdrii gwarąąh'ya', ąįįt'ee ch'eet'igwiniindhan ąįįts'ą' łi'didlii haa vizhit deedąą'ąį' nilii. Adan zhrįh Gwiti', Vidinji' nilii geh'an ts'ą' jii ch'eegwahdrii shroodiinyąą vats'an dhidlit. 
\p  
\v 15 John chųų gwats'an ąhtsii yeeginkhe'. Jyaa yahnyąą, “Jii dinjii eegiihkhii t'ihnyąą, nijin jii jyaa nakhwaiinyą' dąį', ‘Shatąįį k'eeheedik gaa shandaa hil'ee shigweheelyaa gwats'ą' dąį' gwats'an gwandaii geh'an.’” 
\p  
\v 16 Vich'eet'igwiniidhan haa gweedhaa datthak diitee googwąąnchy'aa diits'ą' nizįį.  
\v 17 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa yeenii Moses k'iighai' diineenjit Law intł'eiin'ąįį gaa Jesus Christ ch'eet'igwiniindhan chan ts'ą' łi'didlii haa diitł'eiin'ąįį.  
\v 18 Dinjii ch'ihłak gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa dandee haa nah'in kwaa gaa Vidinji' Jesus Christ zhrįh yaa nilii ts'ą' yeediinaagwildak. 
\s1 John Chųų Gwats'an Ąhtsii Vagwandak. 
\p  
\v 19 Jews khaihkwaii nąįį, digigiinkhii chan ts'ą' Levite nąįį haa John ts'ą' googihił'e', jii giiyųąhkat eenjit “Juu inlii?” 
\p  
\v 20 Zhazhat John nagwąąh'įį kwaa ts'ą' gwinzii gavaagwildak, “Christ t'ihchy'aa kwaa.” 
\p  
\v 21 “Juu inlii gǫ', Elijah\f + \fr 1:21 \ft Deenaadąį' Elijah t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nilii, ts'ą' Christ ehkii k'eeheedik goo'aii.\f* inlii?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p “Nakwaa, ąįį t'ihchy'aa kwaa.” John nyąą. 
\p “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii inlii?” giiyahnyąą 
\p “Nakwaa,” gavahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 22 “Juu inlii diinaa gwandak, juu naroohaahkat eenjit diihił'e' nąįį gavaa gwarahaandak eenjit. Juu inlii?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 23 John jyaa gavahnyąą, “Jidii ihłii nakhwaa gwahaldak: 
\q1 ‘Shįį t'ee oo'at nangwinjir gwa'an ihshral ts'ą' jyaa diinyą' 
\q1 Diik'eegwaadhat tąįį gwinjik veenjit k'igwąą'ee nagoh'ąįį!’” 
\q1 (Jii t'ee Isaiah, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii yadaantł'oo) 
\p  
\v 24-25 Pharisee nąįį juu gihił'e' nąįį John goahkat, “Christ inlii kwaa akwat Elijah chan inlii kwaa, akwat Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii inlii kwaa. Gwiizhit jaghaii chųų gwats'an ąhtsii?” 
\p  
\v 26 John jyaa gavahnyąą “Chųų gwats'an ałtsii; gaa nakhwatee dinjii vaakhwandaii kwaa nadhat t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 27 Shatąįį k'eeheedik, gaa vakwaiitryaa dineehałchaa eenjit gaa hool'ee kwaa.” \fig Kwaiitryaa|src="lb00161b.tif" size="col" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 1.27" \fig* 
\p  
\v 28 Jii t'igwiizhik t'ee Bethany kwaiik'it gwizhit t'igwiizhik Jordan han gwinjik ndųhts'ąįį, nijin John chųų gwats'an ąhtsii izhit. 
\s1 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidivii Gii tsal 
\p  
\v 29 Gęhdaa drin John ąįį Jesus yats'ą' ahaa niił'in ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Jii t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidivii Gii tsal t'inchy'aa. Jii nankat gwatr'agwaanduu oo'an gwihilii t'inchy'aa!  
\v 30 Jii dinjii eegiihkhii t'ihnyąą, nijin jii nakhwaagwaldak dąį', ‘Dinjii shatąįį k'eeheedik gaa shandaa hil'ee, shigweheelyaa gwats'ą' dąį' gwats'an gwandaii geh'an.’  
\v 31 Shįį gaa juu t'inchy'aa vaashandaii kwaa, gaa Israel gwich'in nąįį yaaheendaii eenjit vats'an chųų dhałtsąįį.” 
\p  
\v 32 Jii t'ee John jyaa diinyą': “Dove chiitsal daagąįį zheekat gwats'an yakat needaanąįį gwik'it Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą yakat needaanąįį ts'ą' yaa nilii.  
\v 33 Tth'aii nihk'it vaashandaii kwaa, gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa chųų gwats'an hałtsyaa eenjit shihił'e' ąįį jyaa shaiinyą', ‘Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą dinjii kat needahąądhal; ąįįts'ą' ąįį dinjii t'ee Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą haa chųų gwats'an hahtsyaa.’  
\v 34 Jii gwał'ya' t'ihnyąą,” John gavahnyąą, “Jii dinjii łi'haa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidinji' t'inchy'aa.” 
\s1 Jesus Tr'ookit Vitsyaa Nąįį. 
\p  
\v 35 Gęhdaa drin chan hee zhat John, ditsyaa neekwaii haa zhat nigiilzhii,  
\v 36 Nijin Jesus gehgoo ahaa nah'in dąį', “Jii t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidivii Giitsal t'inchy'aa!” John goovahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 37 Ąįį vitsyaa neekwaii jyaa nyąą giiyiitth'ak ts'ą' Jesus haa gahaa'oo.  
\v 38 Jesus neediil'ee ts'ą' giitąįį adaa gwąąh'in ts'ą' gavaahkat, “Jidii keegǫh'in t'akhwa'in?” 
\p “Geech'ǫąąhtan, nijin gwinch'įį?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 39 “Aanaii, gahǫǫh'yaa,” gavahnyąą. Ąįįts'ą' t'ee giiyaahaa'oo ts'ą' nijin gwich'įį googwąąh'ya' ts'ą' giiyaaniihaa (khaa gwilii geh'an). 
\p  
\v 40 Andrew, John deiinyą' gwiitth'ak ąįįtł'ęę Jesus haa haazhii. (Simon Peter voondee nilii.)  
\v 41 Andrew łyaa khan doondee Simon kantii ts'ą' yagwąh'ąįį Googwahkhan jyaa yahnyąą, “Messiah vagwarąh'ąįį!” (Greek ginjik t'ee Christ t'agahnyąą.)  
\v 42 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Simon ąįį Jesus ts'ą' hiłchįį. 
\p Jesus yąąh'in ts'ą' jyaa yahnyąą, “Simon, nan John vidinji', noozhri' Cephas oohaazhyaa.” (Peter gwinyąą t'igwinyąą, “kii” chan ginyąą t'igwinyąą). 
\p  
\v 43 Gęhdaa drin Jesus Galilee nahkat gwats'ą' heekhaa nigwiin'ąįį. Philip agwąh'ąįį ts'ą' jyaa yahnyąą, “Shaa hinkhaii!”  
\v 44 Philip t'ee Bethsaida kwaiik'it gwats'an ahaa, nijin Andrew chan ts'ą' Peter haa gwigwich'įį.  
\v 45 Philip ąįį Nathaniel agwąh'ąįį ts'ą' jyaa yahnyąą, “Moses va-law dęhtły'aa kat yeeginkhe' akwat Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nąįį dęhtły'aa kat jyąhts'ą' gwadagaantł'oo. Jesus t'inchy'aa, Nazareth gwats'an Joseph ąįį vigii nilii.” 
\p  
\v 46 “Nazareth nijin ji' gweheezyaa li'?” Nathaniel nyąą 
\p “Aanaii ts'ą' gwąąh'in,” Philip yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 47 Nijin Jesus ąįį Nathaniel yats'ą' ahaa gwąąh'in dąį', jyaa yahnyąą, “Jii t'ee łyaa Israel gwich'in nilii, dinjii łi'didlii nilii!” 
\p  
\v 48 Nathaniel yuahkat, “Nats'ąą shaanandaii?” 
\p Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Philip nagwahah'aa gwats'ą' dąį' ts'iivii vakat Figs nahshii t'eh dhindii naał'ya'!” 
\p  
\v 49 “Geech'ǫąąhtan, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidinji' t'iinchy'aa łee Israel gwi-King t'iinchy'aa łee!” Nathaniel yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 50 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Ts'iivii vakat Figs nahshii t'eh dhindii naał'ya' naiinyą' geh'an gwizhrįh gwik'iinjinghit? Jii kwaii andaa ts'ą' gwihil'ee t'igwii'in gwahąąh'yaa t'oonchy'aa!”  
\v 51 Ąįįts'ą' jyaa gavahnyąą, “Jii t'ee łi'didlii haa nakhwaa gwahaldak: zheekat nihky'aa t'igweheenjyaa gahǫǫh'yaa ts'ą' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa zheekat gwich'in nąįį k'iidak, k'iidąą haa Gwidinji' ts'ą' nigiheedaa!” 
\c 2  
\s1 Cana gwizhit Nihłeegwarahchįį 
\p  
\v 1 Galilee nahkat gwizhit Cana kwaiik'it goo'aii, zhat Jesus vahan dhidii, izhit drin tik gwiindhat ąįįtł'ęę zhat nihłeegwirihiłchįį.  
\v 2 Ąįįts'ą' Jesus chan ts'ą' ditsyaa nąįį haa geedan chan zhat nihłeegwirihiłchįį aanaii googahnyąą ts'ą' gwats'ą' gahaajil.  
\v 3 Nijin jak chų' datthak geenį' dąį', Jesus vahan t'iiyahnyąą, “Jak chų' gavaanaanįį.” 
\p  
\v 4 “Ni'ęę, jyaa dini'in shahaiinjyaa kwaa goo'aii t'oonchy'aa. Zhat tth'aii shaa nigwiighit kwaa.” Jesus yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 5 Jesus vahan ąįį juu zhat yeenjit tr'agwah'in nąįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Deenakhwahnyąą gwik'it t'akhwa'in.” 
\p  
\v 6 Izhit geeghaih chųų eenjit kii tyah choh nihk'iitik dhidlii, (ch'ihłak gaa 20 akwat 30 gallon ootą'). Jews nąįį shragoodiinyąą neegeheelyaa eenjit dik'eech'agahtryaa geenjit. \fig Kii tyah choh.|src="lb00135b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 2.6" \fig* 
\p  
\v 7 Jesus ąįį juu zhat gwitr'it t'agwah'in nąįį t'ahnyąą, “Jii tyah kwaii chųų vizhit deedoohjyaa.” Chųų vizhit deedąą'ąį' giiyiłtsąįį. 
\p  
\v 8 Ąįįtł'ęę jyaa gavahnyąą, “Et'ee valat khanohjyaa ts'ą' zhit juu gach'ah'aa ąįį vats'ą' hohkaii.” 
\p Giits'ą' yahaakaii,  
\v 9 ts'ą' yaalaii, ąįį chųų t'ee jak chų' dhidlit. Ąįį jak chų' nijin gwats'an t'inchy'aa yaandaii kwaa gaa zhit juu yeetr'agwah'in nąįį gaagiindaii.  
\v 10 Ąįį juu veegwarąhchįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Lęįį nąįį jak chų' ch'andaa nizįį tr'ookit gagahnįį ąįį datthak giinjik ąįįtł'ęę jak chų' daatł'oo kwaa gagahnįį. Gaa nan ąįį ndaagwąą'ąį' dohju' hee jak chų' nizįį juk gąhnįį.” \fig Kii tyah choh kwaii.|src="lb00135b.tif" size="span" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="JHN 2.10" \fig* 
\p  
\v 11 Jesus jii tr'ookit gwitr'it gwihil'ee t'iizhik Cana kwaiik'it, Galilee nahkat gwizhit. Izhit t'ee dich'eegwahdrii gwizhrįh nigwiin'ąįį, ts'ą' vitsyaa nąįį giik'iinjiighit. 
\s1 Jesus, Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh gwats'ą' Haazhii. 
\r Matthew 21.12-13; Mark 11.15-17; Luke 19.45-46 
\p  
\v 12 Jii jyaa digwiizhik ąįįtł'ęę Jesus, dahan ditsyaa dachaa nąįį haa Capernaum kwaiik'it gwats'ą' gahaajil ts'ą' zhat drin nitsya' gaak'į'.  
\v 13 It'ee khaiinjii Jews nąįį eenjit Passover nigwiindhat ąįįts'ą' Jesus Jerusalem gwats'ą' haazhii.  
\v 14 Kharigidiinjii zheh gwachoh gookwantee nihdeegweedii gwizhit dinjii nąįį aak'ii, divii chan ts'ą' chiitsal kwaii t'įį laraa gihilii gwąąh'in, ąįįts'ą' zhit juu ch'adanh gwalaraa ookwat nąįį chan vakaii'aa, ts'ą' dilk'ii nah'in. \fig Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh gwizhit cheegohaanzhit.|src="cn01787b.tif" size="span" copy="©1978 David C. Cook Publishing Company" ref="JHN 2.14" \fig* 
\v 15 Ąįįts'ą' zhat gwa'an tły'ah haa viitrii iłtsąįį haa Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh gwizhit gwats'an divii, aak'ii haa cheehaanzhit; ąįį ch'adanh gwalaraa ookwat nąįį vakaii'aa ts'ą' giilk'ii izhit vakaii'aa khatąąnahjil ts'ą' goolaraa datthak neiinjil.  
\v 16 Ąįį juu dziitsal dove laraa t'įį hilii nąįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Juk zhat cheegavahohłii! Jii Shiti' vizheh ch'ookwat zheh goo'įį kwaa!”  
\v 17 Vitsyaa nąįį Dęhtły'aa Choh kat jii, jyaa digwinyąą gineegaandaii, “Nizheh gwachoh łyaa tr'ihkhit geenjit yinjiihooł'ee ts'ą' ąįį geenjit shrii tr'igwirehee'aa!” gwinyąą. 
\p  
\v 18 Izhit zhat Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį jii giiyųąhkat, “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vats'an ni'in ji', diinandah geegwaroolii kwaa t'ini'in lee.” 
\p  
\v 19 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Jii kharigidiinjii zheh an goodlit ji' drin tik ts'ą' ndak nineegwahałtsyaa.” 
\p  
\v 20 “Drin tik ąįįtł'ęę ndak nineegwahahtsyaa? Jii Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh łyaa 46 years gwahaadhat ąįįtł'ęę dohju' hee gęhdaa tr'igiinjik t'oonchy'aa?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 21 Gaa Jesus ąįį zhit kharigidiinjii zheh geeginkhii dąį' adan ideeginkhii t'inyąą.  
\v 22 Nijin niindhat ąįįtł'ęę vineegwiindaii dąį' vitsyaa nąįį jii deenyąą chy'aa giinaandaii. Jesus deiinyą' akwat Dęhtły'aa Choh kat deegwinyąą datthak gwik'iinjigiighit gaadlit. 
\p  
\v 23 Passover ch'ara'aa gwizhit (Jesus Jerusalem dhidii) gweedhaa dąį', geegwaroolii kwaa gwinlęįį t'iizhik giiyąąh'ya' ts'ą' giik'iinjiighit.  
\v 24 Gaa Jesus gootr'oahnyąą, dinjii datthak goovaandaii geh'an.  
\v 25 Dinjii eevaaragwaandak gwat'aahchy'aa kwaa ch'adąį' hee goodrii zhit t'oonchy'aa gavaandaii. 
\c 3  
\s1 Jesus, Nicodemus Haa 
\p  
\v 1 Izhit dąį' Jews khaihkwaii tee gwa'an dinjii Nicodemus oaazhii dhidii, Pharisees chan nilii. \fig Jesus, Nicodemus haa|src="cn01670b.tif" size="span" copy="©1978 David C. Cook Publishing Company" ref="JHN 3.1" \fig* 
\v 2 Ch'ihłan khaa Jesus eenihkhee ts'ą' yuahkat, “Geech'ǫąąhtan, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa eenjit geech'ǫąąhtan eenjit nihił'e' naagwiindaii. Ch'ihłak gaa duuyeh Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vehdan geegwaroolii kwaa t'ii'in vaagwiindaii.” 
\p  
\v 3 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Łi'didlii haa naagwahaaldak, dinjii chan vineegahoodlit ji' gwizhrįh K'eegwaadhat Veegwinii'ee gwahąąh'yaa t'oonchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 4 Nicodemus jyaa yahnyąą, “Dinjii vaghaii lęįį gwiizhit nats'ąą vineegweheelyaa t'iinyąą? Duuyeh dahan zhit nidii ts'ą' chan vineegwiilii t'oonchy'aa!” 
\p  
\v 5 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Łi'didlii haa naagwahaaldak, dinjii chųų akwat Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą haa vagoodlit ji' gwizhrįh K'eegwaadhat Veegwinii'ee nihdeeheehaa.  
\v 6 Dinjii ąįį dinjii ts'an vigwilik, gaa dinjii Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą chan vigwilik, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ts'an nilii.  
\v 7 ‘Chan nineegweheelyaa,’ nakhwaihnyąą ąįį łyaa t'igwinyąą eenjit gwik'iinjuhkhit.  
\v 8 Ahtr'aii dąį' nijuk ohtr'aii niindhan datthak gwik'it ahtr'aii dohtth'ak gaa nijin gwats'an akwat nijin gwats'ą' t'inyąą vaanandaii kwaa. Ąįį juu Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą haa vigwilik gwik'it t'inchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 9 “Jii nats'ąą t'agwaiinyąą,” Nicodemus yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 10 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Israel gwizhit łyaa geech'ǫąąhtan hil'ee inlii gwiizhit jii geenjit gaanandaii kwaa?  
\v 11 Łi'didlii haa naagwahaaldak, jidii gaagwiindaii gwizhrįh geegirinkhii, jidii gwarąąh'ya' gwizhrįh chan geegirinkhii googaa nakhwatee ch'ihłak gaa shik'iinjiighit kwaa.  
\v 12 Dząą nijin nankat t'igwii'in geenaagwaldak dąį' shik'iinjiinghit kwaa; akwat zheekat geenaagwaldak ji' izhit chan shik'iinjihįįnghit kwaa.  
\v 13 Ąįįts'ą' ch'ihłak gaa zheekat gwats'ą' haazhii ts'ą' oodaa nidii kwaa, Gwidinji' zhrįh jyaa diizhik.” 
\p  
\v 14 “Deenaadąį' Moses nangwinjir gwa'an gwandah gyųų choh\f + \fr 3:14 \ft Deenaadąį' Israel gwich'in nąįį oo'ok nan gwinjir gwa'an neegihiidal dąį' juu K'eegwahthat kwaa nąįį gyųų choh gii'al. Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ąįį Moses ch'iitsii datłok (bronze) haa gyųų choh ąhtsii ts'ą' dachan kat deedhin'ąįį ahnyąą. Juu ąįį gyųų nah'in ji' t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa yits'ą' tr'iheedal.\f* dachan kat diłchaa, izhit gwik'it Gwidinji' cross kat ndak tr'ihiłchįį.  
\v 15 Juu gik'iinjiighit nąįį khit gwigweheendaii eenjit.  
\v 16 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa łyaa dinjii datthak eet'iindhan geenjit it'ee zhrįh Didinji' gwantł'ąhchįį, ąįįts'ą' juu yik'injiighit nąįį nigiheedhaa kwaa ts'ą' khit gwigweheendaii eenjit.  
\v 17 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Didinji' nankat dinjii an hahtsyaa eenjit gwats'ą' hił'e' kwaa gaa dinjii neehahshii eenjit. 
\p  
\v 18 “Juu Gwidinji' k'injiighit duuyeh an ilii; gaa juu gwik'iinjiighit kwaa ąįįt'ee ch'adąį' an dhidlit, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa et'ee zhrįh Vidinji' k'injiighit kwaa geh'an.  
\v 19 Jii t'ee jyąhts'ą' dinjii an heelyaa t'agwarahnyąą: Jii nankat datthak k'ąą adrii gwilii, gaa dinjii nąįį tǫǫ ąįį geet'igiindhan, ąįį googwitr'it gwiizųų geh'an.  
\v 20 Ąįį juu vigwitr'it gwiizųų nąįį ch'aadrii itr'igii'ee ts'ą' duuyeh ch'aadrii zhit ga'oo, vigwitr'it gwiizųų ąįį gwizhrįh nagwa'aii gitr'ii'ee geh'an.  
\v 21 Gaa zhit juu vigwitr'it gwinzii nąįį shoo haa ch'aadrii zhit ga'oo, dee'in ąįį Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa k'iighai' t'ii'in gwigweheechy'aa eenjit.” 
\s1 Jesus, John Chųų Gwats'an Ąhtsii Haa 
\p  
\v 22 Jii ąįįtł'ęę, Jesus ditsyaa nąįį haa Judea nahkat gwats'ą' gahaajil. Zhat ch'ihłee gwizhrįh gavaa iindi' ts'ą' lęįį nąįį chųų ts'an dhidlit.  
\v 23 Aenon gwizhit John chųų gwats'an ąhtsii, Aenon t'ee Salim geeghaih goo'aii ts'ą' zhat gwizhrįh chųų gwanlii. Lęįį nąįį chųų goots'an tr'ahahtsyaa eenjit yeenineedal.  
\v 24 Zhat dąį' John tth'aii zheegwaazhrąįį nigiiyąąhchįį kwaa. 
\p  
\v 25 Jews nąįį tee gwats'an dinjii ch'ihłak ąįį John vitsyaa nąįį haa gwantł'oo shroogogoonyąą eenjit giiyaa nihzheedagąąn'ee.  
\v 26 John ts'ą' nigiinjil ts'ą' jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Geech'ǫąąhtan, dinjii Jordan han gwinjik ndųhts'ąįį, naa indi' ts'ą' veeginkhe', vanandaii? Juk chųų gwats'an ąhtsii ts'ą' juu nąįį datthak yats'ą' hijyaa t'arahnyąą!” 
\p  
\v 27 John jyaa gavahnyąą, “Zheekat gwats'an jidii gwitr'it diinantł'eegwariin'ąįį zhrįh eenjit gwitr'it gwarahąąh'yaa goo'aii.  
\v 28 Nakhwandah jii jyaa diinyą' ganoondaii, ‘Christ t'ihchy'aa kwaa gaa shįį tr'ookit vits'ii shirihił'e'.’  
\v 29 Zhit juu veegwarąhchįį t'ee da'at ts'anyahaa'yaa. Ąįį juu veegwarąhchįį vijyaa veeghaii nadhat ts'ą' yinkeech'oołk'įį, yideezhuh diitth'ak dąį' shoh ilik. Jyąhts'ą' t'ee shįį chan shoo'ihłik, gwitr'it shintł'eegwiriin'ąįį gęhdaa tr'iinjik geh'an.  
\v 30 Adan nitsii heelyaa, shįį ąįį jyaa deegwahtł'oo sheegwehee'aa kwaa.” 
\p  
\v 31 “Zheekat gwats'an ahaa ts'ą' juu nąįį datthak andaa hil'ee. Juu nankat gwats'an ahaa chan nankat gwats'an nilii ts'ą' nankat gwiky'aa gwizhrįh ginkhii. Juu zheekat gwats'an ahaa t'ee juu nąįį datthak ęhdak dhidii.  
\v 32 Jidii gwaak'įį akwat gwąąh'ya' haa eegwaandak. Ch'ihłak gaa yiginjik k'injiighit kwaa.  
\v 33 Dinjii yiginjik k'eegwahthat t'ee łi'didlii nilii giiky'aandak.  
\v 34 Juu hił'e' t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa viginjik eegwaandak t'oonchy'aa, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ąįį deegwahtł'oo Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą hahtsyaa gwik'it yats'an iłtsąįį geh'an.  
\v 35 Gwiti' łyaa Didinji' eet'iindhan ts'ą' jidii datthak yantł'eegwiin'ąįį.  
\v 36 Juu Gwidinji' k'injiighit t'ee khit gweheendaii. Juu Gwidinji' viginjik k'it t'ii'in kwaa t'ee duuyeh khit gwandaii, gaa khit geenjit Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa yagwahąąhshii.” \fig Jesus, ts'ą' Samaria gwats'an tr'injaa haa.|src="lb00302b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 3.36" \fig* 
\c 4  
\s1 Jesus, Ts'ą' Samaria Gwats'an Tr'injaa Haa 
\p  
\v 1 Zhat dąį' Jesus ąįį John andaa ts'ą' vitsyaa nąįį gwilii ts'ą' datthak chųų goots'an ąhtsii gwinyąą ąįį Pharisee nąįį gwigwiitth'ak.  
\v 2 Jesus ąįį chųų gwats'an ąhtsii kwaa gaa vitsyaa nąįį t'ii'in ąįį t'agoogwahnyąą.  
\v 3 Jesus nijin jyaa digwinyąą gwiitth'ak dąį', Judea nahkat gihłeehoozhii ts'ą' Galilee nahkat gwits'eehoozhii,  
\v 4 Samaria nahkat t'ee, Galilee gwats'ą' hee goo'aii ts'ą' zhat gehgoo haazhii. 
\p  
\v 5 Jesus Samaria nahkat gwizhit kwaiik'it Sychar goozhii k'idik. Deenaadąį' izhit geeghaih t'ee Jacob didinji' Joseph nan intł'eiin'ąįį goo'aii.  
\v 6 Izhit t'ee Jacob vichųų deek'it goo'aii ąįįts'ą' Jesus niighyuk niinzhii ts'ą' cheendak ts'ą' zhat chųų tr'oonjii deek'it eeghaii naadii. Drin tł'an gweedhaa gwiizhit. 
\p  
\v 7 Samaria gwats'an tr'injaa zhat chųų hoondal eenjit k'idik ts'ą' Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Chųų shintł'eiinkaii.”  
\v 8 (Vitsyaa nąįį kwaiik'it shih gooheekwat eenjit nigijyaa gwiizhit.) 
\p  
\v 9 Ąįį tr'injaa jyaa yahnyąą, “Jews nąįį tee gwats'an iinlii, shįį ąįį Samaria gwats'an ihłii, jaghaii chųų shaiinyąą t'iinyąą?” (Jews nąįį duuyeh gaa Samaria gwich'in nąįį k'it zhit ch'aga'aa). 
\p  
\v 10 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa jidii neenjit di'įį gaanandaii akwat juu ihłii shaanandaii ji', oohaahkat ts'ą' chųų gwandaii nintł'eeheekaa.” 
\p  
\v 11 Ąįį tr'injaa jyaa yahnyąą, “Tyah ni'įį kwaa, nanzhit k'iizhak chųų ts'ą' niighit. Nijin chųų gwandaii oohiindal t'iinyąą?  
\v 12 Yeenii diilak Jacob jii chųų deek'it diinantł'eegwiin'ąįį; adan, didinji', dinin nąįį haa datthak gwats'an chųų geenį'. Jacob vandaa neegoo'aii yiindhan lee t'iinyąą?” 
\p  
\v 13 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Juu dząą chųų eenį' t'ee chan hee chųų haał'yaa.  
\v 14 Gaa juu chųų vintł'eiinkaii duuyeh chan chųų dahłįį neelii. Ąįį chųų vintł'eehihkaa ąįį vizhit han gwinjik chųų ninlaii k'it t'inchy'aa ts'ą' khit yaa gweheendaii.” 
\p  
\v 15 Ąįį tr'injaa jyaa nyąą, “Jii chųų t'avaiinyąą shintł'eiinkaii! Ąįį ji' chan chųų haał'yaa kwaa, akwat chan dząą chųų kaneehihdyaa kwaa.” 
\p  
\v 16 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Oo'an neehindii ts'ą' nakąį', oo'ee nąąhchįį.” 
\p  
\v 17 Ąįį tr'injaa jyaa yahnyąą, “Shakąį' kwaa t'oonchy'aa.” 
\p Jesus jyaa nyąą, “Nakąį' kwaa diinyąą dąį' łyaa t'iinyąą łee.  
\v 18 Nakąį' ch'ihłoanli' gwiinli', juk ąįį dinjii vaagwinch'įį nakąį' t'inchy'aa kwaa. Łi'didlii haa shaagwadhandak.” 
\p  
\v 19 Ąįį tr'injaa jyaa yahnyąą, “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii inlii łee.  
\v 20 Yeenii diilak nąįį jii ddhah kat Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa deegihiił'e' gaa nakhwan Jews ąįį Jerusalem gwizhit Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa deerahǫh'e' diinoohnyąą.” 
\p  
\v 21 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Jii ddhah kat akwat Jerusalem gwizhit dinjii nąįį Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa deegahah'aa kwaa nigweheedhaa ąįį łyaa t'igwinyąą.  
\v 22 Samaria gwich'in ǫhłįį ts'ą' juu vats'ą' khadagohjii gaakhwandaii kwaa. Diikhwan Jews gwich'in tr'iinlii ts'ą' juu vats'ą' khadigariinjii gaagwiindaii, Israel gwich'in nąįį k'iighai' neehohshii geh'an.  
\v 23 Gaa it'ee zhat nigwiighit, juk t'ee łyaa gwik'iinjiighit nąįį digiyinji' zhit łi'didlii haa Gwiti' ts'ą' khadigigiinjii. Ąįį gik'iinjiighit k'it t'inchy'aa t'ee Gwiti' keehi'ik t'inchy'aa.  
\v 24 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa t'ee Ch'anky'aa nilii, ts'ą' juu yats'ą' khadigiinjii t'ee digiyinji' zhit łi'didlii haa giits'ą' khadigiheejyaa goo'aii.” 
\p  
\v 25 Ąįį tr'injaa jyaa yahnyąą, “Messiah ąįį Christ oozhii ahaa ts'ą' gaashandaii nijin k'idik ji' jidii datthak eediinaagwahaandak vaashandaii.” 
\p  
\v 26 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Shįį nats'ą' ginkhii t'ee adan t'ihchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 27 Izhit gwiizhit Jesus vitsyaa nąįį oo'ee neegiijil; tr'injaa ts'ą' ginkhii giiky'aanjik dąį' deegiheenjyaa gaa gaagiindaii kwaa. Gootee ch'ihłak gaa ąįį tr'injaa jyaa ahnyąą kwaa, “Jidii yiindhan?” akwat Jesus chan jii agaahkat kwaa, “Jaghaii jii tr'injaa vats'ą' ginkhii?” 
\p  
\v 28 Ąįįtł'ęę ąįį tr'injaa zhat dityaa akhoonyąą ts'ą' kwaiik'it gwits'eehoozhii ts'ą' zhat nąįį jyaa ahnyąą,  
\v 29 Aanaii ts'ą' jii dinjii yeenii deeshi'yaa datthak geeneeshaagwaandak nǫh'in. Jii dinjii lee Christ t'inchy'aa?  
\v 30 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee zhat datthak ąįį kwaiik'it chagahaajil ts'ą' Jesus ts'ą' gahaajil. 
\p  
\v 31 Izhit gwiizhit vitsyaa nąįį yaandeegwii'ąįį ts'ą' jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Geech'ǫąąhtan, gwintsal ch'in'aa!” 
\p  
\v 32 Gaa jyaa gavahnyąą, “Shih shi'įį ąįį vaakhwandaii kwaa.” 
\p  
\v 33 Ąįįts'ą' vitsyaa nąįį jyaa nihłagaanyąą, “Juu shih yats'ą' hiłtsit t'inyąą li'?” 
\p  
\v 34 Jesus gavahnyąą, “Ąįį juu shihił'e' vik'it t'ooshi'ya' shoonyąą ąįį vigwitr'it t'agwahał'ya' gwizhrįh goo'aii ąįįt'ee shishii k'it t'inchy'aa.  
\v 35 Jii jyaa dohnyąą chy'aa ganoondaii, ‘Shree drin dǫǫ ts'ą' gwanzhįh khareheelyaa.’ Nakhwaagwahaldak, gwanzhįh deek'it gwinzii gooh'in; gwanzhįh khareheelyaa eenjit et'ee nizįį! \fig Gwanzhįh khaihłan ninlii.|src="hk00100b.tif" size="col" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society " ref="JHN 4.35" \fig* 
\v 36 Ąįį juu gwanzhįh dehk'it gwitr'it t'agwah'in t'ee vagwarookwat, ąįįts'ą' zhit gwanzhįh khaihłan nilii t'ee khit gwarandaii eenjit khaihłan niyilii t'ii'in. Ąįįts'ą' zhit juu gwiiłshįį ts'ą' juu khaihłan niyilii haa nihłaa shoo geelyaa eenjit.  
\v 37 Jii t'ee łyaa t'igwinyąą, ‘Dinjii ch'ihłak gwąąhshii, dinjii ch'ihłak gwanzhįh khaihłan nilii.’  
\v 38 Gwanzhįh deek'it gwehkįį tr'agoh'in kwaa izhit gwanzhįh khaihłan nohohłyaa eenjit gwats'ą' nakhwahooł'e'. Ch'izhii nąįį zhat tr'agwah'ya' gaa nakhwan ąįį gwanzhįh nakhwats'an dhidlit.” 
\s1 Samaria Lęįį Nąįį Jesus K'iinjigiighit 
\p  
\v 39 Izhit kwaiik'it gwizhit, Samaria gwich'in lęįį nąįį Jesus k'iinjigiighit, ąįį tr'injaa jii jyaa nyąą geh'an, “Yeenii deeshi'ya' datthak geeneeshaagwaandak.”  
\v 40 Ąįįts'ą' nijin Samaria gwich'in nąįį giits'ą' haajil dąį' diinaa dhiindii giiyahnyąą, ąįįts'ą' t'ee Jesus zhat drin neekwaii gavaa iindi'. 
\p  
\v 41 Deegavaiinyą' eenjit lęįį nąįį giik'iinjiighit dhidlit  
\v 42 ts'ą' ąįį tr'injaa jyaa agahnyąą, “Juk et'ee vik'injiriindhat, deediinaiinyą' eenjit kwaa gaa diikhwan chan diits'ą' ginkhe', ts'ą' jii nankat datthak dinjii neehahshii nilii et'ee vaagwiindaii.” 
\s1 Cana Kwaiik'it Gwats'ą' K'eegwaadhat Vidinji', Jesus Shrinilik 
\p  
\v 43 Drin neekwaii zhat naakhaa ąįįtł'ęę Jesus neehoozhii ts'ą' Galilee gwats'ą' haazhii.  
\v 44 Jii t'ee Jesus gwehkįį jyaa diinyą'. “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nąįį daganahkat gwa'an gooveenjit yinjigihił'ee kwaa.”  
\v 45 Nijin Galilee k'idik dąį', giiyeenjit shoo dhidlit, Jerusalem gwizhit Passover gwiinli' dąį' ch'aga'aa gwiizhit deezhik datthak giiyąąh'ya' geh'an. 
\p  
\v 46 Ąįįts'ą' Jesus Galilee nahkat gwizhit Cana kwaiik'it gwits'eehoozhii, izhit t'ee chųų ąįį jak chų' iłtsąįį. Izhit gwats'ą' k'eegwaadhat vidinji' Capernaum kwaiik'it gwizhit iłts'ik.  
\v 47 Nijin ąįį dinjii Jesus Judea nahkat gwats'an Galilee gwats'ą' haazhii gwinyąą gwiitth'ak dąį', yats'ą' haazhii ts'ą' Capernaum gwats'ą' shaa hinkhaii, shidinji' veenjit gwinzii neegwąhtsii yahnyąą, ąįį vidinji' t'ee niheedhaa nigwiindhat. 
\p  
\v 48 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa nakhwandah t'igwiizhik kwaa ji', nakhwatee ch'ihłak gaa duuyeh gwik'iinjiighit ilii!” 
\p  
\v 49 Ąįį nahkat gwats'ą' k'eegwaadhat jyaa yahnyąą, “Shigii niheedhaa gwehkįį shaa hinkhaii.” 
\p  
\v 50 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Oo'an neehindii, nidinji' gweheendaii t'inchy'aa!” Ąįį dinjii Jesus viginjik k'iinjindhat ts'ą' oo'an neehoozhii.  
\v 51 Dizheh gwats'ą' needyaa gwiizhit zhit juu yeetr'agwah'in nąįį gwandak haa giidąąjil, “Nichyaatsal gweheendaii t'oonchy'aa!” 
\p  
\v 52 Nijin nigwiindhat dąį' vidinji' veenjit gwinzii neegahoodlit eenjit gavoahkat, ts'ą' jyaa giiyahnyąą, “K'ehdąį' drintł'an ęhdaa tr'igwiindhat dąį' ts'ik niindhaa di'įį kwaa dhidlit.”  
\v 53 Izhit nigwiindhat dąį' Jesus jii jyaa yahnyąą chy'aa ganaanjik, “Nidinji' gweheendaii t'inchy'aa.” Ąįį dinjii dizhehk'ąą haa datthak gwik'iinjigiighit gaadlit. 
\p  
\v 54 Jesus Judea gwats'an Galilee gwats'ą' haazhii dąį' jii gwitr'it gwihil'ee t'iizhik t'ee neekwat gwizhrįh t'iizhik t'avarahnyąą. 
\c 5  
\s1 Dinjii Chųų Teełtin Eeghaii Shranaazhik 
\p  
\v 1 Jii ąįįtł'ęę Jerusalem gwizhit Israel nąįį ch'ara'aa googwahtsii izhit Jesus gwats'ą' haazhii.  
\v 2 Izhit divii deek'it goo'aii geeghaih chųų dhakaii goo'aii, ąįį eelin zheh gwatsal ch'ihłoanli' goodlii; Hebrew ginjik zhit Bethzatha goozhii.  
\v 3 Ąįį zheh gwadąįį gwizhit iłts'ik lęįį nąįį k'igilt'aii, vandee kwaa, neehidik kwaa akwat vatthąį' iłchįį nąįį. (Chųų hee tł'ak eenjit nagogwal'in;  
\v 4 neegwiidhak hee K'eegwaadhat vizheekat gwich'in chųų zhit neediidhak ts'ą' chųų atł'ak gwahtsii. Juu tr'ookit iłts'ik chųų atł'ak zhit gwizhyahkhat t'ee veenjit gwinzii neegwiilik.).  
\v 5 Izhit dinjii ch'ihłak dhidii, 38 years łąą iłts'ik.  
\v 6 Jesus zhat k'ilt'aii niyiił'in ts'ą' niighyuk iłts'ik yaandaii; ts'ą' jyaa yahnyąą, “Sheenjit gwinzii neegooli' niindhan?” 
\p  
\v 7 Ąįį dinjii jyaa nyąą, “Juu chųų zhit shahahchyaa gaashandaii kwaa; chųų atł'ak dąį' gwizhit hihshyaa gwik'eegwihdaii gwiizhit sharahtee dinjii gwizhyahkhat geh'an.” \fig Dinjii iłts'ik.|src="cn01686b.tif" size="span" copy="©1978 David C. Cook Publishing Company" ref="JHN 5.7" \fig* 
\p  
\v 8 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Ndak niindhat, nichyah oiinjii ts'ą' inkhaa.”  
\v 9 Izhit zhat ąįį dinjii veenjit gwinzii neekhwadlit gwagwahkhan dichyah oonjik ts'ą' ahaa (tr'iinzhii). \fig Dak ninzhii ts'a' dichyah oonjik.|src="cn01689b.tif" size="col" copy="©1978 David C. Cook Publishing Company" ref="JHN 5.9" \fig* 
\p Izhit Neegwaazhii Drin goo'aii,  
\v 10 ts'ą' Israel kįh dilk'ii nąįį ąįį dinjii shranaazhik jyaa agahnyąą, “Juk Neegwaazhii Drin t'oonchy'aa, dii-law zhit nichyah k'eehin'ak kwaa goo'aii gwinyąą.” 
\p  
\v 11 Jyaa gavahnyąą, “Ąįį dinjii sheenjit gwinzii neegwiłtsąįį jyaa shaiinyą', ‘Nichyah oiinjii ts'ą' inkhaa.’” 
\p  
\v 12 Jii giiyųąhkat, “Jii dinjii nichyah oiinjii ts'ą' inkhaa nahnyąą ąįį juu t'inchy'aa?” 
\p  
\v 13 Gaa ąįį dinjii shranaazhik ąįį juu t'inchy'aa yaandaii kwaa, tr'ihkhit dinjii gwanlii tee gwa'an gwiteiinzhii geh'an. 
\p  
\v 14 Ąįįtł'ęę gwandaa Jesus ąįį Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh gookwantee gwizhit yats'ą' tr'ineezhii ts'ą' jyaa yahnyąą, “Et'ee neenjit gwinzii akwat natr'agwaanduu akhagoiinyąą, ąįį akwaa ji' gwandaa nidivee gwiizųų gweheelyaa.” 
\p  
\v 15 Ąįį dinjii ąįį Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį ts'ą' haazhii ts'ą' Jesus oozhii ąįį yats'ą' tr'iinjik gavaa gwaandak. 
\s1 Gwidinji' Vik'iighai' Gwarandaii Tr'ihee'yaa 
\p  
\v 16 Izhit gwats'an t'ee Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį Jesus tr'ookhwaa giindhan, Neegwaazhii Drin dinjii shrineiinlik geh'an.  
\v 17 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Shiti' khit gwitr'it t'agwah'in, ąįįts'ą' shįį chan gwitr'it t'agwał'in gwat'aałchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 18 Jii jyaa diinyą' gwats'an t'ee łyaa geenjit tr'ookhwaa giiyuunyąą. Neegwaazhii Drin gwa-law łeełnaii gwizhrįh geenjit nakwaa gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Shiti' nyąą ts'ą' jyąhts'ą' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vagwahtsii veegoo'aii k'it t'inchy'aa geh'an. 
\p  
\v 19 Ąįįts'ą' Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą: “Łi'didlii haa nakhwaa gwahaldak, Gwidinji' duuyeh adakhai' k'eegwiichy'aa t'ii'in, Viti' dee'in gwąąh'in izhit gwizhrįh gwik'it t'ii'in. Gwiti' dee'in, Gwidinji' chan gwik'it t'ii'in t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 20 Gwiti', Didinji' eet'iindhan ts'ą' dee'in datthak yats'ą' googwaahch'in. Jii dinjii shrineiinlik ąįį gwandaa yats'ą' googwahahchy'aa t'avarahnyąą ts'ą' geegwaroolii kwaa lęįį nakhwandaa t'ihee'yaa.  
\v 21 Gwiti', dinjii niindhat nąįį ineegwahdaii. Izhit gwik'it Gwidinji' chan juu niindhan nąįį gwandaii intł'ineehee'aa t'avarahnyąą.  
\v 22 Gwiti' adan zhrįh dinjii eenjit k'eegwaadhat kwaa t'inchy'aa. Gaa Didinji' chan dinjii datthak eenjit k'eegwaadhat eenjit gwiłtsąįį,  
\v 23 Gwiti' deegwiłtł'oo tr'ihił'ee gwik'it Gwidinji' chan tr'ahah'aa eenjit. Juu Gwidinji' hił'ee kwaa t'ee Gwiti' yihił'e' ąįį chan hił'ee kwaa t'agwarahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 24 “Jii t'ee łi'didlii nakhwaa gwahaldak: Juu shiginjik diitth'ak ts'ą' juu shihił'e' k'injiighit ąįįt'ee gwandaii ndaanąą'ąį' kwaa hee'yaa. Ch'adąį' hee niindhat gwats'an neegwiindaii geh'an Ch'aroahkat Drin zhit ji' duuyeh an ilii.  
\v 25 Jii t'ee łi'didlii nakhwaa gwahaldak: khaiinjii zhat nigwiindhat, ch'adąį' hee zhat nigwiindhat, zhit juu niindhat nąįį Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidinji' giheetth'ak ts'ą' juu yiitth'ak gweheendaii.  
\v 26 Gwiti' dinjii ineegwahdaii eenjit t'aih dii'įį, izhit gwik'it Vidinji' chan dinjii ineegwahahdaii eenjit t'aih intł'eiin'ąįį.  
\v 27 Ąįįts'ą' Vidinji' ąįį dinjii ts'ą' k'eegwahaadhat eenjit t'aih yintł'eiin'ąįį, Gwidinji' nilii geh'an.  
\v 28 Jii nakhwarahtee t'agǫǫnjyaa shrǫ'; zhat nigwiighit juu tth'ank'it gwizhit niindhat nąįį datthak nijin giiyeheetth'ak.  
\v 29 Nijin giiyiitth'ak ji' t'ee tth'ank'it khagiheedaa zhit juu gwinzii t'ee'ya' khaneegiheedaa ts'ą' neegwigweheendaii, zhit juu vigwitr'it gwiizųų nąįį chan, khaneegiheedaa ts'ą' goorahahkat.” 
\s1 Juu Jesus Nilii ts'ą' Dee'in Yeeginkhii Nąįį 
\p  
\v 30 “Duuyeh shakhai' k'eegwiichy'aa t'ishi'in; Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa jyaa shahnyąą ji' gwizhrįh dinjii ts'ą' k'eegwahaldhat, shįį deegoochy'a' nihthan gwizhrįh gwik'it goo'aii kwaa gaa Shiti' shihił'e' ąįį deegoochy'a' niindhan izhit gwik'it goo'aii. 
\p  
\v 31 “Nijin ideenjit giihkhii dąį' zhit deihnyąą ąįį shats'an gwizhrįh t'igwinyąą kwaa.  
\v 32 Gaa zhit juu sheenjit ginkhii ts'ą' deeshahnyąą ąįį łi'didlii nilii gaashandaii.  
\v 33 Ąįį yihił'e' nąįį John ts'ą' nanoozhik ąįįts'ą' łi'didlii haa gavaa ginkhe'.  
\v 34 Dinjii andah t'iinyą' hįhjyaa gwat'aałchy'aa kwaa; neekhwazhii ji' eenjit gwizhrįh jyaa dihnyąą t'ihnyąą.  
\v 35 John adrii ts'ą' gach'ahdrii k'it t'inchy'aa, ch'ihłee gwizhrįh va'aadrii eet'oonghya'.  
\v 36 Gaa jii diihnyąą datthak John deiinyą' andaa gwihil'ee t'ihnyąą. Jidii gwitr'it t'agwał'in t'ee Shiti' geegwitr'it t'agoh'ya' shoonyąą shi'in, izhit deeshi'in gǫǫh'ya'! Gwik'iighai' t'ee Gwiti' shihił'e' gwigweheechy'aa.  
\v 37 Ąįįts'ą' Gwiti' shihił'e', ąįį nakhwandaa sheeginkhe'. Gwehkįį dohtth'ak kwaa, vinin gaa nǫh'in kwaa,  
\v 38 nakhwadrii zhit viginjik dhoh'ąįį chan kwaa, juu hił'e' ąįį k'injuhkhit kwaa geh'an.  
\v 39 Dęhtły'aa Choh kat aakin gǫǫ'įį, gwandaii ndaanąą'ąį' kwaa gaayiitr'ahaatsyaa nohthan geenjit. Ąįįt'ee vizhit shįį sheegirinkhii t'igwinyąą!  
\v 40 Ąįį googaa gwandaii khwa'yaa eenjit shįį shats'ą' hohjyaa kwaa. 
\p  
\v 41 “Dinjii shihił'ee akwat shihił'ee kwaa nąįį adan goots'an t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 42 Gaa shįį łyaa nakhwaashandaii; nakhwadrii zhit Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa veenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan khwa'įį kwaa.  
\v 43 Shiti' voozhri' zhit dząą gwats'ą' hoiizhii gaa shik'iinjuhkhit kwaa; gaa ch'izhii dinjii doozhri' zhit nakhwats'ą' neiinzhii ąįį vik'injahohkhit.  
\v 44 Nihłeenjit khadhoo'ee łyaa geet'ohthan, gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ch'ihłak zhrįh nilii ąįį hil'ee di'įį ąįį geenjit ninjich'ǫhthat kwaa. Jii kwaii jyaa dohchy'aa gwiizhit nats'ąą gwik'iinjuhohkhit?  
\v 45 Gwiti' vandah gwiizųų t'ahǫǫ'ya' nakhwahaihjyaa nohthan kwaa. Moses, vit'injyaahchy'aa ąįį jyaa t'ihee'yaa.  
\v 46 Moses łyaa vik'injuhkhit ji', shįį chan shik'iinjuhkhit haa nihk'it t'oonchy'aa, deenyąą t'ee shįį sheeginkhii t'inyąą.  
\v 47 Gaa deenaadąį' Moses deenyąą ts'ą' gwadąąntł'oo ąįį gwik'iinjuhkhit kwaa akwat gwiizhit nats'ąą shiginjik k'injihohkhit?” 
\c 6  
\s1 Jesus 5,000 Nąįį Ach'ah'al 
\r Matthew 14.13-21; Mark 6.30-44; Luke 9.10-17 
\p  
\v 1 Jii ąįįtł'ęę, Jesus Galilee van ndųhts'ąįį neiinzhii (Tiberias van chan oozhii)  
\v 2 Gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa haa iłts'ik lęįį nąįį shrineiinlik giiyąąh'ya' geh'an lęįį nąįį giitąįį adaa.  
\v 3 Jesus taih kat ditsyaa nąįį haa naadii.  
\v 4 It'ee niighit kwaa Jews Passover ch'arehee'aa geenigwiighit.  
\v 5 Jesus zhit gwa'an gwąąh'in akhai' lęįį nąįį yats'ą' adaa nigwiił'in ts'ą' Philip jyaa ahnyąą, “Jii dinjii lęįį nąįį nijin shih gavaanchy'aa tr'ooheekwat?”  
\v 6 (Philip deeheenjyaa ji' niindhan eenjit t'inyąą; adan ch'adąį' hee deehee'yaa gaandaii.) 
\p  
\v 7 Philip jyaa yahnyąą, “Jii dinjii nąįį nitsya' giin'al ji' gaa łųhchy'aa $200 gwandaa heelyaa.” \fig Łuhchy'aa ts'a' łuk.|src="hk00155b.tif" size="col" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 6.7" \fig* 
\p  
\v 8 Vitsyaa ch'ihłak ąįį Simon Peter vachaa Andrew oozhii ąįį t'iiyahnyąą,  
\v 9 “Yaagha' gwitee gwa'an tsyaa tsal dhidii ąįį łųhchy'aa barley ch'ihłoanli' ts'ą' łuk neekwaii haa di'įį. Gaa jii kwaii duuyeh jii dinjii nąįį datthak eenjit tr'oonadhat!” 
\p  
\v 10 Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Dinjii nąįį dook'įį gavahtsii,” (Zhat tł'oo kat goo'aii.) Ąįįts'ą' t'ee dinjii nąįį gaandii; dinjii 5000 andaa t'ąąnchy'aa zhat dilk'ii.  
\v 11 Jesus łųhchy'aa oonjik, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa mahsį' ahnyąą ts'ą' zhat dinjii dilk'ii nąįį teeyiłtsit. Łuk chan gwik'it t'inlik. Daanchy'aa tr'oo'aa giindhan gwik'it ch'igin'al.  
\v 12 Datthak gwintł'oo ch'igiin'al, ąįįtł'ęę ditsyaa nąįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Zhit jidii giiyeech'aa'al kwaii vit'ineegohjii, ch'ihłok gaa zhyaa an oolį' shrǫ'!”  
\v 13 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee giitineegwįłjik ts'ą', tyah ch'ihłoaatin ants'ą' neekwaii zhit deedigiiyiinlii, ąįįt'ee zhit łųhchy'aa ch'ihłoanli' ts'an reh. 
\p  
\v 14 Ąįį juu zhat dinjii dilk'ii ąįį Jesus gwitr'it gwintsii gwąąh'ya' nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nilii ts'ą' jii nankat gwats'ą' haazhii ąįį t'inchy'aa łee!”  
\v 15 Jesus et'ee gitr'ii'ee ji' gaa King giihahtsyaa eenjit giiyuuheendal ts'ą' gaandaii. Izhit geenjit neehoozhii ts'ą' adan zhrįh taih tee gwats'ą' haazhii. \fig none|src="lb00213b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 6.17" \fig* 
\s1 Jesus Chųų Kat Ahaa 
\r Matthew 14.22-33; Mark 6.45-52 
\p  
\v 16 Khaa nigwiighit gwiizhit vitsyaa nąįį ootthan van ts'ą' gahaajil  
\v 17 ts'ą' tr'ihchoo zhit giinjil ts'ą' van ndųhts'ąįį Capernaum kwaiik'it goo'aii gwats'ą' neegahoojil. Tǫǫ goodlit gaa tth'aii Jesus oo'ee nidii kwaa,  
\v 18 gwiizhit t'ee gwint'aii hiłtr'aii ts'ą' tit nitsii.  
\v 19 Vitsyaa nąįį tik akwat dǫǫ mile aanchy'aa niighit oondaa geekwaa gwiizhit Jesus chųų kat ahaa nigwigwiił'in, tr'ihchoo ts'ą' niighit kwaa niinzhii, łyaa datthak gihilghaa.  
\v 20 “Noojat kwaa, shįį t'ihchy'aa!” Jesus gavahnyąą  
\v 21 Jyaa diinyą' geh'an it'ee tr'ihchoo zhit giihaahchįį gwiizhit nijin gwats'ą' geedaa chy'aa zhat teeghaih nagwaanąįį. 
\s1 Dinjii Nąįį Jesus Keegogwah'in 
\p  
\v 22 Gęhdaa drin ąįį juu oonin Jesus vitsyaa nąįį haa haajil kwaa nąįį tr'ihchoo ch'ihłak tth'aii zhat dhitin łee gwik'igaanjik. Jesus ditsyaa nąįį haa haazhii kwaa gaagiindaii gaa ąįį tr'ihchoo zhat dhitin geh'an giiyehdan haajil łee gwik'igaanjik.  
\v 23 Gwiizhit Tiberias kwaiik'it gwachoo gwats'an tr'ihchoo lat zhat teedhidlit, geeghaih gwa'an Jesus łųhchy'aa eenjit K'eegwaadhat mahsį' ąįįnyą' ąįįtł'ęę gach'ąh'al izhit.  
\v 24 Nijin Jesus akwat vitsyaa nąįį haa zhat gwąąh'ya' kwaa dąį', tr'ihchoo zhit giinjil ts'ą' oonin Capernaum gwats'ą' giiyinkeegwahaah'yaa eenjit gwats'ą' gahaajil. 
\s1 Jesus T'ee Łųhchy'aa Zhit Gwandaii Nilii 
\p  
\v 25 Nijin ąįį dinjii nąįį van ndųhts'ąįį Jesus agogwąh'ąįį dąį' jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Geech'ǫąąhtan, nijin dąį' dząą k'eiindik?” 
\p  
\v 26 Jesus t'agavahnyąą, “Łi'didlii haa nakhwaa gwahaldak: Deenohthan gwik'it łųhchy'aa oo'al ąįį geh'an shinkeegoh'in gaa t'aih haa gwitr'it t'agwał'ya' gǫǫh'ya' geh'an nakwaa.  
\v 27 Shih khan iizųų ilii ąįį eenjit gwitr'it t'agoh'ya' shrǫ', shih khit vaa gwireheendaii ąįį gwandaa nizįį. Jii shih t'ee Gwidinji' nintł'eeyahahchaa. Gwiti' ąįį Gwidinji' deegwahtł'oo t'aih yintł'eiin'ąįį gwagwaakįį.” 
\p  
\v 28 Ąįįtł'ęę jii giiyųąhkat, “Jidii k'it t'inchy'aa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vigwitr'it t'igwehee'yaa t'agwaiinyąą?” 
\p  
\v 29 “Jii gwitr'it t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa t'akhwa'ya' nakhoonyaa, Juu hił'e' ąįį vik'injuhkhit.” Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 30 Jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Gwarahąąh'yaa ts'ą' gik'iinjireheeghit eenjit jidii t'aih diinandah t'ini'yaa? Deehini'yaa?  
\v 31 Yeenii diilak nąįį nangwinjir gwa'an łųhchy'aa giin'al, jii Dęhtły'aa Choh zhit geenjit jyaa digwinyąą: ‘Zheekat gwats'an ch'igihee'aa eenjit łųhchy'aa goots'ą' nahtsit.’” 
\p  
\v 32 “Łi'didlii haa nakhwaa gwahaldak!” Jesus gavahnyąą. “Jidii Moses nakhwantł'in'ąįį t'ee zheekat gwats'an łųhchy'aa t'inchy'aa kwaa. Shiti' ąįįt'ee łųhchy'aa zheekat gwats'an nakhwantł'in'ąįį t'igwii'in.  
\v 33 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa jidii łųhchy'aa gwantł'ahchak ąįį t'ee zheekat gwats'an nilii ts'ą' jii nankat gwandaii gwats'an ąhtsii.” 
\p  
\v 34 “K'eegwaadhat, jii łųhchy'aa khit geenjit diinantł'ahtsit.” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 35 “Ąįį łųhchy'aa vik'iighai' gwarandaii, ąįįt'ee shįį t'ihchy'aa,” Jesus gavahnyąą. “Juu shaa nilii nąįį duuyeh goozhit gwiłts'ik. Juu shik'iinjiighit nąįį duuyeh chųų dahłįį.  
\v 36 Shǫǫh'ya', nakhwaiinyą' gaa reh nihk'it gwik'iinjuhkhit kwaa.  
\v 37 Shiti' juu shantł'ahchįį ąįį nąįį shats'ą' heedaa. Juu shaa nilii nąįį duuyeh an gavaal'ee.  
\v 38 Zheekat gwats'an tr'iizhii ts'ą' jidii shi'yaa goo'aii sharahnyąą ąįį gwik'it t'ishi'yaa, shįį shakhai' t'ishi'in kwaa.  
\v 39 Juu shihił'e' t'ee jii kwaii t'ooshi'ya' shoonyąą: juu shantł'eegoovinlii nąįį gaatr'agwałjii shrǫ' shoonyąą, gaa Khaiinkǫǫ Drinzhit ndaanąą'ąį' ji', datthak gwandaii neegoohałtsyaa eenjit.  
\v 40 Shiti' jii kwaii gwinkeet'iindhan: Juu Gwidinji' k'injiighit ts'ą' giik'iinjiighit nąįį khit gwarandaii goots'an hałtsyaa. Khaiinkǫǫ Drin ndaanąą'ąį' ji' gwandaii neegoohałtsyaa.” 
\p  
\v 41 Israel gwich'in nąįį giiyeenjit vik'įį gwanlii, jii jyaa nyąą geh'an, “Ąįį łųhchy'aa vik'iighai' gwarandaii, ąįįt'ee shįį t'ihchy'aa.”  
\v 42 Izhit geh'an jyaa ginyąą, “Joseph vidinji' Jesus lee t'inchy'aa? Vahan, viti' haa gwiindaii t'inchy'aa adan t'inchy'aa ji', nats'ąą zheekat gwats'an ihshyaa nyąą t'inyąą?” 
\p  
\v 43 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Zhyaa gookhii kwaa!  
\v 44 Juu Shiti' shats'ą' yihił'ee nąįį ji' gwizhrįh shats'ą' heedaa; ts'ą' Khaiinkǫǫ Drin zhit ndaanąą'ąį' ji' gwandaii vats'an neehałtsyaa.  
\v 45 Yeenii Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nąįį jii dagogwąąntł'oo, ‘Dinjii datthak Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa googwahah'e'.’ Juu Shiti' diitth'ak ts'ą' yats'an googwaa'ee t'ee shaa nilii.  
\v 46 Gwiti' nah'ya' gwinyąą t'igwinyąą kwaa; juu Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ts'an ahaa zhrįh Gwiti' nah'ya' t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 47 Łi'didlii haa nakhwaa gwahaldak, juu gwik'iinjiighit di'įį t'ee khit gwarandaii hee'yaa.  
\v 48 Łųhchy'aa vik'iighai' gwarandaii t'ihchy'aa.  
\v 49 Yeenii nakhwalak nąįį nangwinjir gwa'an manna\f + \fr 6:49 \ft Manna t'ee łųhchy'aa k'it t'inchy'aa, niighit dąį' gwanaa Israel nąįį antł'eeyahtsit.\f* giin'al, gaa nigiindhat.  
\v 50 Gaa juu zheekat gwats'an łųhchy'aa a'aa t'ee khit gweheendaii.  
\v 51 Zheekat gwats'an łųhchy'aa gwandaii ąįį t'ihchy'aa. Juu yiin'al t'ee khit geenjit gweheendaii. Ąįį łųhchy'aa antł'eehałchaa t'ee shatthąį' t'inchy'aa. Jii nankat datthak gwantł'eehałchaa.” 
\p  
\v 52 “Jii gwigwiitth'ak dąį' geenjit Jews nąįį nihzheedagąąn'ee. Jii dinjii nats'ąą datthąį' diihah'aa t'inyąą?” ginyąą. 
\p  
\v 53 Jesus jyaa gwahnyąą: “Łi'didlii haa nakhwaa gwahaldak: Gwidinji' vatthąį' in'aa kwaa ts'ą' vadaa ninįį kwaa ji' duuyeh gwarandaii ni'įį.  
\v 54 Juu shatthąį' a'aa ts'ą' shadaa dinįį t'ee khit gwarandaii hee'yaa, ąįįts'ą' Khaiinkǫǫ Drin zhit ndaanąą'ąį' ji' vineegwahałdaii.  
\v 55 Shatthąį' t'ee łyaa shih t'inchy'aa, shadaa t'ee łi'haa tr'iheenjyaa eenjit t'inchy'aa.  
\v 56 Juu shatthąį' a'aa ts'ą' shadaa dinįį t'ee shizhit gwandaii ts'ą' shįį chan vizhit gwįįhdaii.  
\v 57 Gwiti' gwandaii ąįįt'ee shihił'e' ąįįts'ą' veh'an gwįįhdaii. Izhit gwik'it, juu sha'aa t'ee shęh'an gweheendaii.  
\v 58 Izhit geh'an t'ee jii łųhchy'aa zheekat gwats'an t'inchy'aa; yeenii nakhwalak łųhchy'aa giin'al ts'ą' nigiindhat ąįį łųhchy'aa k'it t'inchy'aa t'arahnyąą kwaa. Jii łųhchy'aa ąįį juu yiin'al ji' khit gweheendaii.” 
\p  
\v 59 Capernaum kwaiik'it gwizhit Israel tr'igiinkhii zheh gwizhit Jesus jii eenjit geech'ǫąąhtan. \fig Jesus, Israel tr'iginkhii zheh gwizhit geech'oahtan.|src="lb00244b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 6.59" \fig* 
\s1 Khit Gwireheendaii Eenjit Ginjih 
\p  
\v 60 Vitsyaa lęįį nąįį jii datthak eenjit gwigwiitth'ak dąį' jyaa ginyąą, “Jii jidii eech'ǫąąhtan łyaa vagwantrii. Juu yuuhaahky'aa ts'ą' gwik'it t'ihee'yaa?” 
\p  
\v 61 Jesus deeginyąą giiyaagwaandak kwaa gaa jidii eenjit nihzheedagąąn'ee gavaandaii ts'ą' ąįį eenjit jyaa gavahnyąą, “Jii jyaa diinyą' eenjit akhagohnyą' nohthan?  
\v 62 Ąįį ji', Gwidinji' gwehkįį nijin gwats'an tr'iinzhii gwits'eehoozhii nǫh'ya' ji' yu'?  
\v 63 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vanky'aa t'ee gwandaii gwats'an ąhtsii; gwatthąį' ąįį jyaa dagwąhtsii veegoo'aii kwaa. Jii ginjih eenakhwaagwaldak ąįįt'ee łyaa shroodiinyąą ts'ą' gwandaii nilii.  
\v 64 Googaa nakhwalat nąįį jii deiinyą' gwik'iinjiighit kwaa.” (Tr'ookit dąį' gwats'an Jesus juu gootee gwik'iinjiighit kwaa ts'ą' juu gwintł'eeyahahchyaa.)  
\v 65 Jii chan jyaanyąą, “Jii geh'an gwizhrįh jyaa nakhwaiinyą' duuyeh ch'ihłak gaa shats'ą' hahaii, Gwiti' jyąhts'ą' yeenjit gwiłtsąįį ji' gwizhrįh!” 
\p  
\v 66 Jii kwaii geh'an, vitsyaa lęįį nąįį akhagiiyuunyąą. 
\p  
\v 67 Ąįįts'ą' Jesus ditsyaa 12 nąįį t'ahnyąą, “Nakhwan chan gavaahohjyaa nohthan?” 
\p  
\v 68 Simon Peter jyaa yahnyąą, “Shik'eegwaadhat, juu vats'ą' tr'iheedaa gǫ'? Gwandaii ndaanąą'ąį' kwaa gweheelyaa eenjit nan zhrįh ginjik ni'įį.  
\v 69 Ąįįts'ą' juk Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vats'an Shroodiinyąą inlii naagwiindaii ts'ą' gwik'injiriighit.” 
\p  
\v 70 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “12 ǫhłįį ts'ą' gwitee tr'anakhwiilii, gaa nakhwatee ch'ihłak Ch'anky'aa Tr'aanduu nilii!”  
\v 71 (Simon Iscariot vigii eeginkhii t'inyąą. Judas t'ee Vitsyaa 12 nąįį tee dhidii gaa gwintł'eeyahahchyaa.) 
\c 7  
\s1 Jesus, Dachaa Nąįį Haa 
\p  
\v 1 Jii ąįįtł'ęę, Jesus Galilee nahkat datthak neehidik; Judea nahkat ąįį gwats'ą' neehidik gitr'ii'ee, Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį giiyuukhwaa giindhan geh'an.  
\v 2 Dinjii chan hee khaihłan niheedaa ts'ą' ąįį eenjit niighit kwaa Israel nąįį tr'ał zheh googwahahtsyaa nineegweedhat (Tabernacles googahnyąą).  
\v 3 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Jesus vachaa nąįį jyaa yahnyąą, “Dzaa gihłeehinkhaii ts'ą' Judea nahkat gwats'ą' hinkhaii, zhit deeni'in kwaii nitsyaa nąįį googwahąąh'yaa eenjit.  
\v 4 Ch'ihłak gwinzii shaagoondaii niindhan gwiizhit duuyeh dee'in nagwąąh'įį. Jyaa dini'in akwat jii nankat datthak naagweheendaii gwahtsii.”  
\v 5 (vachaa nąįį gaa giik'iinjiighit kwaa). 
\p  
\v 6 Jesus jyaa goovahnyąą, “Tth'aii gwats'ą' hihshyaa eenjit gwinzii zhat shaa nigwiighit kwaa. Nakhwan ąįį nijin ji' hohjyaa gaa gwinzii.  
\v 7 Jii nankat nąįį juu datthak sheet'iindhan kwaa gaa gootr'agwaanduu gwanlii goovaihnyąą geh'an, nakhwan ąįį jyaa nakhwagahthan kwaa.  
\v 8 Nijin dinjii khaihłan niinjil gwats'ą' hohjyaa ts'ą' ch'oh'aa. Shįį ąįį zhat nihihshyaa kwaa. Gwats'ą' hihshyaa eenjit tth'aii gwinzii zhat shaa nigwiighit kwaa.”  
\v 9 Jyaa diinyą' ąįįtł'ęę t'ee adan ąįį Galilee dhidii. 
\s1 Jesus, Tabernacles Ch'aga'aa Gwats'ą' Haazhii 
\p  
\v 10 Vachaa nąįį dinjii khaihłan niinjil gwats'ą' gahaajil ąįįtł'ęę Jesus gweentak gootąįį haazhii.  
\v 11 Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį dinjii khaihłan niinjil tee giiyinkeegwaah'in, “Adaajii t'inchy'aa?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 12 Datthak dinjii khaihłan niinjil tee dagaadzit ts'ą' giiyeeginkhii. Goolat nąįį, “Dinjii nizįį t'inchy'aa giiyahnyąą!” Goolat nąįį, “Akwaa, dinjii nan'ee t'inchy'aa!” giiyahnyąą.  
\v 13 Gaa ch'ihłak gaa gwandah giiyeeginkhii kwaa, Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį agąąnjat geh'an. 
\p  
\v 14 Drin dǫǫ gwizhit datthak ch'aga'aa ndaanagąąhjik gwiizhit Jesus Kharigidiinjii Zhee Gwachoh gwizhit nihdeiinzhii ts'ą' geech'ǫąąhtan. (Drin nihk'iidǫǫ gwizhit datthak dinjii ch'aga'aa)  
\v 15 Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį eenjit geegagoolii kwaa t'inyąą ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą, “Jii dinjii gooltin kwaa gwiizhit deegwiłtsii gwandaii t'inyąą?” 
\p  
\v 16 Jesus jyaa goovahnyąą, “Jidii eech'oaałtan shats'an t'igwinyąą kwaa gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa shihił'e' vats'an t'ihnyąą.  
\v 17 Juu Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa doo'ya' yuunyąą gwik'it t'inchy'aa ąįį t'ee jidii eech'oaałtan ąįį Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vats'an t'igwii'in akwat shats'an t'igwii'in ji' eenjit gaaheendaii.  
\v 18 Juu deeyiindhan zhrįh gwik'it geech'ǫąąhtan t'ee zhyaa sharahoh'e' niindhan, juu yihił'e' ąįį eenjit hil'ee niindhan ąįįt'ee łi'didlii nilii ts'ą' oots'it t'inyąą kwaa.  
\v 19 Deenaadąį' Moses va-law nakhwantł'in'ąįį, t'oonchy'aa. Nakhwatee ch'ihłak gaa Law k'eegwahthat kwaa. Jaghaii geenjit shęhdaa tr'agǫh'aa geetr'agoh'in?” 
\p  
\v 20 Izhit zhat dinjii lęįį nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Nizhit ch'anky'aa iizųų dhidii! Juu nęhdaa tr'igwihee'aa gwik'eegwandaii t'igwii'in?” 
\p  
\v 21 Jesus jyaa goovahnyąą. “Gwitr'it gwinzii ch'ihłak t'agwał'ya' ts'ą' datthak nakhwandaa t'igwiizhik.  
\v 22 Moses nakhwagii chyaatsal vadhah gihłeehoht'ii nakhwaihnyąą geh'an Neegwaazhii Drin chyaatsal vadhah gihłeehoht'ii, (Moses ąįį nakwaa gaa yeenii nakhwalak nąįį tr'ookit khagwigwiin'ąįį.)  
\v 23 Moses va-law łeehaanaii kwaa eenjit chyaatsal Neegwaazhii Drin vadhah gihłeerahaht'ii goo'aii ji' jaghaii Neegwaazhii Drin dinjii ts'ą' tr'iinjik eenjit shats'ą' nakhwak'įį gwanlii?  
\v 24 Dinjii gwiizųų t'ii'in dohnyą' shrǫ', nijin gwinzii t'ii'in dąį', K'eegwaadhat jyaa dagoo'ya' shrǫ' diinoohnyąą!” 
\s1 Jesus Lee Christ T'inchy'aa? 
\p  
\v 25 Jerusalem gwich'in lat nąįį jyaa diginyąą, “Jii dinjii lee giihaahkhwaa geegwitr'it t'agoogwah'in chy'aa?  
\v 26 Dzaa gooh'in! Juu nąįį datthak andah ginkhii googaa ch'ihłak gaa k'eegwiichy'aa t'inyąą kwaa. Kįh dilk'ii nąįį Christ t'inchy'aa giiyaandaii t'igii'in gwich'in.  
\v 27 Gaa Christ nijin vigwiilkįį ji' izhit ch'ihłak gaa nijin gwats'an t'inchy'aa giiyaaheendaii kwaa. Ąįįts'ą' diikhwan ąįį nijin gwats'an t'inchy'aa vaagwiindaii.” 
\p  
\v 28 Jesus Kharigidiinjii Zhee Gwachoh gwizhit gwint'aii ginkhii ts'ą' jyaanyąą, “Shaakhwandaii ts'ą' nijin gwats'an ihshyaa gaakhwandaii? Gaa shakhai' dząą gwats'ą' hoiizhii kwaa, juu dząą gwats'ą' shihił'e' t'ee łi'didlii nilii. Nan ąįį vaanandaii kwaa.  
\v 29 Gaa shįį ąįį vaashandaii, vats'an tr'iizhii ts'ą' shihił'e'.” 
\p  
\v 30 Ąįįts'ą' zheegwaazhrąįį nihdeegiihahchįį gwik'eegogwandaii, gaa ch'ihłak yakat naanjik kwaa, tth'aii vidrin nigwiighit kwaa geh'an.  
\v 31 Gaa zhat lęįį nąįį giik'iinjiighit ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą. “Nijin Christ vineegwiilkįį ji', jii dinjii dee'ya' ąįį andaa ts'ą' gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa t'ihee'yaa?” 
\s1 Gwiky'aahtii Nąįį Jesus Zheegwaazhrąįį Nigihiłchįį 
\p  
\v 32 Pharisee khaihkwaii nąįį dinjii tee gwa'an dagaadzit Jesus ts'ą' eegiginkhii googiitth'ak, ąįįts'ą' geedan chan ts'ą' giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį haa zheegwaazhrąįį nigiihahchyaa eenjit, gwak'ąąhtii nąįį giiyinkeehił'e'.  
\v 33 Jesus jyaa nyąą, “Tth'aii gwintsal gwizhrįh nakwaa t'ihihchy'aa, ąįįtł'ęę juu nakhwats'ą' shihił'e' ąįį vats'ą' neehihdyaa,  
\v 34 Shįį shinkeegoh'in gaa duuyeh shagoh'ąįį, nijuk neehidyaa duuyeh gwats'ą' hohjyaa geh'an.” 
\p  
\v 35 Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį jyaa nihłagaanyąą, “Nijuk gwats'ą' heekhaa ts'ą' khyų' vagwarahah'aa t'inyąą? Greek kwaiik'it Jews nąįį tee gwats'ą' hahaii ts'ą' geech'oohąąhchyaa lee t'inyąą?  
\v 36 Jyaa goovahnyąą, ‘Shikeegohǫǫh'yaa gaa duuyeh shagoh'ąįį, ts'ą' nijuk hihdyaa duuyeh gooh'in.’ Deiinyąą t'inyąą?” 
\s1 Chųų Vats'an Gwandaii Ninlaii 
\p  
\v 37 Ąįį ch'ara'aa drin ndaanąą'ąį' łyaa ch'andaa gwihil'ee. Izhit drin Jesus ndak nidhikhin ts'ą' gwint'aii jyaanyąą. “Juu chųų dahłįį shats'ą' hahaii ts'ą' chųų dinįį.  
\v 38 Dęhtły'aa Choh kat jyaa digwinyąą, ‘Juu shik'iinjiighit, vidrii zhit gwats'an chųų gwandaii t'iheenjyaa.’”  
\v 39 Juu yik'injiighit nąįį eenjit Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą ts'an gahaa'yaa eenjit Jesus geeginkhii t'inyąą. Izhit zhat dąį' ąįį Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą tth'aii goontł'eerah'ąįį kwaa, Jesus tth'aii hee niighit kwaa ts'ą' ch'eegwąhndit ilii kwaa geh'an. 
\s1 Dinjii Nąįį Nihłehjuk Gininjich'ahthat 
\p  
\v 40 Dinjii tee lęįį nąįį jii jyaa nyąą giiyiitth'ak dąį' jyaa ginyąą, “Jii dinjii Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii t'inchy'aa łee!” 
\p  
\v 41 Ch'izhii nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Christ t'inchy'aa oo'ee?” 
\p Gaa ch'izhii nąįį chan jyaa nyąą, “Christ duuyeh Galilee gwats'an ahaa t'inchy'aa!  
\v 42 Dęhtły'aa Choh kat, dinjii yeenii King David ts'an deedhaa ts'ą' Bethlehem gwizhit vigweheelyaa ąįįt'ee Christ, dinjii neehahshii heelyaa gwinyąą, ąįį kwaiik'it t'ee David gwiinch'į'.  
\v 43 Nihłitee giiyeenjit nihzheedagąąn'ee.  
\v 44 Goolat nąįį zheegwaazhrąįį narohchyaa giiyuunyąą, ch'ihłak gaa giikat naanjik kwaa.” 
\s1 Jews Kįh Dilk'ii Nąįį Giik'injiighit Kwaa 
\p  
\v 45 Ąįį gwiky'aahtii nąįį, giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį chan ts'ą' Pharisee khaihkwaii nąįį haa ts'eegahoojil, ąįį nąįį googaahkat, “Jaghaii adahaa oo'ee noohchįį kwaa?” 
\p  
\v 46 Ąįį gwiky'aahtii nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Jii dinjii łyaa vik'it t'igwinyąą kwaa t'arahnyąą!” 
\p  
\v 47 “Nakhwan chan neenakhwaiin'ak lee t'ohnyąą,” Pharisee khaihkwaii nąįį jii googaahkat.  
\v 48 “Diitee gwa'an nik'ee diikhaihkwaii akwat Pharisee khaihkwaii ch'ihłak yik'injiighit haakhwandaii?  
\v 49 Juk dząą dinjii nąįį Moses va-law haagiindaii kwaa, ąįį geh'an t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa doo'ya' gavoonyąą gwik'it t'iginchy'aa kwaa!” 
\p  
\v 50 Nicodemus t'ee Pharisee ch'ihłak nilii, ąįįt'ee gwehkįį dąį' Jesus eenoozhii ts'ą' nah'ya'. Nicodemus jyaa gavahnyąą,  
\v 51 “Dii-law zhit duuyeh dinjii tr'ahaahkhwaa gwats'ą' dee'ya' eenjit vęhdaa tr'agwara'aii goo'aii gwinyąą.” 
\p  
\v 52 Ąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Nan chan Galilee gwats'an inkhaa? Dęhtły'aa Choh kat vagwan'ee ąįį ji' t'ee Galilee gwats'an Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii ahaa kwaa gwiky'aahaandal.”  
\v 53 Ąįįtł'ęę t'ee juu nąįį datthak digizheh gwits'eegahoojil. 
\c 8  
\s1 Tr'injaa Vakai' T'inchy'aa Kwaa Giiky'aanjik 
\p  
\v 1 Gaa Jesus ąįį Taih Vakat Olives Nahshii ts'ą' haazhii.  
\v 2 Gęhdaa vanh dąį' hee Kharigidiinjii Zhee Gwachoh gwits'eehoozhii. Lęįį nąįį yeelin niinjil ts'ą' dhidii ts'ą' geegoovąąhtan.  
\v 3 Law eech'ǫąąhtan nąįį chan ts'ą' Pharisee nąįį haa dinjii va'at ch'izhii dinjii haa dhichįį ik'igaanjik ąįį nihdeegąąhchįį ts'ą' juu nąįį datthak ts'ą' nigiiyąąhchįį.  
\v 4 “Geech'ǫąąhtan,” Jesus agahnyąą, “Jii tr'injaa dinjii va'at ch'izhii dinjii haa dhichįį vik'igwaanjik.  
\v 5 Moses dii-law zhit tr'injaa jyaa dii'in t'ee kii haa tr'ahaahkhwaa goo'aii nyąą. Akwat, geenjit deehiinjyaa?”  
\v 6 Goodhaii nideegiihaatthal eenjit jyaa giiyahnyąą t'iginyąą, gwik'it t'iizhik giiyahaanjyaa eenjit. 
\p Gaa Jesus ąįį khatroogwiintthaii ts'ą' nankat danleetth'ak haa ch'adąąntł'oo.  
\v 7 Zhat nigiilzhii ts'ą' gwintł'oo giiyųąhkat, ndak ninehjin ts'ą' jyaa goovahnyąą, “Nakhwatee juu vatr'agwaanduu gwakwaa, ąįį jii tr'injaa adan tr'ookit kii haa yatthat.”  
\v 8 Chan hee khatroogwiintthaii ts'ą' nankat ch'adąąntł'oo. 
\p  
\v 9 Nijin jii gwigwiitth'ak dąį', gootee googwąąnchy'aa ts'ą' gihłeegihii'oo, juu vaghaii lęįį nąįį tr'ookit. Jesus zhrįh zhat dhidii, ąįį tr'injaa chan zhat nadhat.  
\v 10 Ndak ninehjin ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Tr'injaa nijin neegahoojil? Nik'ee gwintł'ee nahahchyaa ch'ihłak dząą dhidii?” 
\p  
\v 11 “Shik'eegwaadhat datthak gihłeegahoojil,” ąįį tr'injaa nyąą. 
\p “Akwat, shįį chan duuyeh narahaahkhwaa geenjit gwintł'ee nahałchįį t'oonchy'aa, oo'an neehiindii ts'ą' chan natr'agwaanduu neegooli' shrǫ'.” Jesus yahnyąą. 
\s1 Jesus Nankat Gwach'ahdrii Nilii 
\p  
\v 12 Nijin chan hee Jesus goots'ą' neegeedi', “Jii nankat gwach'aadrii ihłii. Juu shaa ahaa t'ee gwandaii aadrii hee'yaa ts'ą' chan duuyeh tǫǫ gwizhit ahaa.” 
\p  
\v 13 Ąįį Pharisee khaihkwaii nąįį jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Et'ee nahzhrįį ideenjit ginkhii akwat deiinyąą datthak zhyaa t'iinyąą.” 
\p  
\v 14 “Nakwaa!” Jesus gavahnyąą, “Shahzhrįh ideenjit giihkhii ji' gaa deihnyąą datthak łi'didlii nilii t'inchy'aa, nijin gwats'an ihshyaa akwat nijin gwits'eehihdyaa gaashandaii geh'an. Nakhwan ąįį nijin gwats'an tr'iizhii akwat nijin neehihdyaa gaakhwandaii kwaa.  
\v 15 Dinjii vidrii zhit t'oonchy'aa gaakhwandaii kwaa gwiizhit jyaanchy'aa dohnyąą, shįį ąįį duuyeh dinjii agwarahahshįį eenjit gwantł'ałchįį.  
\v 16 Gaa jyaa dihiinjyaa ji', łi'didlii haa t'ihihjyaa, shįį zhrįh jyąhts'ą' sheegoo'aii kwaa, Gwiti' shihił'e' chan shaa t'inchy'aa.  
\v 17 Nakhwa-law zhit gwadanakhwatł'oo, nijin vandah t'igwiizhik neekwaii nąįį łi'didlii t'igwinyąą ginyąą dąį' gwizhrįh łi'didlii nilii.  
\v 18 Ideenjit giihkhii ąįįts'ą' Shiti' shihił'e' chan sheenjit ginkhii.” 
\p  
\v 19 “Niti' adaajii?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p “Shaakhwandaii kwaa ts'ą' Shiti' chan vaakhwandaii kwaa, shaakhwandaii ji' Shiti' chan vaakhwahandaii goo'aii t'oonchy'aa.” Jesus gavahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 20 Kharigidiinjii Zhee Gwachoh gwizhit jii kwaii jyaa nyąą, ąįį nijin gwizhit gwintł'eegaandak goo'aii gwizhit. Ąįįts'ą' t'ee ch'ihłak gaa zheegwaazhrąįį niyąąhchįį kwaa, tth'aii zhat veegoo'aii kwaa geh'an. 
\s1 Nijin Gwats'an Hihshyaa Duuyeh Gwats'ą' Hohjyaa 
\p  
\v 21 Jesus chan hee jyaa dagoovahnyąą, “Hihshyaa t'oonchy'aa; shikeegohǫǫh'yaa gaa nakhwatr'agwaanduu zhit nahohthaa nijuk hihshyaa izhit duuyeh gwats'ą' hohjyaa.” 
\p  
\v 22 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Israel gwakhaihkwaii nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Nijin gwats'ą' hihshyaa ąįį duuyeh gwats'ą' hohjyaa nyąą akwat adahaaghwaa lee t'inyąą?” 
\p  
\v 23 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Yeezhak gwats'an ohdaa gaa shįį ąįį yeedak gwats'an ihshyaa. Dzaa nankat gwats'an tr'oojil gaa shįį ąįį nankat gwats'an ihshyaa kwaa.  
\v 24 Ąįį geh'an t'ee nakhwatr'agwaanduu zhit nahohthaa nakhwaihnyąą. ‘Juu Ihłii Ąįį Ihłii.’ Gwik'injuhkhit kwaa ji' t'ee ąįį geh'an nakhwatr'agwaanduu zhit nahohthaa.” 
\p  
\v 25 “Juu inlii?” giiyahnyąą? 
\p Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Juu ihłii tr'ookit dąį' gwats'an nakhwaihnyąą ąįį ihłii t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 26 Deekhwa'ya' eenjit gwintł'ee nakhwahałchyaa, gaa juu shihił'e' ąįį Łi'didlii nilii, ąįįts'ą' jidii vats'an gwiihtth'ak ąįį zhrįh jii nankat eegwahaaldak t'ihnyąą.” 
\p  
\v 27 Gwiti' eeginkhii t'inyąą giiyaandaii kwaa.  
\v 28 Ts'ą' t'ee Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Nijin Gwidinji' ndak gahoohchįį t'ee ‘Juu Ihłii Ąįį Ihłii!’ gaakhwahandaii, izhit t'ee shakhai' t'ihnyąą kwaa ts'ą' Gwiti' jidii geeshoołtin ąįį gwaałtan t'ihnyąą gaakhwahandaii.  
\v 29 Juu shihił'e' ąįį shaa nilii, akhashoonyąą kwaa, doo'ya' shoonyąą gwik'it t'ishi'in geh'an.” 
\p  
\v 30 Lęįį nąįį Jesus deiinyą' giik'injiighit. 
\s1 Deenaadąį' Gwats'an Dinjii Abraham Ts'an Deedhaa 
\p  
\v 31 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee juu gootee giik'iinjiighit nąįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Jii geenakhwaałtan kwaii gwik'eegǫhthat ji', łyaa shitsyaa ǫhłįį,  
\v 32 łi'didlii haakhwahandaii, ts'ą' gadanakhwahahchyaa.” 
\p  
\v 33 “Abraham vats'an direedhaa, ąįįts'ą' ch'ihłak gaa ts'an tr'iinli' kwaa. Deiinyąą t'iinyąą, ‘Gadanakhwahałchyaa.’ diinyąą dąį'?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 34 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Łi'didlii eenakhwaagwahaldak: juu datr'agwaanduu gwahtsii t'ee tr'aanduu goots'ą' k'eegwaadhat k'it t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 35 Ąįį juu slave nilii nąįį digizheh k'ąą gwizhit dagalak nąįį tee gwats'an giheelyaa kwaa gaa Gwidinji' ąįį khit zhat gwats'an heelyaa.  
\v 36 Gwidinji' gadanakhwaahchįį ji', t'ee łyaa khit geenjit gadahohdaa.  
\v 37 Abraham ts'an dohthaa gaashandaii, ąįį googaa shęhdaa tr'agahoh'aa geetr'agoh'in, jidii geenakhwaałtan gwik'iinjuhkhit kwaa geh'an.  
\v 38 Jidii Shiti' shats'ą' gwigweełch'in ąįį geenakhwaagwaldak, gaa nakhwan ąįį nakhwati' deenakhwahnyąą ąįį gwizhrįh gwik'eegǫhthat.” 
\p  
\v 39 “Diilak t'ee Abraham t'inchy'aa,” giiyahnyąą. 
\p “Abraham vats'an dohthaa ji', nakhwan chan vigwitr'it t'agahoh'yaa.  
\v 40 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vats'an łi'didlii diitth'ak ąįį geenakhwaagwaldak gwizhrįh t'ishi'ya'. Ąįį googaa shęhdaa tr'agahoh'aa geetr'agoh'in. Abraham jyaa dee'ya' kwaa t'oonchy'aa!  
\v 41 Nakhwati' dee'ya' ąįį vik'it t'akhwa'in,” Jesus gavahnyąą. 
\p “Kwaiitak-gii tr'inlii kwaa, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa zhrįh diiti', diikhwan zhrįh vidinji' łi'didlii tr'iinlii,” ginyąą. 
\p  
\v 42 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa nakhwati' nilii ji', sheet'ahoohkhyaa, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vats'an ihshyaa ts'ą' juk dząą dhidii geh'an. Shakhai' dząą gwats'ą' hoiizhii kwaa gaa dząą gwats'ą' shihił'e'.  
\v 43 Jaghaii deiinyąą t'iihnyąą datthak gaakhwandaii kwaa? Deiinyąą t'ihnyąą ąįį goohtth'ak nohthan kwaa geh'an t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 44 Nakhwati' Ch'anky'aa Tr'aanduu vigii ǫhłįį ts'ą' nakhwati' nilii ts'ą' doo'ya' nakhoonyaa gwik'it t'akhwa'in. Tr'ookit dąį' gwats'an dinjii aghan nilii. Ch'ihłok gaa łi'didlii nilii kwaa, łi'didlii vizhit kwaa geh'an. Oots'it zhrįh gwizhit nilii geh'an tr'oots'it gwiti' nilii.  
\v 45 Łi'didlii eegiihkhii geh'an shik'injuhkhit kwaa.  
\v 46 Nakhwatee ch'ihłak nik'ee vandah shatr'agwaanduu gwałtsii shąąh'ya'? Łi'didlii eegiihkhii t'ihnyąą ji' jaghaii shik'injuhkhit kwaa?  
\v 47 Juu Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ts'an ahaa t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa viginjik oołk'įį. Nakhwan ąįį Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vats'an ohdaa kwaa, ąįį geh'an ch'oodǫǫhk'įį kwaa t'oonchy'aa.” 
\s1 Nats'ąą Jesus Ideeginkhii 
\p  
\v 48 Israel nąįį Jesus jyaa gahnyąą, “Samaria gwich'in inlii ts'ą' nizhit ch'anky'aa iizųų dhidii ąįį łyaa lee t'igwinyąą?” 
\p  
\v 49 “Shizhit ch'anky'aa iizųų kwaa t'oonchy'aa,” Jesus gavahnyąą, “Shiti' hooł'e', gaa nakhwan ąįį shahooh'ee kwaa.  
\v 50 Sharahoh'e' yiihthan kwaa, gaa ch'ihłak zhrįh sharahoh'e' yiindhan, ts'ą' adan ąįį jidii gwiizųų akwat gwinzii haa heenjyaa.  
\v 51 Jii t'ee łyaa łi'didlii. Juu shik'eegwahthat t'ee duuyeh niighit.” 
\p  
\v 52 Israel nąįį jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Et'ee nizhit ch'anky'aa iizųų dhidii naagwiindaii! Abraham chan niindhat, yeenii Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nąįį chan niinjik, googaa gwiizhit jyaa diinyąą, ‘Juu shik'eegwahthat t'ee duuyeh niighit.’  
\v 53 Diilak Abraham chan ts'ą' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nąįį niinjik. Abraham vandaa t'agwahtsii sheegoo'aii diinyąą lee t'iinyąą? Jidii ihłii niindhan?” 
\p  
\v 54 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Ideenjit zhrįh yinjiihooh'ee ji', ąįį yeenjihooh'ee giilį' nilii. Shiti' sheeyinjihił'ee. Ąįįt'ee nakhwan chan Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vohnyąą reh.  
\v 55 Ch'ihłok gaa vaakhwandaii kwaa gaa shįį ąįį gwinzii vaashandaii. Vaashandaii kwaa dihnyąą ji' t'ee nakhwak'it oohihts'it. Gaa vaashandaii ts'ą' viginjik k'eegwałthat.  
\v 56 Nakhwalak Abraham nijin drin shahąąh'yaa ji' geenjit shoo nilii, ch'adąį' gwąąh'ya' ts'ą' shoo dhidlit.” 
\p  
\v 57 Jews nąįį jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Tth'aii googaa 50 years old inlii kwaa gwiizhit Abraham nah'ya'?” 
\p  
\v 58 “Łi'didlii haa giihkhii! Abraham vehkii dąį' gwats'an Shįį Ihłii!” Jesus gavahnyąą 
\p  
\v 59 Kii giiyeenjit teegwįłjik gaa Jesus gweentak Kharigidiinjii Zhee Gwachoh cheehoozhii. 
\c 9  
\s1 Jesus, Dinjii Vandee Kwaa Haagweech'in Neegwiłtsąįį 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus ahaa gwiizhit dinjii vandee kwaa ts'ą' vagoodlit niił'in.  
\v 2 Vitsyaa nąįį yuahkat, “Geech'ǫąąhtan, vandee kwaa ts'ą' vagoodlit ąįį juu vatr'agwaanduu t'oonchy'aa? Adan vats'an akwat viyehghan nąįį?” 
\p  
\v 3 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Vandee kwaa ąįį adan vatr'agwaanduu akwat viiyehghan gootr'agwaanduu gwadrąįį t'oonchy'aa kwaa. Gaa jii dinjii vandee kwaa ąįį, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vat'aii gwizhrįh eegweheechy'aa eenjit vaagweech'in neegahoodlit.  
\v 4 Tth'aii drin gwanlii gwiizhit juu shihił'e' ąįį nihk'it vigwitr'it t'agwarahah'yaa gwizhrįh goo'aii. Et'ee tǫǫ gweheelyaa ts'ą' duuyeh tǫǫ gwitr'it t'agwarah'in.  
\v 5 Dzaa nankat dhiidii gwiizhit, jii nankat eenjit aadrii ihłii.” 
\p  
\v 6 Jii jyaa diinyą' ąįįtł'ęę, Jesus nankat haazhree ts'ą' łųh niłtraa ąįį dinjii vaagweech'in kwaa andee kat giinjik ts'ą'  
\v 7 jyaa yahnyąą, “Oo'an Siloam\f + \fr 9:7 \ft Siloam, Israel nąįį googinjik zhit “yihił'e'” googwahnyąą.\f* teełtin gwats'ą' hinkhaii zhat chųų haa neech'aanjii.” Ąįįts'ą' ąįį dinjii zhat gwats'ą' haazhii ts'ą' neech'aanjik ts'ą' vaagweech'in ts'ą' k'inidik. 
\p  
\v 8 Ąįį yeeghaii gwich'įį nąįį chan ts'ą' juu khit ch'oodiikwat yąąh'in nąįį ch'agoahkat, “Jii dinjii lee dhidii ts'ą' ch'oodiikwat chy'aa?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 9 Goolat nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Adan t'inchy'aa,” goolat nąįį chan jyaa ginyąą “Adan t'inchy'aa kwaa, gaa yigwich'in.” 
\p Ąįį dinjii jyaa gavahnyąą “Ąįį dinjii t'ee shįį t'ihchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 10 “Nats'ąą naagweech'in needhindlit?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 11 “Dinjii Jesus oaazhii ąįį nankat haazhree ts'ą' łųh niłtraa ąįį shandee kat giinjik ts'ą' jyaa shahnyąą, ‘Oo'an Siloam teełtin gwats'ą' hinkhaii zhat chųų haa neech'aanjii.’ Zhat gwats'ą' hoiizhii neech'aaljik ts'ą' shaa gweech'in needhiidlit,” goovahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 12 “Adaajii?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p “Adaajii vaashandaii kwaa,” goovahnyąą. 
\s1 Pharisee Nąįį Nats'ąą Vaagweech'in Neegwahoodlit Li' Eenjit Gwankeegoogwah'in 
\p  
\v 13 Ąįįtł'ęę t'ee ąįį dinjii vandee kwaa iinli' chy'aa Pharisee nąįį ts'ą' giihiłchįį.  
\v 14 Nijin ąįį Jesus dinjii andee łųh t'iinlik dąį' vaagweech'in neeyiłtsąįį drin Neegwaazhii Drin gwanlii.  
\v 15 Pharisee nąįį ąįį dinjii nats'ąą vaagweech'in neekhwadlit eenjit giiyųąhkat. Goovaagwaandak, “Shandee łųh t'inlik ąįįtł'ęę neech'aaljik ts'ą' juk shaagweech'in,” nyąą. 
\p  
\v 16 Pharisee lat nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Jii dinjii juu t'iizhik Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ts'an t'inchy'aa kwaa, Neegwaazhii Drin jyaa dihee'yaa kwaa goo'aii ąįį gwik'eegwahthat kwaa geh'an.” 
\p Goolat nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Nats'ąą dinjii vatr'agwaanduu gwanlii ąįį gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa t'ihee'yaa?” ąįįts'ą' t'ee datthak geenjit nihzheedagąąn'ee. 
\p  
\v 17 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Pharisee nąįį chan hee giiyųąhkat, “Naagweech'in neegwiłtsąįį akwat veenjit deehiinjyaa?” 
\p “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nilii t'inchy'aa,” jyaa nyąą. 
\p  
\v 18-19 Israel kįh dilk'ii nąįį ąįį dinjii vandee kwaa iinli' ąįįtł'ęę vaagweech'in neekhwadlit ąįį gwik'iinjigiighit gitr'igii'ee, ąįįts'ą' t'ee giiyehghan nąįį jii oahkat, “Jii lee nigii tsyaa? Vandee kwaa ts'ą' vagoodlit vohnyąą gwiizhit jaghaii juk vaagweech'in gǫ'?” 
\p  
\v 20 Ąįį viyehghan jyaa ginyąą, “Diigii t'inchy'aa ts'ą' vandee kwaa ts'ą' vagoodlit vaagwiindaii.  
\v 21 Gaa jaghaii juk vaagweech'in neekhwadlit akwat juu vaagweech'in neeyiłtsąįį vaagwiindaii kwaa. Oohkat, vaghaii lęįį t'inchy'aa ts'ą' adakhai' nakhwaagwaandak!”  
\v 22 Ąįį viyehghan nąįį Israel kįh dilk'ii nąįį agąąnjat geh'an jyaa diginyąą t'iginyąą, ąįį juu Jesus ąįį Christ t'inchy'aa nyąą t'ee Israel tr'igiinkhii zheh cheerahahchyaa ch'adąį' ginyą' geh'an.  
\v 23 Izhit geh'an t'ee “Vaghaii lęįį t'inchy'aa ts'ą' oohkat!” googahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 24 Chan hee ąįį dinjii vandee kwaa iinli' chy'aa aanaii giiyahnyąą ts'ą' jyaa giiyahnyąą “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vandah łi'didlii haa geegwandak! Jii dinjii vatr'agwaanduu gwanlii ts'ą' vaagwiindaii.” 
\p  
\v 25 “Vatr'agwaanduu gwanlii akwat vatr'agwaanduu gwakwaa ji' gaa vaashandaii kwaa t'inchy'aa,” ąįį dinjii nyąą. “Ch'ihłak gwizhrįh gaashandaii, shandee kwaa gwiili' gaa juk shaagweech'in neegakhwadlit.” 
\p  
\v 26 “Deeniinlik? Nats'ąą naagweech'in neegwiłtsąįį?” giiyųąhkat. 
\p  
\v 27 “Ch'adąį' nakhwaagwaldak t'oonchy'aa, gaa khų' ch'oodǫǫhk'įį. Jaghaii chan hee geenakhwaagwaldak yuuhthan? Nakhwan chan vitsyaa ǫhłį' nohthan?” gavahnyąą 
\p  
\v 28 Ąįįts'ą' shruk haa giits'ą' khaginkhee, “Ąįį dinjii vitsyaa iinlii; diikhwan ąįį vitsyaa tr'iinlii.  
\v 29 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa, Moses ts'ą' giinkhe' gaagwiindaii; ąįį dinjii t'avaiinyąą, nijin gwats'an tr'iinzhii gaa vaagwiindaii kwaa t'inchy'aa!” 
\p  
\v 30 Ąįį dinjii jyaa gavahnyąą, “Łyaa shandaa t'ohnyąą, nijin gwats'an tr'iinzhii vaakhwandaii kwaa gaa shaa gweech'in neegwiłtsąįį!  
\v 31 Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vatr'agwaanduu gwanlii nąįį oołk'įį kwaa vaagwiindaii. Dinjii nikiigwah'ee ts'ą' doo'ya' gavoonyąą gwik'it t'inchy'aa nąįį oołk'įį vaagwiindaii.  
\v 32 Jii nan goodlit dąį' gwats'an dinjii ch'izhii dinjii haagweech'in neegwiłtsąįį gwinyąą gwiriitth'ak kwaa.  
\v 33 Jii dinjii Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vats'an t'inchy'aa kwaa ji' duuyeh k'eegwiichy'aa t'ii'in.” 
\p  
\v 34 Jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Tr'agwaanduu gwitr'it gwizhit nagoodlit ts'ą' gwizhit diink'iindhat. Geediinǫąąhtan gwik'eegwiindaii lee t'iinyąą?” Ąįįts'ą' Israel tr'igiinkhii zheh gwizhit cheet'eegiiheełnaii. 
\s1 Gwik'injigwiighit Gwiky'aanjii Kwaa Nąįį 
\p  
\v 35 Ąįį dinjii cheet'eeheełnaii gwinyąą ąįį Jesus gwiitth'ak. Yagwąh'ąįį ts'ą' jyaa yahnyąą, “Gwidinji' k'injiinghit?” 
\p  
\v 36 Ąįį dinjii jyaa nyąą, “Juu t'inchy'aa veeshaagwandak vik'injihihthaa eenjit!” 
\p  
\v 37 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Ch'adąį' nah'ya' t'inchy'aa, ąįį juu t'avaiinyąą et'ee juk zhat nats'ą' giihkhii.” 
\p  
\v 38 “K'eegwaadhat iinlii it'ee nik'iinjihkhit!” Ąįį dinjii yahnyąą ts'ą' yats'ą' nikiigwiintthaii. 
\p  
\v 39 Jesus jyaa nyąą, “Dinjii oohaałkat eenjit dząą nankat gwats'ą' hoiizhii t'ishi'in. Vaagweech'in kwaa nąįį haagweech'in neegwahałtsyaa ts'ą' juu vaagweech'in adoodiinyąą nąįį chan haagweech'in kwaa neehałtsyaa eenjit.” 
\p  
\v 40 Pharisee lat juu zhat yaadilk'ii nąįį jyaa nyąą giiyiitth'ak dąį' jii giiyųąhkat, “Diikhwan chan diinaagweech'in kwaa diinyąą lee t'inyąą?” 
\p  
\v 41 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Nakhwaa gweech'in kwaa ji', duuyeh nakhwatr'agwaanduu gwilii gaa ‘Diinaagweech'in,’ dohnyąą gwiizųų t'ohnyąą gaakhwandaii gaa jyaa dohnyąą t'ohnyąą ąįį ji' tth'aii nakhwatr'agwaanduu gwanlii.” \fig Divii k'ąąhtii.|src="bk00004b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 9.41" \fig* 
\c 10  
\s1 Divii K'ąąhtii ts'ą' Didivii Nąįį Haa 
\p  
\v 1 “Łi'didlii eenaagwagwahaldak! Juu divii dehk'it goo'aii ąįį gindeiinvyaa k'it k'ii'ee nihdeiinzhii kwaa ts'ą' ch'adanh k'ii'ee gwats'ą' haazhii t'ee ch'an'įį ts'ą' dinjii łi'didlii nilii kwaa t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 2 Gaa divii k'ąąhtii nąįį gindeiinvyaa k'it gwizhrįh nihdeegadal.  
\v 3 Gindeiinvyaa k'ąąhtii nąįį nihdeegiiyahchik; didivii tee ch'oaazhri' gwizhrįh giiyiitth'ak ts'ą' giits'ą' chagahdal ts'ą' jyąhts'ą' cheegavahaazhik.  
\v 4 Datthak cheegoovaahchik dąį' goots'įį ahaa ts'ą' giitąįį adaa, giideezhuh diitth'ak ts'ą' giiyaandaii geh'an.  
\v 5 Ch'izhii dinjii ąįį duuyeh tąįį geedaa; t'oohłii galgahahdaa, giideezhuh haa heendaii kwaa geh'an.” 
\p  
\v 6 Jesus jii gwandak gwah'įį gwizhit geegavaagwaandak gaa deegavahnyąą ąįį deegwinyąą t'igwinyąą gaagiindaii kwaa. \fig Divii dehk'it.|src="lb00014b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 10.6" \fig* 
\s1 Jesus Divii K'ąąhtii Nizįį Nilii 
\p  
\v 7 Ąįįts'ą' Jesus chan hee jyaa nyąą, “Łi'didlii eenakhwaagwahaldak: Shįį t'ee divii nąįį eenjit gindeiinvyaa ihłii.  
\v 8 Juu shehkii nihdeiinjil nąįį t'ee ch'an'įį giinlii ts'ą' łi'didlii giinlii kwaa; gaa divii nąįį googoołk'įį kwaa.  
\v 9 Shįį t'ee gindeiinvyaa t'ihchy'aa juu shik'iighai' gindeiinvyaa k'it nihdeiinzhii t'ee neegoorahahshii, nihdineeheedik ts'ą' chineeheedik ts'ą' tł'oo chyah nizįį hee'aa.  
\v 10 Ch'an'įį nąįį ch'igiheen'įį, dinjii ęhdaa tr'agwa'ak akwat an googwahahtsyaa eenjit gwizhrįh nihdeegadal. Shįį ąįį gwinzii gogweheendaii ji' eenjit dząą nankat gwats'ą' hoiizhii t'ishi'in. 
\p  
\v 11 “Divii k'ąąhtii nizįį ihłii. Divii k'ąąhtii nizįį didivii eenjit naheedhaa ji' gaa t'inchy'aa.  
\v 12 Divii k'ąąhtii nilii kwaa ąįį laraa t'įį divii k'ąąhtii ts'ą' divii di'įį kwaa ąįį zhoh niił'in dąį' divii akhoonyąą ts'ą' zhoh goolat teegwįłjik ts'ą' shrihteegaajil.  
\v 13 Ąįį divii laraa t'įį k'ąąhtii ąįį t'oohłii divii ts'į' neehilgit, zhyaa laraa t'įį tr'agwah'in geh'an divii eenjit niinjich'adhat kwaa. 
\p  
\v 14-15 “Divii k'ąąhtii nizįį ihłii. Gwiti' shaandaii ts'ą' shįį chan vaashandaii, izhit gwik'it shidivii nąįį haashandaii ts'ą' geedan chan shaagiindaii. Gooveenjit ji' gaa nihihthaa.  
\v 16 Goolat nąįį ch'adanh giilk'ii. Oo'ee neegoohihłyaa, goots'ą' giihkhii dąį' shigiitth'ak ts'ą' nihteeneegiheedaa ts'ą' ch'ihłak giheelyaa ts'ą' divii k'ąąhtii ch'ihłak zhrįh gook'eehąąhtyaa. 
\p  
\v 17 “Gwiti' sheet'iindhan geh'an nihihthaa galjat kwaa, ąįįtł'ęę neegwihįhdaii chan sheenjit gwiłtsąįį.  
\v 18 Ch'ihłak gaa gwįhdaii shihłeegwehee'aa kwaa, shakhai' gwintł'eehih'aa. Shakhai' gwintł'eehih'aa ts'ą' shakhai' chan noohihdal. Jii t'ee Shiti' jyąhts'ą' sheenjit gwiłtsąįį.” 
\p  
\v 19 Jii ginjik kwaii eh'an chan hee nihzheedagąąn'ee  
\v 20 Gootee lęįį nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Vizhit ch'anky'aa iizųų dhidii! Vagwandaii iizųų! Jaghaii oodǫǫhk'įį t'ohchy'aa?” 
\p  
\v 21 Gaa ch'izhii nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Dinjii vizhit ch'anky'aa iizųų gwiizhit jyąhts'ą' ginkhii kwaa t'oonchy'aa! Nats'ąą ch'anky'aa iizųų dinjii vandee kwaa haagweech'in neegwahahtsyaa?” 
\s1 Jews Nąįį Jesus Ik'injigiighit Kwaa 
\p  
\v 22 Et'ee khaii gwanlii Jerusalem gwizhit Hanukkah khaihłan nineegiidal nineegwiidhat; \fig Solomon's Porch.|src="lb00248b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 10.22" \fig* 
\v 23 Jesus ąįį Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh gwizhit Solomon's Porch t'agahnyąą gwizhit gwa'an neehidik.  
\v 24 Nijin ąįį Jews nąįį Jesus eelin nigiilzhii ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą dąį', “Deegwiłkhyuk diits'ą' gwit'eegwaha'aa t'inchy'aa? Łi'didlii haa diinaa gwandak nan lee Christ inlii?” 
\p  
\v 25 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Ch'adąį' hee nakhwaagwadhaldak gaa shik'iinjuhkhit kwaa; nakhwandah Shiti' voozhri' zhit t'ishi'in gooh'in t'ee juu ihłii gwigweech'in.  
\v 26 Gaa shik'iinjuhkhit kwaa geh'an shidivii hohłyaa kwaa.  
\v 27 Shidivii nąįį shiginjik haandaii, shįį chan goovaashandaii ts'ą' shatąįį geedaa.  
\v 28 Khit geenjit gwigweheendaii nigwii'ąįį, ts'ą' duuyeh gahchįį; ch'ihłak gaa duuyeh shats'an yan'įį.  
\v 29 Shiti' shintł'eegoovinlii ts'ą' ch'andaa t'aht'aii, ts'ą' duuyeh gaa Shiti' vats'an gooroonjii.  
\v 30 Gwiti', shįį haa ch'ihłak tr'iinlii.” 
\p  
\v 31 Ąįįts'ą' Jews nąįį chan hee Jesus eenjit kii tee gwigwįłjik.  
\v 32 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Nakhwandah gwitr'it gwinzii gwinlęįį t'ishizhik, ąįįt'ee Gwiti' shintł'eegwiin'ąįį; ąįį gwitee jidii shrit t'ishizhik eenjit kii haa shohohkhwaa?” 
\p  
\v 33 Israel nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Ąįį gwitr'it gwinzii kwaii eenjit kii haa narahaahkhwaa t'igwii'in kwaa gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vinehts'į' ginkhii ąįį eenjit. Dinjii zhrįh iinlii, gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa hinlyaa gwik'eegwiindaii!” 
\p  
\v 34 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Nakhwa-law Dęhtły'aa Choh kat jii deegwinyąą khit ts'ą' łyaa łi'didlii ąįį gaagwiindaii; ‘Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ǫhłįį,’ nyąą,  
\v 35 zhit juu Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Viginjik antł'inlii nąįį.  
\v 36 Shįį ąįį, Gwiti' gwiteetr'ashąhchįį ts'ą' nankat gwats'ą' shihił'e'. Nats'ąą Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidinji' ihłii dihnyąą eenjit vinehts'į' giihkhii shohnyąą t'ohnyąą?  
\v 37 Shiti' vigwitr'it t'agwał'in shi'in kwaa ji' shik'iinjuhkhit kwaa.  
\v 38 Gaa nihk'it t'ishi'in ts'ą', shik'iinjuhkhit kwaa ji' gaa Shiti' vigwitr'it t'ishi'in ąįį geenjit shik'iinjuhkhit. Ąįį ji' t'ee Gwiti' shizhit t'inchy'aa akwat chan Gwiti' shizhit t'inchy'aa shaakhwandaii eenjit.” 
\p  
\v 39 Chan hee zheegwaazhrąįį nigiihahchyaa gwik'igogwandaii, gaa goovantł'ee tr'ineezhii. 
\p  
\v 40 Jesus chan hee Jordan han gwinjik nineezhii ts'ą' nijin John tr'ookit vats'an chųų dhidlit izhit dhidii.  
\v 41 Lęįį nąįį yats'ą' haajil ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą, “John jyaa deegwahtł'oo gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa t'iizhik, gaa jii dinjii daiinyą' datthak łi'didlii.”  
\v 42 Ąįįts'ą' zhat dinjii gwanlii lęįį nąįį giik'iinjinghit. 
\c 11  
\s1 Lazarus Niindhat 
\p  
\v 1 Dinjii Lazarus oaazhii Bethany kwaiik'it gwizhit gwich'įį ąįį iłts'ik naanaii. Bethany gwizhit t'ee Mary chan ts'ą' veejii Elizabeth haa gwigwich'įį.  
\v 2 (Jii Mary t'ee gwehkįį K'eegwaadhat vakwai' kat gwanzhįh chų' gwinzii vagwaatsan t'inlik ts'ą' dikiighai' haa yach'ąhjik ąįį voondee Lazarus ąįį iłts'ik.)  
\v 3 Ąįį tr'injaa neekwaii t'ee Jesus ts'ą' nideech'igiin'ąįį, “K'eegwaadhat, nijyaa gwilęįį iłts'ik,” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 4 Nijin Jesus jyaa ginyąą gaviitth'ak dąį' jyaa nyąą, “Jii ts'ik haa niheedhaa kwaa t'inchy'aa, gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vich'eegwahdrii gwizhrįh nagwahaatth'aa ąįįts'ą' gwik'iighai' shįį Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidinji' shich'eegwahahdrii.” 
\p  
\v 5 Jesus ąįį Martha chan ts'ą' vijuu Mary, Lazarus nąįį haa eet'iindhan.  
\v 6 Nijin Jesus Lazarus iłts'ik gwinyąą gwiitth'ak dąį', drin neekwaii gwahaadhat gaa nihk'it zhat dhidii.  
\v 7 Ąįįtł'ęę ditsyaa nąįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Judea gwits'eerahoojyaa.” 
\p  
\v 8 “Geech'ǫąąhtan,” vitsyaa nąįį yahnyąą, “Niighit kwaa gwanaa dąį' Judea nąįį kii haa narookhwaa nagoonyąą; chan hee zhat gwits'eehindyaa lee t'iinyąą?” 
\p  
\v 9 Jesus jyaa nyąą, “12 hr. gwizhrįh drin goo'aii, izhit gwizhrįh dinjii vaagweech'in ts'ą' duuyeh gat'aadhak.  
\v 10 Gaa tǫǫ gwiizhit zhit gwa'an neehidik ji' git'eehaadhak, ąįį dinjii vizhit tǫǫ gwanlii geh'an.” 
\p  
\v 11 Jesus jyaa nyąą, “Diijyaa Lazarus naachįį, gaa vats'ą' hihshyaa ts'ą' khakihih'aa.” 
\p  
\v 12 Vitsyaa nąįį t'igiiyahnyąą, “K'eegwaadhat, dhichįį t'inchy'aa ji', veenjit gwinzii neegweheelyaa t'inchy'aa.” ginyąą. 
\p  
\v 13 Gaa Jesus ąįį Lazarus niindhat nyąą t'inyąą, zhyaa dhichįį yahnyąą t'inyąą giiyuunyąą.  
\v 14 Ąįįts'ą' łyaa gwinzii gavaa gwaandak, “Lazarus niindhat t'inchy'aa,  
\v 15 gaa nakhweh'an vaa iidi' kwaa eenjit shoo ihłii shik'injahohkhit eenjit. It'ee vats'ą' tr'ahoojyaa.” 
\p  
\v 16 Thomas (Twin chan oozhii) ąįį ch'izhii Jesus vitsyaa nąįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Geech'ǫąąhtan datthak vaa tr'ahoojyaa, nireheedhaa eenjit.” 
\s1 Jesus, Niindhat Nąįį Khakinlii Tł'ęę Gwandaii Neegooviłtsąįį 
\p  
\v 17 Nijin Jesus k'idik dąį', drin dǫǫ gwanaa dąį' hee giiyaahtsii łee.  
\v 18 Bethany kwaiik'it t'ee Jerusalem gwats'ą' mile neekwaii goo'aii,  
\v 19 ts'ą' Israel lęįį nąįį Mary, Martha, haa goochaa niindhat geenjit gavaatr'igwigwidii 
\p  
\v 20 Nijin Martha ąįį Jesus ahaa gwiintth'ak dąį' dizheh gwats'an yats'ą' chiinzhii, gaa Mary ąįį zhat gwizhit dhidii. 
\p  
\v 21 Martha ąįį Jesus jyaa dahnyąą, “Shik'eegwaadhat, dząą iindi' ji' duuyeh diichaa niighit!  
\v 22 Juk zhat Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa oahkat ji' nik'eegwahahthat gaashandaii.” 
\p  
\v 23 “Nachaa neegweheendaii t'inchy'aa,” Jesus yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 24 “Drin ndaagwąą'ąį' ji' neegweheendaii ąįį gaashandaii,” Martha yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 25 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Shįį t'ee niindhat nąįį khakihlii tł'ęę neegogwandaii neegoovałtsii.  
\v 26 Juu shik'iinjiighit nąįį t'ee nigiindhat ji' gaa neegwigweheendaii giheelyaa. Shik'iinjiighit eenjit khit gweheendaii ts'ą' duuyeh niighit jii nik'ee gwik'iinjinghit?” 
\p  
\v 27 “Aahą' K'eegwaadhat, Christ, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidinji' inlii ts'ą' dząą nankat gwats'ą' hinkhaa naashandaii,” Martha yahnyąą. 
\s1 Jesus Itree 
\p  
\v 28 Ąįįtł'ęę t'ee Martha dizheh nihdineezhii ts'ą' gweentak dijuu Mary oozhrii, “Geech'ǫąąhtan dząą dhidii, ts'ą' nǫh'ya' noonyąą,” jyaa yahnyąą.  
\v 29 Nijin Mary gwaak'įį dąį' khan yats'ą' haazhii.  
\v 30 (Jesus ąįį kwaiik'it gwats'ą' niighit kwaa nijin Martha yąąh'ya' chy'aa tth'aii hee dhidii.)  
\v 31 Nijin ąįį Israel gwich'in yaatr'igwidii nąįį khan chiinzhii giiyąąh'in dąį' giitąįį haajil, tth'ank'it gwats'ą' heekhaa ts'ą' tr'igwiheedii t'ii'in giiyuunyąą. 
\p  
\v 32 Nijin Mary ąįį Jesus ts'ą' tr'iinzhii ts'ą' niyiił'in dąį' yakwai' eeghaii nikiigwiintthaii. “K'eegwaadhat, dząą iindi' ji' duuyeh shachaa niighit!” yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 33 Nijin Jesus, Mary chan ts'ą' tr'igwidii nąįį gwąąh'in ts'ą' adan chan haa tr'igwigwidii.  
\v 34 “Nijin vanǫǫhjik?” goovahnyąą. 
\p “Aanaii ts'ą' gwąąh'in!” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 35 Jesus iintrii. 
\p  
\v 36 Ts'ą' Israel gwich'in nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Deegwahtł'oo yeet'iindhan nǫh'in!” 
\p  
\v 37 Gaa goolat nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Dinjii vandee kwaa gaa haagweech'in neegwiłtsąįį! Lazarus niheedhaa gwits'į' yits'iheenjyaa shrǫǫ?” 
\s1 Lazarus Neegwiindaii 
\p  
\v 38 Chan hee gwintł'oo gitr'ii'ee ts'ą' Jesus yatth'ank'it gwats'ą' haazhii, ąįį tth'ank'it kii zhit gweedii ąįį gwadąįį kii dha'aii.  
\v 39 “Gwadąįį kii gihłeehoh'ąįį!” Jesus gavahnyąą. 
\p Lazarus niindhat ąįį veejii Martha jyaa nyąą, “Juk t'ee drin dǫǫ okhwatsii t'inchy'aa, K'eegwaadhat, vatthąį' tr'ahaatsan.” 
\p  
\v 40 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Gwik'iinjuhkhit ji' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vich'eegwąhndit hǫǫh'yaa nakhwaihnyąą gaanoondaii?” 
\p  
\v 41 Gwadąįį kii gihłeegahaa'aii. Jesus yeedak gwąąh'in ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Shoodǫǫhk'įį geenjit mahsį', Shiti'.  
\v 42 Khit ts'ą' shoodǫǫhk'įį gaashandaii, gaa jii dinjii nąįį dząą giilk'ii geh'an t'ihnyąą, shohǫǫh'e' ąįį shaagiheendaii eenjit.” 
\p  
\v 43 Ąįį jyaa diinyą' tł'ęę gwint'aii khashraa'iintrat ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Lazarus, cheehinkhaii!” \fig none|src="cn01768b.tif" size="span" copy="©1978 David C. Cook Publishing Company" ref="JHN 11.43" \fig* 
\v 44 Ąįį dinjii niindhat chy'aa chiinzhii, vanli', vakwai' haa gwach'aa vanooljik, vinin kat chan gwach'aa t'inchy'aa. “Gwach'aa vakat gihłeehohłii ts'ą' vanoohjii,” Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą. 
\s1 Jesus Tr'ahaahkhwaa Geenjit Geetr'agogwah'in 
\r Matthew 26.1-5; Mark 14.1-2; Luke 22.1-2 
\p  
\v 45 Israel gwich'in lęįį nąįį Mary haa neegihiidal nąįį Jesus deezhik googwąąh'ya', ts'ą' giik'iinjihkhit.  
\v 46 Gaa goolat nąįį Pharisee nąįį ts'ą' neegahoojil ts'ą' Jesus deezhik geegoovaagwaandak.  
\v 47 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee jii Pharisee chan ts'ą' giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį haa Israel gwakhaihkwai' nąįį ts'ą' giginkhe' ąįįtł'ęę jyaa ginyąą. “Deereheelyaa? Gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa lęįį t'ii'in!  
\v 48 Jyąhts'ą' datthak zhyaa tr'ąąh'in ji' juu nąįį datthak giik'iinjiheeghit, ts'ą' Roman gwakhaihkwaii nąįį dząą gwats'ą' giheedaa ts'ą' Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh chan ts'ą' jii nahkat datthak an googwahahtsyaa!” 
\p  
\v 49 Gootee dinjii ch'ihłak, Caiaphas, oaazhii ąįį zhat dąį' ndak khii giinkhih choh nilii ąįį jyaa nyąą, “Gaa deegwii'in gaakhwandaii kwaa t'ohnyąą!  
\v 50 Jii nahkat datthak an gweheelyaa gwits'į' dinjii nąįį eenjit gwizhrįh dinjii ch'ihłak ąįį tr'iiłkhwąįį ji' ts'ąįį gweheezyaa nik'ee gaakhwandaii?”  
\v 51 Zhyaa t'inyąą kwaa gaandaii gaa zhat dąį' ndak khii giinkhih choh ts'ą' Israel gwich'in nąįį eenjit niheedhaa yaandaii t'iiyahnyąą, ąįį  
\v 52 nąįį zhrįh eenjit kwaa gaa Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vigii nąįį, an-nihłik gwa'an gwigwich'įį nąįį ch'ihłak neehahtsyaa eenjit. 
\p  
\v 53 Izhit drin gwats'an t'ee Israel gwakhaihkwaii nąįį Jesus nats'ąą gahaahkhwaa geegiginkhii.  
\v 54 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Jesus gaandaii ts'ą' Judea nahkat gwandah neehidik kwaa, gaa neehoozhii ts'ą' nangwinjir gwa'an kwaiik'it Ephraim gwats'ą' haazhii ts'ą' ditsyaa nąįį haa dhidii. 
\p  
\v 55 Israel gwich'in nąįį Passover it'ee khaiinjii geenigwiindhat, ts'ą' dinjii lęįį nihky'aa nanhtee gwats'an Jerusalem gwats'ą' gahaajil, Passover gwats'ą' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa eenjit shriitr'eedagahaachyaa.  
\v 56 Datthak Jesus keegihi'ik, Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh gwizhit khaihłan nigiinjil ts'ą' nihłaagwaakat, “Veenjit deeyųųhthan? Łyaa duuyeh dząą gwats'ą' hahaii gwich'in, shrǫǫ ohnyąą?” nihłagaanyąą.  
\v 57 Pharisee chan ts'ą' giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį haa juu Jesus nah'ya' ji' geegǫǫndak ginyąą, zheegwaazhrąįį nigiihahchyaa geenjit. 
\c 12  
\s1 Mary, Jesus, Gwanzhįh Gwinzii Vagwaatsan Chų' Yakat T'inlik 
\r Matthew 26.1-5; Mark 14.1-2; Luke 22.1-2 
\p  
\v 1 Passover gwats'ą' drin nihk'iitik gwiizhit Jesus, Bethany kwaiik'it gwats'ą' haazhii, izhit Jesus Lazarus niindhat dąį' ineegwahdaii ąįį zhat gwich'įį.  
\v 2 Izhit giiyeenjit vikeech'iłchy'aa, ts'ą' Martha yeenach'aahtsit, izhit zhat Lazarus vakat ch'ara'aa ts'ą' yaa dhidii.  
\v 3 Ąįįts'ą' Mary ąįį gwanzhįh gwinzii vagwaatsan chų' oonjik ts'ą' Jesus vakwai' kat t'inlik ąįįtł'ęę dikiighai' haa yach'ahjii ąįį yihił'ee geh'an t'iiyah'in. Ąįį vichų' zheh gwizhit datthak neech'iinthaii. 
\p  
\v 4 Jesus vitsyaa ch'ihłak, Judas Iscariot oaazhii ąįįt'ee gwintł'eeyahahchyaa ąįį jyaa nyąą,  
\v 5 “Jaghaii jii gwanzhįh chų' $300. Denarius\f + \fr 12:5 \ft Denarius ch'ihłak t'ee drin ch'ihłak googwitr'it.\f* vit'ii hohłii kwaa ts'ą' neeshraahchy'aa nąįį antł'ohłii kwaa?”  
\v 6 Neeshraahchy'aa nąįį eenjit niinjich'adhat kwaa gaa ch'an'įį nilii t'inyąą. Laraa dhah neeha'ak ts'ą' yats'an ch'an'įį t'inyąą. 
\p  
\v 7 Gaa Jesus jyaa nyąą, “Mary vihłeehiindii! Shireheetsii drin ji' eenjit yit'eehaahchy'aa t'iiyah'in vaanigwiin'ąįį kwaa!  
\v 8 Gweedhaa datthak neeshraahchy'aa nąįį gweheelyaa, gaa shįį ąįį khit geenjit nakhwaa hihdyaa kwaa.” 
\s1 Lazarus Tr'ookhwaa Giindhan 
\p  
\v 9 Jews lęįį nąįį Jesus Bethany dhidii gwinyąą gwigwiitth'ak ts'ą' zhat gwats'ą' gahaajil. Jesus eenjit gwizhrįh kwaa gaa Lazarus chan, ąįįt'ee Jesus yineegwahdaii reh.  
\v 10 Ąįįts'ą' giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį Lazarus chan gahaahkhwaa eenjit gwigwiłtsąįį.  
\v 11 Deezhik veh'an Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį akhagoonyąą ts'ą' dinjii lęįį nąįį teehaajil geh'an Jesus k'injigiighit. 
\s1 Jesus, Jerusalem Nihdeehahkhaii 
\r Matthew 21.1-11; Mark 11.1-11; Luke 19.28-40 
\p  
\v 12 Ąįįtł'ęę gęhdaa drin dinjii lęįį nąįį Jesus Jerusalem gwats'ą' ahaa gwinyąą gwigwiitth'ak eenjit zhat Passover giilk'ii.  
\v 13 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee ts'iivii Palm ąįį vachan kwaii goonjik ts'ą' giidivee haajil, gazhral ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą “Hosanna! Juu K'eegwaadhat voozhri' zhit ahaa ąįį Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vaa oolį'! Israel gwi-King Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vaa oolį'!” \fig none|src="cn01784b.tif" size="span" copy="©1978 David C. Cook Publishing Company" ref="JHN 12.13" \fig* 
\p  
\v 14 Jesus łąįį choh tsal (Donkey) agwąh'ąįį kat daandii, Dęhtły'aa Choh zhit jyaa deegwiinyą' gwik'it: 
\q1  
\v 15 “Zion kwaiik'it gwachoo gwich'in nąįį, noojat shrǫ'! 
\q1 Et'ee nakhwa-King nakhwats'ą' ahaa, łąįį choh tsal (Donkey) kat doodii.” 
\p  
\v 16 Vitsyaa nąįį deegwinyąą t'igwinyąą gaagiindaii kwaa. Gaa nijin Jesus neegwiindaii dąį' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vich'eegwąhndit yintł'eiin'ąįį Dęhtły'aa Choh kat jyaa deegwinyąą, ąįįts'ą' giiyeenjit jyaa diizhik gineegaanjik. \fig none|src="lb00314b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 12.16" \fig* 
\p  
\v 17 Lazarus tth'ank'it gwizhit gwats'an Jesus yineegwahdaii dąį' juu andah t'iizhik nąįį deezhik geegoogwaandak.  
\v 18 Ąįį geenjit t'ee giits'ą' haajil gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa t'iizhik giiyeegwiitth'ak.  
\v 19 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Pharisee nąįį jyaa nihłagaanyąą, “Gooh'in, łyaa gaayiich'arahtsii kwaa! Gooh'in, jii nahkat datthak giitąįį hijyaa!” 
\s1 Greek Gwich'in Nąįį Jesus Tr'ǫǫh'ya' Giiyuunyąą 
\p  
\v 20 Juu Jerusalem gwizhit Passover gwats'ą' haajil ts'ą' khadigigeheejyaa eenjit nąįį tee gwa'an Greek nąįį dilk'ii.  
\v 21 Philip ts'ą' (Bethsaida kwaiik'it Galilee nahkat gwats'an ahaa) nigiinjil ts'ą' jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Jesus tr'ǫǫh'ya' tr'oonyaa.” 
\p  
\v 22 Philip ąįį Andrew ts'ą' haazhii, ts'ą' nihłaa Jesus ts'ą' gahaa'oo ts'ą' Jesus haa googwaandak.  
\v 23 Jesus jyaa goovahnyąą, “Et'ee juk Gwidinji' vich'eegwąhndit vintł'eerehee'aa.  
\v 24 Łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwahaldak! Tł'ooli' tsal naadhak ts'ą' nan zhyaadhak ąįįtł'ęę an ilik gwik'it neet'eehaldhak ts'ą' nihihthaa, an dhidlit ji', tł'ooli' lęįį vats'an haahshii.  
\v 25 Juu dagwandaii zhrįh hił'ee ji', an heelyaa. Juu dagwandaii hił'ee kwaa ji' khit geenjit gwandaii hee'yaa.  
\v 26 Juu sheenjit gwitr'it t'agoh'ya' niindhan ji' shatąįį heekhaa gwizhrįh, shitsyaa heelyaa ts'ą' nijin dhidii shaa heedyaa eenjit. Shiti', juu shaa t'inchy'aa hił'ee t'inchy'aa.” 
\s1 Jesus Tr'ahaahkhwaa Geeginkhii 
\p  
\v 27 “Et'ee łyaa shidrii zhit tr'igwidii dha'aii gaa reh deehihjyaa gǫ'? ‘Shiti', jii kwaii shats'ą' t'agǫǫ'ya' shrǫ'!’ Gaa ąįį geenjit dząą gwats'ą' hoiizhii, khaiinjich'ashahadhat gwahaał'yaa eenjit.  
\v 28 Shiti', Noozhri' hil'ee ąhtsii!” 
\p Ąįįtł'ęę zheekat gwats'an khagiriinkhee, “Hil'ee dhałtsąįį ts'ą' chan jyaa dineehihłyaa.” 
\p  
\v 29 Ąįį zhat dilk'ii nąįį zheekat gwats'an girinkhii gwigwiitth'ak ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą, “Nagoahtan lee t'igwinyąą? Ch'izhii nąįį chan zheekat gwich'in yats'ą' ginkhii t'inyąą!” 
\p  
\v 30 Gaa Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Jii girinkhii goohtth'ak sheenjit t'igwinyąą kwaa gaa nakhwan ąįį nakhweenjit t'igwinyąą.  
\v 31 Et'ee juk jii nankat Ch'aroohahkat Drin nigwiindhat Ch'anky'aa Tr'aanduu kįh dhidii ąįį charahahchyaa gwik'it t'ishi'in shi'in. It'ee neerahoojyaa.  
\v 32 Nijin nankat gwats'an deeshiriłchįį ts'ą' sharoołkhwąįį ji' juu nąįį tthak shats'ą' giheedaa.”  
\v 33 (Nats'ąą khaiinjich'iheedhaa ts'ą' niheedhaa ąįį geegwaandak t'inyąą.) 
\p  
\v 34 Zhat dilk'ii nąįį jyaa ginyąą: “Dęhtły'aa Choh zhit Christ khit geenjit gweheendaii gwinyąą. Nats'ąą Gwidinji' ndak deerahahchyaa deenyąą t'iinyąą? Gwidinji' ąįį juu t'arahnyąą?” 
\p  
\v 35 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą “Tth'aii gwintsal gwizhrįh nakhwaa ch'ahałdrii t'oonchy'aa. Tǫǫ gweheelyaa gwehkįį deekhwa'yaa goo'aii gwik'it t'akhwa'in. Nakhwaa tǫǫ nagwahaadhal gwits'į'. Juu tǫǫ gwizhit dinjii nilii t'ee nijuk ahaa gaaheendaii kwaa geh'an  
\v 36 Tth'aii drin gwanlii dąį' vat'oohchy'aa. Khit naa ch'ahaadrii eenjit.” Jesus jyaa diinyą' ąįįtł'ęę t'oołii neehoozhii ts'ą' goh'it idiildii. 
\s1 Jews Nąįį Gwik'injigiighit Kwaa 
\p  
\v 37 Gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa lęįį gavandah t'iizhik googaa giik'iinjiighit kwaa.  
\v 38 Isaiah, Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Eenjit Ginkhii nilii ąįį jii kwaii łi'didlii heelyaa nyąą: 
\q1 “K'eegwaadhat, juu yik'injiheeghit? 
\q1 Juu yat'aii nah'ya'?” 
\p  
\v 39 Khyų' giik'iinjiighit geh'an Isaiah jii jyaa diinyą': 
\q1  
\v 40 “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa goovaagweech'in kwaa gwiłtsąįį, 
\q1 niinjich'agadhat kwaa gooviłtsąįį, 
\q1 goovaagweheechy'aa kwaa eenjit, 
\q1 googwandaii ninjich'iheedhat kwaa, 
\q1 Duuyeh goots'ą' tr'ihihdal eenjit shats'ą' gihijyaa.” 
\q1  
\v 41 Isaiah, Jesus vich'eegwąhndit gwąąh'ya' geh'an jyąhts'ą' yeeginkhii t'inyąą. 
\p  
\v 42 Zhit dąį' Israel kįh dilk'ii lęįį nąįį giik'iinjiindhat gaadlit gaa Pharisee nąįį anagogwaah'įį, Israel nąįį tr'igiinkhii zheh chagoorahahchyaa, kwaa gwits'į'.  
\v 43 Dinjii deenyąą ąįį gwik'it geedaa ts'ą' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa deenyąą ąįį gwik'it geedaa kwaa. 
\p  
\v 44 Jesus gwint'aii khaginkhee ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Juu shik'injiighit t'ee shįį zhrįh shik'injiighit kwaa gaa juu shihił'e' chan k'injiighit t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 45 Juu shąąh'in t'ee juu shihił'e' chan nah'in t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 46 Jii nankat gava aadrii ihłii ts'ą' gwats'ą' hoiizhii, ąįįts'ą' juu shik'injiighit ji' duuyeh tǫǫ dhidii.  
\v 47 Juu shiginjik diitth'ak gaa gwik'eegwahthat kwaa ji', duuyeh an ałtsii eenjit gwantł'ałchįį. Dinjii an hałtsyaa eenjit nankat gwats'ą' hoiizhii kwaa, gaa dinjii neehałshii eenjit gwizhrįh.  
\v 48 Juu shaa t'inchy'aa kwaa ts'ą' shiginjik diitth'ak kwaa ąįįt'ee an yahahtsyaa veenjit dhidii. Khaiinkǫǫ Drin ndaanąą'ąį' ji' deihnyą' t'ee an yahahtsyaa!  
\v 49 Aahą', jii deihnyą' ąįį shįį zhrįh shats'an t'igwinyąą kwaa gaa Gwiti' shihił'e' ąįį deiinyąą shahnyąą gwik'it giihkhii t'ihnyąą.  
\v 50 Viginjik k'iighai' t'ee khit gwireheendaii. Deihnyą' datthak t'ee Gwiti' deiinyąą shahnyąą gwik'it giihkhii t'ihnyąą.” 
\c 13  
\s1 Jesus, Ditsyaa Nąįį Kwai' K'eech'ąhtryaa 
\p  
\v 1 It'ee Passover ch'arehee'aa gwats'ą' drin nigwiindhat. It'ee Jesus vidrin eenigwiindhat ts'ą' jii nankat gihłeeheekhaa ts'ą' Gwiti' ts'ą' heekhaa gaandaii. Dzaa nankat juu yaa t'iinchy'a' nąįį eet'iinghya' ts'ą' ndaagwąą'ąį' gwats'ą' gooveet'iindhan. 
\p  
\v 2 Jesus ditsyaa nąįį haa khaa neech'aga'aa. Ch'anky'aa Tr'aanduu ąįį Simon Iscariot vidinji' Judas ąįį ch'adąį' hee Jesus gwintł'eehahchyaa gwiłtsąįį.  
\v 3 Jesus ąįį Gwiti' t'aih datthak yintł'eiin'ąįį gaandaii; Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ts'an tr'iinzhii ts'ą' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ts'ą' heekhaa gaandaii.  
\v 4 Ąįįts'ą' Jesus vakaii'aa ts'an ndak nidhikhin, ts'ą' ankhii dagwach'aa gihłeehaalii, ts'ą' dohshroo dazhrak tł'an diłchaa.  
\v 5 Ąįįtł'ęę vizhit neech'araanjii zhit chųų gwizhinjaa ts'ą' ditsyaa nąįį kwai' k'eech'ąhtryaa ąįįtł'ęę ąįį dazhrak tł'an dohshroo haa gooch'ahjii. 
\p  
\v 6 Simon Peter ts'ą' niinzhii, ąįį t'iiyahnyąą, “Shik'eegwaadhat, shakwai' k'eech'ahąhtryaa?” 
\p  
\v 7 Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Juk deeshi'in gaakhwandaii kwaa, gaa nahgwan gaakhwahandaii.” 
\p  
\v 8 Peter t'iiyahnyąą, “Duuyeh, ch'ihłok, gaa shakwai' k'eech'ąhtryaa t'oonchy'aa!” 
\p Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Nakwai' k'eech'ałtryaa kwaa ji', shitsyaa neenilyaa kwaa t'oonchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 9 Simon Peter t'iiyahnyąą, “Shik'eegwaadhat, shakwai' zhrįh k'eech'ohtryaa shrǫ'! Akwat, shanli' chan ts'ą' shiki' haa chan k'eech'ąhtryaa!” 
\p  
\v 10 Jesus t'inyąą, “Juu gwinzii dik'eech'aahtryaa t'ee vakat shrąįh kwaa ts'ą' dik'ineech'aatryaa t'ee vakat shrąįh kwaa ts'ą' dik'ineehaatryaa gwat'aahchy'aa kwaa, vakwai' zhrįh. Datthak nakhwakat shrąįh kwaa nakhwatee ch'ihłak zhrįh.”  
\v 11 Jesus ch'adąį' hee gootee juu gwintł'eeyahahchyaa gaandaii, ąįį geh'an jyaa nyąą, “Datthak nakhwakat shrąįh kwaa gaa ch'ihłak zhrįh.” 
\p  
\v 12 Datthak gookwai' k'eech'ąhtryaa tł'ęę Jesus ankhii dagwach'aa neenaazhii ts'ą' vakaii'aa ts'ą' neenakhwadii. “At'ohju' deenakhwiilik deeshi'in nik'ee gaakhwandaii?” gavahnyąą.  
\v 13 “Shigeech'ǫąąhtan chan ts'ą' Shik'eegwaadhat shohnyąą, ąįįt'ee gwinzii t'oohnyąą, ąįį adan t'ihchy'aa.  
\v 14 Nakhwak'eegwaadhat, nakhwageech'ǫąąhtan ihłii, ts'ą' at'ohju' nakhwakwai' k'eech'ałtryaa. Nakhwan chan, nihłakwai' k'eech'ohtryaa.  
\v 15 Shik'it t'akhwa'yaa eenjit t'ishi'in, nakhweenjit deeshizhik gwik'it t'akhwa'yaa eenjit.  
\v 16 Łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwahaldak, slaves ąįį dinjii yits'ą' k'eegwaadhat ąįį andaa hil'ee kwaa; dinjii hil'e' ąįį juu yihił'e' andaa veegoo'aii kwaa.  
\v 17 It'ee łi'didlii haa khwandaii: izhit gwik'it t'akhwa'in ji' gwintł'oo shoohohłyaa!” 
\p  
\v 18 “Datthak nakhweegihkhii t'ihnyąą kwaa; ąįį juu nąįį teegǫǫłjik nąįį haashandaii. Gaa jii Dęhtły'aa Choh zhit deegwiinyą' gwik'it t'igiheenjyaa eenjit, ‘Dinjii juu shishii in'al t'ee shits'į' t'iheechy'aa.’  
\v 19 Jii gwik'it t'igweheenjyaa gwehkįį juk nakhwaagwaldak t'ihnyąą, ąįįts'ą' nijin gwik'it t'igwiizhik ‘Juu Ihłii Ąįį Ihłii!’ gwik'iinjuhohkhit geenjit.  
\v 20 Jii t'ee łi'didlii: juu vats'ą' ch'ahooł'e' ąįį k'injiighit ąįįt'ee shik'iinjiighit, ąįį juu shik'iinjiighit, t'ee juu shihił'e' ąįį k'injiighit.” \fig none|src="lb00320b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 13.20" \fig* 
\s1 Jesus Gwintł'eesharahahchyaa Nyąą 
\r Matthew 26.20-25; Mark 14.17-21; Luke 22.21-23 
\p  
\v 21 Jesus jyaa diinyą', ąįįtł'ęę łyaa tr'igwidii, ts'ą' gwinzii akǫǫ t'agoovahnyąą: “Łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwaldak: nakhwatee ch'ihłak gwintł'eeshahahchyaa.” 
\p  
\v 22 Datthak nihłitee googwąąh'in ts'ą' juu t'ahnyąą ąįį gaagiindaii kwaa.  
\v 23 Vitsyaa nąįį tee juu Jesus yeet'iindhan ąįį yeeghaii dhidii.  
\v 24 Ąįį dinjii ąįį Simon Peter t'iiyahnyąą, “Juu t'ahnyąą ąįį geenjit oahkat lee?” 
\p  
\v 25 Ąįį dinjii Jesus eeghaii naadii ts'ą' yuahkat, “Shik'eegwaadhat, juu t'aiinyąą?” 
\p  
\v 26 Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Łųhchy'aa teehałchaa ts'ą' vintł'eehałchaa, ąįį dinjii t'aihnyąą.” Ąįįts'ą' t'ee łųhchy'aa oonjik ts'ą' teeyahtsit ts'ą' Simon Iscariot viinji' Judas intł'eeyahtsit  
\v 27 Judas łųhchy'aa oonjik googwahkhan Satan vizhit diindhat. Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Khan deehini'yaa goo'aii gwik'it t'ini'in!”  
\v 28 Ąįį vakaii'aa ts'ą' yaadilk'ii nąįį ch'ihłak gaa Judas jaghaii t'inyąą giiyaandaii kwaa.  
\v 29 Judas ąįį laraa k'ąąhtii nilii ts'ą' Jesus vitsyaa lat nąįį ch'ara'aa drin eenjit ch'oiinkwat yahnyąą giiyuunyąą, ąįį akwaa ji' neeshraahchy'aa nąįį ts'iinyąą yahnyąą giiyuunyąą. 
\p  
\v 30 Khaa gwanlii ts'ą' Judas łųhchy'aa oonjik tł'ęę zhat cheehoozhii. 
\s1 Ch'eet'igwiniindhan Nihłeenjit Khwa'įį 
\p  
\v 31 Judas cheehoozhii ąįįtł'ęę, Jesus jyaa nyąą, “It'ee Gwidinji' vich'eegwahdrii gwizhrįh nagwaatth'at. It'ee Gwidinji' vik'iighai' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vich'eegwahdrii gwizhrįh nagwaatth'at.  
\v 32 Ąįįts'ą' vik'iighai' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vich'eegwahdrii gwizhrįh nagwaatth'at ji', zhazhat Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa adakhai' Gwidinji' vich'eegwahdrii gwizhrįh nigwehee'aa.  
\v 33 Shigii nąįį, it'ee niighit kwaa gwizhrįh nakhwaa t'ihihchy'aa. Shinkeegahoo'yaa gaa Jews nąįį deegavaiinyą' juk nakhwaagwaldak, ‘Nijuk hihshyaa duuyeh gwats'ą' hohjyaa.’  
\v 34 Jii t'ee juk gwizhrįh nakhwaa gwahaldak jyaa khwa'in nakhwaihnyąą, nakhwatee googwąąnchy'aa ts'ą' nihłeenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan khwa'įį. Nakhweenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan shi'įį, ts'ą' nakhwan chan nihłeenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan khwa'įį.  
\v 35 Ch'eet'igwiniindhan nihłeenjit khwa'įį ji', juu nąįį datthak shitsyaa ǫhłįį nakhwaaheendaii.” 
\s1 Niighit Kwaa Peter, Shaanandaii Kwaa Hinjyaa 
\r Matthew 26.31-35; Mark 14.27-31; Luke 22.31-34 
\p  
\v 36 “K'eegwaadhat, nijin gwats'ą' hiinkhaii?”, Simon Peter yahnyąą. “Nijin gwats'ą' hihshyaa duuyeh gwats'ą' hinkhaii t'oonchy'aa,” Jesus yahnyąą, “Gaa nahgwan ji' hee shatąįį hinkhaa t'oonchy'aa.” nyąą. 
\p  
\v 37 “K'eegwaadhat, jaghaii juk naahihshyaa kwaa gǫ'?” Peter nyąą. “Neenjit nihihthaa ji' gaa,” Peter yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 38 Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Łyaa sheenjit nihiindhaa ji' gaa lee t'iinyąą? Łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwahaldak: vanh rooster khakeehee'aa gwehkįį tik łąą shaanandaii kwaa hinjyaa t'oonchy'aa.” 
\c 14  
\s1 Jesus Vik'iighai' Gwiti' Vats'ą' Tr'iheedaa 
\p  
\v 1 “Nakhwadrii zhit tr'agohdii ts'ą' nakhweenjit goozųų shrǫ'!” Jesus gavahnyąą. “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vik'injuhkhit, ts'ą' shįį chan shik'iinjuhkhit.  
\v 2 Shiti' vizheh gwizhit gwintsii, ts'ą' izhit nakhweenjit shrigwihihłyaa. Jyąhts'ą' nakhwadivee goo'aii kwaa ji' duuyeh jyaa nakhwaihnyąą.  
\v 3 Ąįįts'ą' hoiizhii ąįįtł'ęę izhit nakhweenjit shrigwiilik ąįįtł'ęę, oo'ee neehihdyaa ts'ą' adahaa nakhwahaalchyaa, nijin t'ihchy'aa izhit shaa t'ahohchy'aa eenjit.  
\v 4 Nijin gwats'ą' hihshyaa ąįį nats'ąą gwats'ą' hohdaa gaakhwandaii.” 
\p  
\v 5 Thomas jyaa yahnyąą, “K'eegwaadhat, nijin gwats'ą' hinkhaa t'iinyąą, gaagwiindaii kwaa. Nats'ąą gaagweheendaii?” 
\p  
\v 6 Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Shik'iighai' shatąįį gwats'ą' hohdaa t'igwinyąą, łi'didlii ihłii, gwandaii ihłii; shik'iighai' gwizhrįh dinjii Gwiti' ts'ą' niheehaa goo'aii.  
\v 7 It'ee shaakhwandaii akwat Shiti' chan vaakhwahandaii ts'ą' juk gwats'an vaakhwandaii hohłyaa, nǫh'ya' t'inchy'aa.” Jesus gavahnyąą 
\p  
\v 8 Philip jyaa yahnyąą, “K'eegwaadhat, Gwiti' diits'ą' agwąąhkįį; ąįį gwizhrįh gwit'eegwaahchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 9 Jesus jyaa nyąą, “Łyaa niighyuk nakhwaa t'ihchy'aa gwiizhit tth'aii shaakhwandaii kwaa Philip? Juu shaa'ya' t'ee gwiti' chan nah'ya' t'oonchy'aa. Jaghaii gwiizhit ‘Gwiti' diits'ą' agwahch'in!’ diinyąą?  
\v 10 Gwiti' vizhit t'ihchy'aa ts'ą' Gwiti' shizhit t'inchy'aa ąįį nik'ee gwik'iinjinghit Philip? Jidii ginjik nakhwats'an dhałtsąįį t'ee shats'an t'igwinyąą kwaa. Gwiti' shizhit t'inchy'aa ąįį digwitr'it t'agwah'in t'igwinyąą.  
\v 11 Gwiti' vizhit t'ihchy'aa ts'ą' Gwiti' shizhit t'inchy'aa ąįį gwik'iinjuhkhit. Akwaa ji', gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa t'agwał'in gǫǫh'ya' gwik'iighai' gwik'iinjuhkhit.  
\v 12 Łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwahaldak, juu shik'iinjiighit ąįį chan jidii gwitr'it t'agwał'ya' gwik'it t'ihee'yaa. Aahą', shandaa gaa gwitr'it t'agwahah'yaa. Shįį ąįį Gwiti' vats'ą' hihshyaa geh'an.  
\v 13 Ąįįts'ą' jidii shoozhri' zhit ach'oohkat datthak gwik'it gweheelyaa gwahałtsyaa. Gwidinji' vik'iighai' Gwiti' vich'eegwahdrii gwigweheechy'aa eenjit.  
\v 14 Shoozhri' zhit jidii ach'oohkat, nakhwak'it shi'yaa.” 
\s1 Jesus, Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą Goots'ą' Hah'aa Goovahnyąą 
\p  
\v 15 “Sheenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan khwa'įį ji', Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa shiginjik k'eegohohthat t'akhwa'in.  
\v 16-17 Gwiti' nakhweenjit oohaałkat ts'ą' nakhwats'eheenjyaa nakhwats'ą' niheehaa, ąįįt'ee Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą łi'didlii t'arahnyąą. Ąįį khit ts'ą' nakhwaaheelyaa. Jii nankat dinjii nąįį an-giihaa'aa, giiyąąh'in kwaa ts'ą' giiyaandaii kwaa geh'an. Gaa nakhwan'ąįį vaakhwandaii. Juk nakhwaa t'inchy'aa ts'ą' nakhwazhit t'iheechy'aa. 
\p  
\v 18 “Duuyeh akhanahoihnyąą; nakhwats'ą' neehihdyaa.  
\v 19 It'ee niighit kwaa jii nankat gihłeehihshyaa gaa khit nakhwaahihłyaa, ts'ą' chan neegwihįhdaii ts'ą' nakhwan chan neegohǫhdaii t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 20 Izhit drin ji' Gwiti' vizhit t'ihchy'aa ts'ą' nakhwan chan shizhit t'ohchy'aa, ts'ą' nakhwazhit t'ihchy'aa gwik'eehoondal t'oonchy'aa. 
\p  
\v 21 “Juu ch'iitth'ak ts'ą' shik'eegwahthat, ąįįt'ee sheenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan di'įį. Juu sheenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan di'įį t'ee Shiti' chan yeenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan di'įį. Shįį chan veenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan shi'yaa ts'ą' vats'ą' adagwahaalkyaa.” 
\p  
\v 22 Judas Iscariot ąįį kwaa gaa ch'izhii Judas ąįį jyaa yahnyąą, “K'eegwaadhat, jaghaii diits'ą' adagwahaankyaa gwiizhit jii nankat ąįį kwaa?” 
\p  
\v 23 Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Juu sheenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan di'įį t'ee shiginjik k'eegwahahthat. Shiti' chan yeenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan hee'yaa, ts'ą' Shiti', shįį haa vats'ą' nirehee'al ts'ą' vizhit t'igweheechy'aa.  
\v 24 Juu sheenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan di'įį kwaa t'ee duuyeh shiginjik k'eegwahthat. Jii jyaa danakhwaihnyąą t'ee shats'an t'inchy'aa kwaa gaa Gwiti' shihił'e' vats'an t'igwinyąą. 
\p  
\v 25 “Tth'aii nakhwaa dhiidii dąį' jii kwaii nakhwaagwaldak t'ihnyąą.  
\v 26 Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą gwits'inyaa nilii ts'ą' shoozhri' zhit Gwiti' yahah'aa ąįį jidii datthak geegavąąhtan ts'ą' deenakhwaiinyą' datthak gineehoondaii nakhwahahtsyaa. 
\p  
\v 27 “Tsinehdan nakhwaa akhoohįįhjyaa; shats'an tsinehdan nakhwantł'eehihłyaa. Ąįį tsinehdan jii nankat duuyeh gwintł'eeyah'ąįį t'arahnyąą gaa shįį ąįį ts'anhan'yaa eenjit nintł'eehih'aa. Tr'agohdii ts'ą' nakhwayinji' zhit goozųų shrǫ', noojat shrǫ'.  
\v 28 Jii jyaa nakhwaiinyą' shoodǫǫhk'į', ‘Neehihdyaa gaa nakhwats'eehihdyaa.’ Sheet'ǫhthan ji', Gwiti' vits'eehihdyaa geenjit shoohohłyaa, shandaa veegoo'aii geh'an.  
\v 29 Jii deegweheenjyaa diinyą' ąįį gwik'it gweheelyaa gwats'ą' nakhwaagwaldak t'ihnyąą, gwik'it goodlit ji' gwik'iinjuhohkhit geenjit.  
\v 30 It'ee nahgwan gwizhrįh nakhwaa neegihihjyaa. Jii nankat gwizhrįh gwakhaihkwaii choh ahaa. Shandaa t'aih di'įį kwaa.  
\v 31 Gaa jii nankat dinjii nąįį datthak Gwiti' veet'iihthan gaageheendaii gwizhrįh; ąįį geh'an jidii doo'ya' shoonyąą datthak gwik'it t'ishi'in shi'in. 
\p “It'ee neerahoojyaa.” 
\c 15  
\s1 Jesus, Gwanzhįh Vakat Gwąąhshii K'it T'inchy'aa 
\p  
\v 1 “Shįį t'ee łyaa gwanzhįh vakat gwąąhshii t'ihchy'aa, ąįįts'ą' Shiti' chan gwanzhįh nahshii nilii. \fig none|src="hk00110b.tif" size="col" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 15.1" \fig* 
\v 2 Jidii shakat gwanzhįh dachan gwinzii nahshii kwaa t'ee gihłeehaht'aa, jidii shakat gwinzii vakat gwąąhshii t'ee gwinzii k'ąąhtii ts'ą' shriiyuunyąą ąįįt'ee vakat gwanzhįh lęįį neehaanzhii eenjit.  
\v 3 Gwandak nizįį eenakhwaagwadhaldak ąįį haa ch'adąį' hee shroodiinyąą dhoodlit t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 4 Khit shaa ǫhłįį ts'ą' shįį chan khit nakhwaa hihłyaa, gwanzhįh dachan ch'ihłak duuyeh adakhai' gwąąhshii. Vakat gwanzhįh nahshii, vadachan lęįį khaihłok nahshii ji' gwizhrįh. Izhit gwik'it shaa ǫhłįį ji' gwizhrįh nakhwats'an gwahąąhshįį k'it t'igwehee'yaa. 
\p  
\v 5 “Jak vakat nahshii ihłii, nakhwan chan jak t'an ǫhłįį. Juu shaa nilii t'ee vaa ihłii ts'ą' vats'an gwąąhshii; shehdan ji' duuyeh.  
\v 6 Juu shaa nilii kwaa t'ee charahahchyaa, jak dachan akharoonyąą ts'ą' dhagaii gwik'it; ąįį k'it t'inchy'aa jak dachan t'ee khaihłan nirilii ts'ą' kǫ' zhit tr'ahk'an t'inchy'aa.  
\v 7 Shiginjik ohtą' ts'ą' shaa ǫhłįį ji', jidii ach'oohkat datthak nakhwats'an hałtsyaa.  
\v 8 Jyąhts'ą' t'ee Shiti' vich'eegwahdrii gwigweech'in t'agwarahnyąą, gwintł'oo nakhwats'an gwąąhshii, jyąhts'ą' t'ee shitsyaa hohłyaa.  
\v 9 Shiti' sheet'iindhan gwik'it shįį chan nakhweenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan shi'įį. Shich'eet'igwiniindhan zhit gǫhdaii.  
\v 10 Shiginjik k'eegohthat ji', shich'eet'igwiniindhan zhit t'ahohchy'aa. Shiti' viginjik k'eegwałthat ts'ą' vee ch'eet'igwiniindhan zhit t'ihchy'aa gwik'it. 
\p  
\v 11 “Sheeshroonchy'aa nakhwazhit t'iheechy'aa ts'ą' nakhwazhit ch'eeshroonchy'aa deedahaan'ai' eenjit.  
\v 12 Shiginjik zhit jyaa digwinyąą gwik'it t'ohchy'aa, nihłeet'oohthan, nakhweet'iindhan gwik'it.  
\v 13 Dinjii dijyaa, nąįį haa eenjit oo'an dahaachyaa t'ee łyaa vee ch'eet'igwiniindhan nitsii t'arahnyąą.  
\v 14 Shiginjik k'it ohdaa ji' shijyaa hohłyaa.  
\v 15 Et'ee chan duuyeh dinjii vitsyaa yeetr'agwah'in neehanzhok k'it t'anakhwahał'yaa kwaa, ąįį ch'itsyaa dee'in t'ii'in yaaheendaii kwaa eh'an. Shijyaa ąįį nakhwahaihjyaa, jidii Shiti' vats'an gwiitth'ak datthak geenakhwaagwaldak geh'an.  
\v 16 Shįį ąįį gwitee tr'ashǫǫhchįį kwaa gaa shįį ąįį gwitee tr'anakhwaałchįį ts'ą' nakhwats'an gwanzhįh haahshii. Ąįį gwanzhįh khit ts'ą' gweheendaii. Ąįįts'ą' shoozhri' zhit jidii ach'oohkat Gwiti' nats'an yahahtsyaa t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 17 Izhit geenjit jii jyaa danakhwahihjyaa, nihłeenjit ch'eet'igwiniindhan khwa'įį.” 
\s1 Jii Nankat Jesus Vitsyaa Giitr'ii'ee 
\p  
\v 18 “Juu nan dha'aii ąįį nitr'ii'ee ji', shįį tr'ookit sheet'igiinghya' kwaa jyaa gineehandaii yuu.  
\v 19 Jii nankat ts'an inlii ji', vats'an iinlii ts'ą' geh'an neet'iheenghyaa. Gaa shįį ąįį jii nankat gwats'an gwitee tr'anąąłchįį ts'ą' jii nankat gwats'an iinlii kwaa. Ąįį geh'an jii nankat nitr'ii'ee t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 20 Jii deenakhwaiinyą' gineehoondaii yuu, ‘Dinjii vitsyaa yeetr'agwah'in ts'ą' neeyahanzhok ąįį yandaa ts'ą' veegoo'aii kwaa t'oonchy'aa.’ Khaiinjich'ishiriłthat ji', nakhwan chan gwik'it t'ahoh'yaa. Shiginjik k'eegwigwiłthat ji', nakhwaginjik chan k'eegogwahahthat t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 21 Gaa shats'an ǫhłįį geh'an jyaa nakhwagahah'yaa; juu shihił'e' ąįį gaagiindaii kwaa geh'an.  
\v 22 Dząą gwats'ą' hoiizhii ts'ą' goots'ą' giihkhe'. Akwaa ji' duuyeh datr'agogwaanduu gwizhrįh nagogwa'aii, ąįį geh'an datr'agogwaanduu eenjit deegiheenjyaa gaa gaagiindaii kwaa.  
\v 23 Juu sheet'iindhan kwaa chan Shiti' eet'iindhan kwaa t'oonchy'aa.  
\v 24 Gooteegwitr'it t'agwał'ya' kwaa ji' duuyeh datr'agogwaanduu oo'an gwigwihilii, izhit duuyeh gaa t'igwee'ya' kwaa t'oonchy'aa izhit geh'an deeshi'ya' googwąąh'ya' ts'ą' Shiti' shįį haa diitr'igii'ee.  
\v 25 Gaa jii łyaa gwik'it t'igweheenjyaa goo'aii, goo-law zhit deegwinyąą gwik'it gweheelyaa eenjit, ‘geenjit gwakwaa shitr'ii'ee,’ 
\p  
\v 26 “Gwits'inyaa k'eeheedik, ąįįt'ee Gwiti' vats'an Ch'anky'aa łi'didlii nilii. Gwiti' vats'an nakhwats'ą' nihih'aa ts'ą' sheegwahaandak.  
\v 27 Ąįįts'ą' nakhwan chan, sheegohoondak tr'ookit dąį' gwats'an shaa ǫhłįį geh'an.” 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 “Teehohdaa gwits'į' jii kwaii naagwaldak t'ihnyąą.  
\v 2 Israel gwich'in nąįį ditr'igiinkhii zheh gwats'an kwaii cheenagahahchyaa. Ąįįts'ą' juu nęhdaa tr'igwiin'ąįį chan Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vaa ihłii shi'in heenghyaa ąįį chan gwats'ą' gweedhaa.  
\v 3 Shįį akwat Gwiti' haagiindaii kwaa geh'an jii kwaii jyaa danagahah'yaa.  
\v 4 Gaa nijin jii kwaii jyaa danahah'yaa nigwiindhat ji' gaanahandaii ts'ą' naagwaldak chy'aa gineehandaii eenjit. Tr'ookit naa iidi' dąį' jii kwaii geenaagwaldak kwaa.” 
\s1 Nats'ąą Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą Tr'agwah'in 
\p  
\v 5 “Juk juu shihił'e' ąįį vits'eehihdyaa; gaa nakhwatee ch'ihłak gaa jii shǫąąhkat kwaa, ‘Nijin gwats'ą' hinkhaa?’  
\v 6 It'ee nakhwaagwaldak, ts'ą' nakhwadrii zhit tr'igwidii dha'aii.  
\v 7 Gaa jii t'ee łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwaldak: hoiizhii ji' gwizhrįh nakhwadiveegweheezyaa. hoiizhii kwaa ji', Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą gwits'inyaa duuyeh nakhwats'ą' hahaii. Gaa shįį hoiizhii ji' t'ee nakhwats'ą' nahałchyaa.  
\v 8 Ąįįts'ą' nijin k'idik ji', jii nankat gwidinjii nąįį gootr'agwaanduu gwiizųų t'igii'in gaagavahąhdaii, ąįįts'ą' nats'ąą gootr'agwaanduu gweheezyaa chan gaagavahąhdaii, nats'ąą neegeheezhii akwat goorahahkat drin nigweheedhaa chan eenjit gaagavahąhdaii.  
\v 9 Shik'iinjigiighit kwaa geh'an gootr'agwaanduu gwanlii ąįį giizųų, ts'ą'  
\v 10 jidii gwinzii ginyąą chan zhyaa t'iginyąą, Gwiti' vats'ą' hihshyaa ts'ą' neeshahǫǫ'yaa kwaa geh'an.  
\v 11 Ts'ą' Ch'aroohahkat Drin geenjit chan, jii nankat Ch'anky'aa Tr'aanduu gwats'ą' k'eegwaadhat, ch'adąį' hee gwizhrįh narąhchįį. 
\p  
\v 12 “Łyaa tth'aii gwinlęįį eenjit nakhwaagwahaldak gaa tr'ihkhit lęįį ts'ą' gineehoondaii kwaa.  
\v 13 Gaa nijin Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą łi'didlii nilii k'idik ji' łi'didlii zhit gwizhrįh t'ahohchy'aa. Adan zhrįh vats'an t'igwinyąą kwaa gaa jidii gwehkįį gwiitth'ak akwat yeendaa deegweheenjyaa kwaii geegwahaandak.  
\v 14 Deenakhwaiinyą' datthak geenakhwaaneegwahaandak jyąhts'ą' t'ee ch'agwąhdit shintł'eegwehee'aa.  
\v 15 Jidii Shiti' vats'an nilii jii datthak chan shats'an; ąįį geh'an t'ee Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą jidii vintł'eegwiriin'ąįį datthak geenakhwaaneegwahaandak t'oonchy'aa.” 
\s1 Tr'igwidii ts'ą' Shoo Ginlii 
\p  
\v 16 “It'ee nahgwan chan neeshahǫǫ'yaa kwaa; ąįįtł'ęę gwats'an nahgwan chan neeshahǫǫ'yaa.” 
\p  
\v 17 Vitsyaa lat nąįį jyaa nihłagaanyąą, “Deiinyąą t'inyąą li'? Jyaa diinahnyąą, ‘It'ee nahgwan chan neeshahǫǫ'yaa kwaa ts'ą' ąįįtł'ęę gwats'an nahgwan chan neeshahǫǫ'yaa.’ Jii chan jyaa nyąą, ‘Gwiti' vats'ą' hihshyaa geh'an.’” 
\p  
\v 18 “‘Jii nahgwan it'ee,’ nyąą ąįį deenyąą t'inyąą?” Nihłagaanyąą, “Jidii eeginkhii t'inyąą vaagwiindaii kwaa!” ginyąą. 
\p  
\v 19 Jesus ąįį giiyuuhkat giindhan gavaandaii ts'ą' jyaa gavahnyąą, “Jyaa nakhwaiinyą', ‘It'ee nahgwan chan neeshahǫǫ'yaa kwaa ąįįtł'ęę gwats'an nahgwan chan neeshahǫǫ'yaa.’ Jii geenjit nihłookat lee t'ohnyąą?  
\v 20 Jii t'ee łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwahaldak, hohtree ts'ą' tr'agohohdii, gaa jii nankat gwich'in nąįį shik'injiighit kwaa nąįį geenjit shoo heelyaa, tr'agohohdii gaa shoo ąįį neeheelyaa.  
\v 21 Nijin tr'injaa tr'iinin haa iłts'ik dąį' khaiinjich'iighit ts'ą' vaa shroonchy'aa kwaa. Gaa nijin tr'iinin igwilik ąįįtł'ęę khaiinjich'iighit chy'aa ganaandee, vigii nankat niinzhii eenjit shoo nilii geh'an.  
\v 22 Ąįį geh'an juk tr'agohdii ts'ą' nakhwaa shroonchy'aa kwaa t'oonchy'aa, gaa chan neenakhwahaal'yaa ts'ą' nakhwadrii zhit shoo neehee'aa, ąįį shoo t'ee duuyeh nakhwałeeraha'aii t'inchy'aa. 
\p  
\v 23 Izhit zhat drin nigwiindhat ji' shahohkat kwaa. Łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwahaldak, shoozhri' zhit Gwiti' jidii eenjit oohkat nakhwats'an hahtsyaa t'inchy'aa.  
\v 24 Gwehkįį shoozhri' zhit tth'aii ch'oohkat kwaa akwat: jidii ach'oohkat ąįį nik'eegwahaadhat t'oonchy'aa, shoh nakhwazhit deedahaa'aii t'oonchy'aa.” 
\s1 Jii Nankat Gwatr'agwaanduu Gaayiigwiłtsąįį 
\p  
\v 25 “Jii kwaii t'ee gwandak zhit geenakhwaagwaldak t'ihnyąą. Gaa zhat nigwiindhat ji' duuyeh gwandak zhit nakhwaagwaldak, gaa juk Gwiti' gwinzii nakhwąnin ts'ą' veegihihkhyaa.  
\v 26 Izhit drin nigwiindhat ji' shoozhri' zhit oohohkat; nakhweenjit oohaałkat t'ihnyąą kwaa,  
\v 27 Gwiti' nakhweet'iindhan geh'an. Sheet'ǫhthan akwat Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vats'an ihshyaa ąįį gwik'iinjuhkhit geh'an nakhweet'iindhan.  
\v 28 Gwiti' vats'an ihshyaa ts'ą' nankat gwats'ą' hoiizhii; ąįįts'ą' it'ee nankat gihłeehihdyaa ts'ą' Gwiti' vits'eehihdyaa.” 
\p  
\v 29 Ąįįts'ą' vitsyaa nąįį jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Gwąąh'in, gwandak zhit nakwaa gaa gwinzii diinin ts'ą' diinaa goondak.  
\v 30 Juk it'ee jidii datthak gaanandaii gwik'igwaanjik; ts'ą' naroahkat gaa gwit'eegwaahchy'aa kwaa łee. Jii geh'an Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa ts'an tr'iinzhii gwik'injiriighit.” 
\p  
\v 31 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą: “It'ee shik'iinjuhkhit?  
\v 32 Ch'adąį' hee zhat nigwiindhat, shrihtee hohdaa ts'ą' nakhwazheh gwits'eehohdaa ts'ą' shįį zhrįh hihdyaa. Gaa shahzhrįh hihdyaa kwaa ts'ą' Gwiti' shaa t'inchy'aa geh'an.  
\v 33 Shaa tsinehdan hohłyaa geh'an nakhwaagwaldak t'ihnyąą. Jii nankat gogwantrii datthak gahǫǫh'yaa. Gaa nihk'it nakhwaa shroonchy'aa! Jii nankat gaayiidhałtsąįį!” 
\c 17  
\s1 Jesus, Ditsyaa Nąįį Eenjit Khadigiinjii 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus jyaa diinyą' ąįįtł'ęę zheekat k'iidak gwąąh'in ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Shiti', it'ee zhat nigwiindhat. Nidinji' nich'eegwahdrii vintł'eiin'ąįį, ąįįts'ą' Gwidinji' nich'eegwahdrii nintł'ineehee'aa eenjit.  
\v 2 Dinjii datthak teegwahąhdal eenjit t'aih vintł'eiin'ąįį, ts'ą' juu yaanilii nąįį gwandaii ndaanąą'ąį' kwaa teeheelyaa eenjit.  
\v 3 Jii jyąhts'ą' t'ee gwandaii ndaanąą'ąį' kwaa khwa'įį: Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa łi'didlii ch'ihłak zhrįh inlii, ts'ą' Jesus Christ, khadhoo'ee ąįį juu nąįį datthak goovaaheendaii eenjit.  
\v 4 Gwitr'it shintł'eegwin'ąįį datthak gęhdaa tr'aałjik ts'ą' jyąhts'ą' t'ee nich'eegwahdrii nankat neenjit googwahaałkyaa.  
\v 5 Gwiti' neeghaih ch'eegwahdrii shintł'eegwiin'ąįį, jii nan goodlit gwats'ą' ch'eegwahdrii nan, shįį haa tr'ii'įį ąįį reh. 
\p  
\v 6 “Dinjii nankat gwats'an oodhiinjik ts'ą' shintł'eegoovinlii, ąįį nąįį ts'ą' neegiihkhe'. Nats'an giinlii, ts'ą' shintł'eegaviinlii. Niginjik k'eegwigwiłthat,  
\v 7 ąįįts'ą' juk jidii shintł'eegwiinlii datthak nats'an t'inchy'aa gaagiindaii.  
\v 8 Jidii niginjik shintł'eiin'ąįį datthak goovintł'eiilii, ts'ą' giik'iinjiighit nats'an tr'iizhii ąįį łi'deegwidlii gaagiindaii, ts'ą' shahooh'e' gwik'iinjigiighit. 
\p  
\v 9 “Gooveenjit khagidihjii, juu nits'į' t'inchy'aa nąįį eenjit khagidihjii kwaa, gaa juu shintł'eiinlii nąįį eenjit khagidihjii, nats'an giinlii geh'an.  
\v 10 Juu shats'an nilii nąįį nats'an giinlii, ts'ą' juu nats'an nilii nąįį shats'an giinlii. Ąįįts'ą' gooveh'an ch'eegwahdrii shats'an goodlit.  
\v 11 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee nats'ą' hihshyaa, it'ee nankat gihłeehihdyaa, gaa geedan ąįį nankat gahaaky'aa. Gwiti' Shroodiinyąą Noozhri' zhit t'aih ni'įį haa gavoiintą', ąįį Noozhri' shintł'eiin'ąįį reh, nan shįį haa ch'ihłak tr'iinlii gwik'it ch'ihłak giheelyaa eenjit.  
\v 12 Gavaa iindi' dąį', Noozhri' zhit t'aih haa gook'aałti', ąįį noozhri' shintł'eiin'ąįį reh. Gook'aałti', ts'ą' teegahaajil kwaa, dinjii ch'ihłak zhrįh teehaazhii. Ąįįt'ee Dęhtły'aa zhit deegweheenjyaa goo'aii ąįį gwik'it t'igweheenjyaa eenjit.  
\v 13 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee nats'ą' hihshyaa, gaa jii nankat tth'aii dhiindii gwiizhit jyaa dihnyąą t'ihnyąą, goodrii zhit shoh deedahaan'ai' eenjit.  
\v 14 Niginjik nankat gavintł'eiinlii ts'ą' lęįį nąįį gaveet'iindhan kwaa ji', nahkat gwats'an giinlii kwaa geh'an, shįį chan nankat gwats'an ihłii kwaa gwik'it.  
\v 15 Nankat gihłeegavahiinlyaa eenjit t'ihnyąą kwaa, gaa Ch'anky'aa Tr'aanduu ts'į' gook'ąąhtii.  
\v 16 Nankat gwats'an ihłii kwaa ts'ą' geedan chan nankat gwats'an giinlii kwaa.  
\v 17 Niginjik łi'didlii zhit shroodiinyąą gavahtsii.  
\v 18 Nankat gwats'ą' shahooh'ya' gwik'it nankat gwats'ą' goohooł'e'.  
\v 19 Gooveenjit nantł'eedahaalchyaa, geedan chan łi'haa nantł'eedagahaachyaa ji' eenjit.” 
\s1 Jesus Gwik'injiighit Nąįį Tthak Eenjit Khadigiinjii 
\p  
\v 20 “Geedan zhrįh gooveenjit khadigihjii kwaa, gaa juu shik'injiheeghit nąįį chan shitsyaa nąįį shiginjik eegoogwaandak geh'an.  
\v 21 Datthak ch'ihłak giheelyaa eenjit gooveenjit khadigihjii. Shiti', shaa inlii gwik'it geedan chan diinaa gooli' ts'ą' shįį chan naa ihłii gwik'it. Ch'ihłak giheelyaa, juu nąįį datthak shahooh'e' gaageheendaii eenjit.  
\v 22 Nich'eegwahdrii shintł'eiin'ąįį ąįį goovantł'eiin'ąįį, ch'ihłak giheelyaa eenjit, nan shįį haa ch'ihłak tr'iinlii gwik'it.  
\v 23 Gavaa ihłii ts'ą' nan shaa inlii ts'ą' łyaa ch'ihłak giheelyaa eenjit, shahooh'e' ts'ą' sheet'iindhan gwik'it gaveet'iindhan gaageheendaii eenjit. 
\p  
\v 24 “Gwiti', shintł'eegaviinlii ts'ą' nijin t'ihchy'aa shaa t'agoochy'a' goovoihnyąą ts'ą' nich'eegwahdrii shintł'eiin'ąįį gahąąh'yaa geenjit. Nan gweheelyaa gwehkįį sheet'iinghya' geenjit.  
\v 25 Gwiti' Łi'didlii Choh! Nankat naagwiindaii kwaa, gaa shįį ąįį naashandaii, ts'ą' shahooh'e' chan gaagiindaii.  
\v 26 Juu inlii neegiihkhe' ts'ą' naagiindaii ts'ą' khit jyaa shi'yaa, ts'ą' ch'eet'igwiniindhan sheenjit ni'įį goozhit t'oonchy'aa ts'ą' shįį chan ch'eet'igwiniindhan shi'įį goozhit t'oochy'a'.” 
\c 18  
\s1 Niveet'ah'in Nąįį Jesus Giiyuunjik 
\r Matthew 26.47-56; Mark 14.43-50; Luke 22.47-53 
\p  
\v 1 Jyąhts'ą' khadigeedi' ąįįtł'ęę Jesus k'ǫǫ Kidron deetaa ditsyaa nąįį haa neiinzhii. Izhit gwanzhįh deek'it goo'aii, izhit Jesus ditsyaa nąįį haa gwiteiinzhii.  
\v 2 Judas, Jesus gwantł'ąhchįį ąįį gwanzhįh deek'it nijin goo'aii gaandaii ąįį gwehkįį zhat khit ditsyaa nąįį ninidik yaandaii.  
\v 3 Judas ąįį gwanzhįh deek'it gwats'ą' ąįį Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh gwak'ąąhtii nąįį akwat Roman niveet'ah'in lęįį nąįį haadlii, ąįįt'ee giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį chan ts'ą' Pharisee nąįį goohił'e': datthak kheeghan akwat chųų daak'a' tyah akwat gał vakat gwaak'a' neegahaazhik.  
\v 4 Jesus deereheelyaa datthak ch'adąį' hee gaandaii; ąįįts'ą' goots'ą' niinzhii ts'ą' jyaa gavahnyąą: “Juu vinkeegǫh'in t'akhwa'in?” 
\p  
\v 5 “Jesus Nazareth gwats'an,” giiyahnyąą. 
\p “Shįį t'ee t'ihchy'aa,” gavahnyąą. 
\p Judas, Jesus gwantł'ahchįį chan zhat nadhat.  
\v 6 Nijin Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą dąį', “Shįį t'ee t'ihchy'aa,” an gagahaajil ts'ą' nan kat oo'an gahaajil.  
\v 7 Jesus chan hee gavaahkat, “Juu vinkeegǫh'in t'akhwa'in?” 
\p “Jesus Nazareth gwats'an,” ginyąą. 
\p  
\v 8 “Shįį t'ee t'ihchy'aa, ch'adąį' nakhwaiinyą'. Shįį shinkeegoh'in t'akhwa'in ji', jii ch'izhii nąįį gavaanagoh'aa shrǫ'!” Jesus gavahnyąą.  
\v 9 (Deiinyą' chy'aa łi'didlii gweheelyaa ji' eenjit jyaa nyąą t'inyąą: “Ch'ihłak gaa haa tr'igweendaii kwaa, Shiti', juu shintł'eiinlii nąįį tee gwats'an”). 
\p  
\v 10 Peter ąįį kheeghan shrii choh di'įį, khąhnaii ts'ą' ndak khii giinkhih choh vi-slave Malchus oaazhii ąįį shriits'ąįį dzee' gadąąhtrit.  
\v 11 Jesus Peter jyaa ahnyąą, “Nizhrii choh gwizhit nąhchįį! Shiti' chųų tyah vizhit khaiinjich'iidhat shintł'eiin'ąįį zhit ch'ishinjyaa kwaa shǫįįnyąą?” 
\s1 Jesus, Annas ts'ą' Nigiiyąąhchįį 
\p  
\v 12 Niveet'ah'in ts'ą' dagakhaihkwai' chan ts'ą' gwak'ąąhtii nąįį haa Jesus goonjik ts'ą' giikat dich'iłchaa,  
\v 13 ąįįts'ą' Annas tr'ookit ts'ą' giihiłchįį. Caiaphas t'ee vichį' eedhidii ts'ą' zhat dąį' Caiaphas ndak khii giinkhih choh nilii.  
\v 14 Caiaphas t'ee dinjii ch'ihłak zhrįh dinjii tee gwats'an juu nąįį datthak niindhat eenjit ji' gweheezyaa Jews nąįį ąįįnyą'. 
\s1 Peter, Jesus Haandaii Kwaa Nyąą 
\r Matthew 26.69-70; Mark 14.66-68; Luke 22.55-57 
\p  
\v 15 Peter, ch'izhii ch'itsyaa haa Jesus tąįį gahaa'oo. Ąįį ch'izhii ch'itsyaa t'ee ndak khii giinkhih choh gwinzii yaandaii ąįįts'ą' Jesus zhit giinkhih choh vizheh gokwantee yaa gwats'ą' haazhii.  
\v 16 Peter ąįį oo'at chiitąįį ohts'ąįį dhidii. Ąįį ch'izhii ch'itsyaa gwinzii giinkhih choh yaandaii chineezhii ts'ą' oo'at chiitąįį nich'it tsal haa giinkhe' ąįįtł'ęę Peter nihdaahchįį.  
\v 17 Ąįį oo'at chiitąįį ohts'ąįį nich'it tsal ąįį Peter jyaa ahnyąą, “Zhit dinjii vitsyaa ch'ihłak inlii?” 
\p “Nakwaa, vitsyaa ihłii kwaa!” Peter yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 18 Chiitąįį gwiink'oo, ts'ą' ąįį ndak khii giinkhih choh vitsyaa chan ts'ą' geech'agwaa'ya' nąįį haa gwigwiilk'in ąįį eelin giheendhaa eenjit nigiilzhii. Peter chan heendhaa eenjit gootee nadhat. 
\s1 Ndak Khii Giinkhih Choh Jesus Oahkat 
\r Matthew 26.59-66; Mark 14.55-64; Luke 22.66-71 
\p  
\v 19 Ąįį ndak khii giinkhih choh ąįį Jesus, vitsyaa nąįį akwat geech'ǫąąhtan kwaii eenjit yuahkat. 
\p  
\v 20 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą: “Lęįį nąįį ts'ą' gwandah geech'ǫąąłchya', Israel nąįį tr'igiinkhii zheh kwaii akwat Kharigidiinjii Zheh Gwachoh gwizhrįh gwizhit geech'ǫąąłchya', izhit t'ee Jews nąįį khaihłan nineedal reh. Ch'ihłok gaa nagwąą'įį gwizhit giihkhe' kwaa.  
\v 21 Jaghaii geenjit shoohkat t'ohnyąą gǫ'? Ąįį juu gwaałchy'a' oohkat. Deegavaiinyą' ąįį geenjit gavoohkat, deihnyą' shaagiindaii.” 
\p  
\v 22 Nijin Jesus jyaa nyąą dąį', zhat gwak'ąąhtii ch'ihłak dhidii ąįį yaant'an ts'ą' jyaa yahnyąą. “Nats'ąą ndak khii giinkhih choh ts'ą' ginkhii t'iinyąą!” 
\p  
\v 23 Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Yee'at k'ii'an t'iinyą' ji', juk dząą gavaagwandak. Gaa deiinyą' eenjit oiints'it kwaa ji', jaghaii shįįt'an ni'in?” 
\p  
\v 24 Ts'ą' t'ee Annas, ąįį Jesus tth'aii vakat ch'adookhwachaa gwizhit ndak khii giinkhih choh Caiaphas ts'ą' niyąąhchįį. 
\s1 Peter, Chan Hee Jesus Haandaii Kwaa Nyąą 
\r Matthew 26.71-75; Mark 14.69-72; Luke 22.58-62 
\p  
\v 25 Gwiizhit Peter ąįį tth'aii hee gwaak'a' gwats'ą' heendhaa eenjit nadhat. Ąįįts'ą' zhat dilk'ii nąįį jyaa giiyahnyąą. “Nan lee zhit dinjii vitsyaa ch'ihłak lee t'iinchy'aa?” 
\p Gaa Peter ąįį zhyaa t'igwinyąą gavahnyąą ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Nakwaa, vitsyaa ihłii kwaa.” 
\p  
\v 26 Ąįį ndak khii giinkhih choh vi-slave ch'ihłak ąįį zhit juu Peter yidzee gihłeehiłtr'it valak yąąh'ya' ąįį Peter jyaa ahnyąą, “Nanlee gwanzhįh deek'it vaa naał'ya' lee t'iinchy'aa?” 
\p  
\v 27 Chan hee Peter “Nakwaa” nyąą gwiizhit rooster khashraa'iintrat. \fig Jii t'ee rooster|src="bk00062b.tif" size="col" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 18.27" \fig* 
\s1 Jesus, Pilate ts'ą' Nigiiyąąhchįį 
\r Matthew 27.1-2, 11-14; Mark 15.1-5; Luke 23.1-5 
\p  
\v 28 Jesus ąįį Caiaphas vizheh cheegiihiłchįį ts'ą' oo'at Roman khaihkwaii choh vizheh nihdeegiiyąąhchįį. Vanh dąį' gineech'ahoo'aii hee. Jews nąįį Passover ch'igihee'aa eenjit shroodigidiinyąą geh'an khaihkwaii choh vizheh nihdeegijyaa gitr'igii'ee, nihdeegiinjil ji' duuyeh Passover ch'a'aa.  
\v 29 Ąįįts'ą' ąįį Roman khaihkwaii choh (Pilate) yats'ą' ch'izhii ts'ą' yuahkat, “Jii dinjii jidii eenjit gwiizųų tr'agwah'ya'?” 
\p  
\v 30 Jyaa diginyąą, “Gwiizųų tr'agwah'ya' kwaa ji' duuyeh nats'ą' narąhchįį t'inchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 31 Pilate jyaa gavahnyąą, “Ts'an oo'įį ts'ą' nakhwa-law zhit deehohłyaa gwik'it t'ohłii.” 
\p Jews nąįį jyaa ginyąą “Dinjii drin gwarahahtsyaa geenjit goo'aii kwaa.”  
\v 32 (Jesus nats'ą' vidrin tr'ahahtsyaa diinyą' chy'aa ąįį gwik'it gweheelyaa eenjit t'igwiizhik) 
\p  
\v 33 Pilate dizheh nihdineezhii ts'ą' Jesus oahkat, “Nanlee Jews nąįį eenjit King inlii?” 
\p  
\v 34 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Nan shǫąąhkat akwat ch'izhii nąįį ts'an sheegwiintth'ak lee t'iinyąą?” 
\p  
\v 35 Pilate jyaa yahnyąą, “Jew ihłii shaiinyąą? Naa gwich'in nąįį akwat ąįį googiinkhii choh nąįį haa shintł'eenagąhchįį t'oonchy'aa. Nigwitr'it deezhik t'igwinyąą?” 
\p  
\v 36 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Shanahkat dząą nankat gwats'an nilii kwaa: shanahkat dząą nankat gwats'an nilii ji', shitsyaa nąįį Jews nąįį intł'eesharahahchyaa gwits'į' nich'itsigahahthat. Nakwaa, shanahkat dząą nahkat gwats'ą' nilii kwaa t'oonchy'aa!” 
\p  
\v 37 Ąįįts'ą' Pilate yuahkat, “King inlii diinyąą lee t'iinyąą?” 
\p Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Nan reh King inlii. Shaiinyąą. Ch'ihłak eenjit gwizhrįh shagoodlit ts'ą' nankat gwats'ą' hoiizhii t'ishi'in, łi'didlii eegihihkhyaa eenjit. Juu łi'didlii ts'an nilii ąįįt'ee shoołk'įį.” 
\p  
\v 38 “Ąįį łi'didlii ąįį jidii t'aiinyąą?” Pilate yuahkat. 
\s1 Jesus Tr'ahaahkhwaa Goodlit. 
\r Matthew 27.15-31; Mark 15.6-20; Luke 23.13-25 
\p Ąįįtł'ęę Pilate cheehoozhii ts'ą' Jews nąįį jyaa ahnyąą: “Jaghaii tr'ahaahkhwaa veegwaał'in kwaa.  
\v 39 Passover nineegwiidhak dąį' dinjii ch'ihłak zheegwaazhrąįį nakhweenjit chinałchik, ąįįt'ee khit jyąhts'ą' nakhweenjit gwik'it goo'aii geh'an. Jews nąįį nakhwa-King nakhweenjit chinoałchyaa shoohnyąą?” 
\p  
\v 40 Datthak gazhral ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą, “Nakwaa, adan nakwaa! Barabbas ąįį gwiindhan.” (Barabbas t'ee Roman nahkat gookat deeheehaa gwik'eegoonjik inli' t'arahnyąą.) 
\c 19  
\p  
\v 1 Ąįįtł'ęę Pilate ąįį Jesus oohjik ts'ą' tr'ąhtrii yeenjit gwiłtsąįį. \fig Gwanzhih khoh.|src="lb00121b.tif" size="col" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 19.1" \fig* 
\v 2 Niveet'ah'in nąįį khoh haa giiyeenjit ts'eh iłtsąįį ąįį giiniin'ąįį, ik Purple ąįį chan giinaahtsųų,  
\v 3 giits'ą' niinjil ts'ą' shroondaii jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Jews nąįį King niighyuk goondaii!” Ąįįts'ą' giits'ą' nineedal ts'ą' giiyant'an. 
\p  
\v 4 Pilate chan hee chineezhii ts'ą' dinjii nąįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Gooh'in, jaghaii tr'ahaahkhwaa veegwaał'in kwaa ąįį gahǫǫh'yaa eenjit nakhwats'ą' chahałchyaa.”  
\v 5 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Jesus chiinzhii, khoh ts'eh naa'aii ts'ą' ik Purple chan naazhii. Pilate dinjii nąįį jyaa ahnyąą, “Gooh'in, jii dinjii nǫh'in!” 
\p  
\v 6 Nijin zhit gwak'ąąhtii chan ts'ą' giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį nigiiyiił'in dąį' gazhral ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą, “Gohtsak! Gohtsak!” 
\p Gaa Pilate ąįį jyaa gavahnyąą. “Nakhwan ąįį ǫhjii ts'ą' gohtsak, shįį ąįį jaghaii geenjit tr'ahaahkhwaa veegwaał'in kwaa!” 
\p  
\v 7 Jews nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidinji' ihłii nyąą geh'an dii-law zhit tr'ahaahkhwaa goo'aii gwinyąą.” 
\p  
\v 8 Nijin Pilate jii gwiitth'ak dąį', gwandaa naajat dhidlit.  
\v 9 Dizheh gwachoh nihdineezhii ts'ą' Jesus jyaa ahnyąą, “Nijin gwats'an inkhaa?” 
\p Gaa Jesus yidii ginkhii kwaa.  
\v 10 Pilate jyaa yahnyąą, “Shats'ą' gihinkhyaa kwaa? Jii ganandaii, nineehįhdal ji' gaa geenjit t'aih shi'įį, ganarahahtsak ji' gaa geenjit t'aih shi'įį.” 
\p  
\v 11 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa t'aih nintł'eiin'ąįį haa sheenjit t'aih nilii t'oonchy'aa. Ąįįts'ą' zhit juu nintł'eeshąhchįį ąįį gwandaa vatr'agwaanduu gweheelyaa.” 
\p  
\v 12 Nijin Pilate jii gwiitth'ak dąį' vineeroonjii yuunyąą. Gaa Jews nąįį gazhral ts'ą' jyaa ginyąą, “Jii dinjii vineiinjik ji' t'ee, Rome nahkat gwats'ą' k'eegwaadhat Caesar duuyeh nijyaa nilii! Juu King ihłii nyąą t'ee Caesar vijyaa t'inchy'aa kwaa!” 
\p  
\v 13 Nijin Pilate jii gwiitth'ak dąį', Jesus chyąąhchįį ts'ą' oo'at ch'aroahkat deek'it naadii. (Jii t'ee Hebrew ginjik zhit “Gabbatha” t'arahnyąą.)  
\v 14 Izhit t'ee Passover gwats'ą' drintł'an khaiinjii nigwiindhat. Pilate ąįį Jews nąįį shroondaii jyaa ahnyąą, “Dząą nakhwa-King!” 
\p  
\v 15 Gazhral ts'ą' jyaa giiyahnyąą, “Vęhdaa tr'agǫh'ąįį! Vęhdaa tr'agǫh'ąįį! Cross kat gohtsak!” 
\p Pilate gavoahkat, “Nakhwaa-King gwałtsak shoohnyąą?” 
\p Giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį jyaa ginyąą, “Caesar zhrįh dii-King nilii t'oonchy'aa!” 
\p  
\v 16 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Pilate ąįį Jesus gagahahtsak eenjit gavantł'ahchįį. 
\s1 Jesus Gigiłtsak 
\r Matthew 27.32-44; Mark 15.21-32; Luke 23.26-43 
\p Ąįįts'ą' t'ee niveet'ah'in nąįį Jesus goonjik.  
\v 17 Da-cross ichyaa giiyiłtsąįį ts'ą' oodee taih “Dinjii kiitth'an k'itiltsį',” googwahnyąą gwats'ą' ahaa. (Hebrew ginjik zhit Golgotha goozhii)  
\v 18 Izhit t'ee cross kat gigiiyiłtsak veeghaih nihts'įį chan dinjii neekwaii gigiłtsak. \fig Jesus gigiyiłtsak.|src="lb00324b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 19.18" \fig* 
\v 19 Pilate dęhtły'aa kat gwadąąntł'oo ts'ą' ya-cross kat giłtsak “Jesus Nazareth gwats'an ahaa, Jews nąįį datthak eenjit King Nilii,” vakat gwinyąą. \fig none|src="lb00327b.tif" size="col" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 19.19" \fig* 
\v 20 Jews lęįį nąįį giikat aakin gwaa'įį, ąįį nijin Jesus giltsak ąįį kwaiik'it gwachoo gwats'ą' nahgǫǫ geh'an. Lęįį nąįį vakat deegwinyąą gaageheendaii eenjit Hebrew, Latin, chan ts'ą' Greek ginjik zhit danohootł'oo.  
\v 21 Giinkhih kįh dilk'ii nąįį Pilate jyaa agahnyąą, “‘Jews nąįį datthak eenjit King nilii.’ ąįį doiintł'oo shrǫ' gaa jii ąįį diintł'oo, ‘Jii dinjii jyaa nyąą, Jews nąįį datthak eenjit King ihłii.’” 
\p  
\v 22 Pilate jyaa gavahnyąą, “Jidii danoihtł'oo ąįį jyaa deheechy'aa t'oonchy'aa.” 
\p  
\v 23 Niveet'ah'in nąįį Jesus cross kat gigiłtsak ąįįtł'ęę giigwach'aa niveet'ah'in dǫǫ nąįį nihteegiyilzhii. Zhak khii ik chan oonjik, gwach'aa k'eelkai' nilii kwaa ts'ą' ch'ihłak zhrį' nilii.  
\v 24 Niveet'ah'in nąįį jyaa nihłagaanyąą, “Gwahkwaa łeerahch'aa; juu yuuheendal ji' eenjit, veenjit tseeroo'ya'.” Dęhtły'aa Choh kat deegwinyąą ąįį łi'didlii heelyaa eenjit jyąhts'ą' teegoodhat t'igwinyąą: 
\q1 “Shagwach'aa nihteegilzhii, shi'ik eenjit tseegee'ya'.” 
\p Niveet'ah'in nąįį izhit gwik'it t'igiizhik t'agwarahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 25 Va-cross gwats'ą' niighit kwaa vahan nadhat, vahan vijuu, Clopas va'at Mary chan, Mary Magdalene chan.  
\v 26 Jesus dahan chan ts'ą' ditsyaa eet'iindhan ąįį zhat nigiilzhii nagooviił'in; ąįįts'ą' dahan łyaa jyaa ahnyąą, “Ni'ęę, dząą t'ee nigii.” 
\p  
\v 27 Ąįįtł'ęę ditsyaa jyaa ahnyąą, “Dząą nahan.” Izhit gwats'an ąįį vitsyaa dizheh yaagweheechy'aa eenjit gwits'eeyihiłchįį. 
\s1 Jesus Niindhat 
\r Matthew 27.45-56; Mark 15.33-41; Luke 23.44-49 
\p  
\v 28 Jesus et'ee jidii datthak gwik'it t'igwiizhik gaandaii ąįįts'ą' Dęhtły'aa Choh kat deegwinyąą ąįį łi'didlii eenjit jyaa nyąą, “Chųų doiihłii.” 
\p  
\v 29 Hyssop gał ts'iivii k'it t'inchy'aa tsii gwach'aa nagahtsuu ąįį k'ik tyah ghoo zhit jak chų' daatł'oo kwaa dhakaii; ąįį giizhit teegąhtsuu ts'ą' oodak giits'ą' ootą'.  
\v 30 Jesus juk chų' eenį' ąįįtł'ęę jyaa nyąą, “It'ee ndaagwąą'ąį'!” 
\p Ąįįtł'ęę zhak diki' niin'ąįį ts'ą' niindhat. 
\p  
\v 31 Ąįįtł'ęę Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį ąįį dinjii juu gagooriłtsak nąįį gootth'an łeegahahnaii ąįįtł'ęę cross ts'an nineegeheelyaa eenjit Pilate goahkat. Neegwaazhii Drin łyaa shroodiinyąą ts'ą' gwigwihił'ee drin nigwiighit geh'an zhat drin cross kat goochį' dhidlii gitr'igii'ee. Drin ts'ą' gwats'ą' drin gweedhaa geh'an jyaa digiizhik.  
\v 32 Niveet'ah'in nąįį ąįį dinjii neekwaii Jesus haa gagoogiłtsak nąįį tth'an łeegiiłnaii.  
\v 33 Gaa nijin Jesus inigwigwiin'ąįį dąį', ch'adąį' hee niindhat łee ts'ą' giitth'an łeelnaii kwaa.  
\v 34 Niveet'ah'in ch'ihłak googaa kheeghan ch'ok haa Jesus tseech'iingit, Googwahkhan chųų, dah haa khaatil.  
\v 35 (Shįį t'ee jyaa digwiizhik gwąął'ya' ts'ą' geegihkhe' łi'didlii t'ihnyąą gaashandaii ąįįts'ą' nan chan gwik'iinjihinghit ji' geenjit.)  
\v 36 Dęhtły'aa Choh kat jyaa digwinyąą. Ąįį łi'didlii heelyaa eenjit, “Vatth'an ch'ihłak gaa łeehaahnaii kwaa.”  
\v 37 Dęhtły'aa Choh kat ch'adanh chan jyaa digwinyąą, “Dinjii giiyaahgwat aakin giiyaa'įį!” 
\s1 Jesus Vanarąhjii 
\r Matthew 27.57-61; Mark 15.42-47; Luke 23.50-56 
\p  
\v 38 Jii ąįįtł'ęę Arimathea kwaiik'it gwachoo gwats'an dinjii Joseph oaazhii ąįį Jesus vichį' ooheendal ji' eenjit Pilate oahkat. (Joseph ąįį Jesus vitsyaa nilii gaa nagwąąh'įį, Jews khaihkwaii nąįį aanjat geh'an.) Pilate ąįį gwik'it t'ini'in yahnyąą ts'ą' t'ee yichi' oonjik ts'ą' oo'an neeyihiłchįį.  
\v 39 Nicodemus tr'ookit dąį' khaa Jesus nah'ya' chy'aa ąįį Joseph haa haazhii, myrrh, ts'ą' aloes chan gwanzhįh chų' gwinzii vagwaatsan 100 lb. adahaa haadlii.  
\v 40 Ąįį dinjii neekwaii nąįį Jesus vichį' neegąhchįį ts'ą' gwach'aa ts'ik jyah giinooandoo, ąįį gwanzhįh gwinzii vagwaatsan haa. Jyąhts'ą' t'ee Jews nąįį dinjii anagahąhdal dąį' t'igii'in.  
\v 41 Ąįį nijin Jesus goołkhwąįį geeghaih nahgwan gwanzhįh deek'it goo'aii izhit gwizhit gwa'an kii zhit gweedii goo'aii gwehkįį dinjii gitsii kwaa.  
\v 42 Et'ee Jews nąįį Neegwaazhii Drin gwats'ą' drin nigwiindhat ąįįts'ą' ąįį kii zhit gweedii goo'aii ąįį geeghaih niighit kwaa goo'aii. Geh'an zhat Jesus vichį' nagąąhchįį. 
\c 20  
\s1 Jesus Vatth'ank'it Zhit Gwihiljii 
\r Matthew 28.1-8; Mark 16.1-8; Luke 24.1-12 
\p  
\v 1 Drin Zhit vanh dąį' tth'aii tǫǫ gwanlii gwiizhit Mary Magdalene ąįį kii zhit gweedii gwats'ą' haazhii akhai' gwadąįį kii gihłeerahaa'aii łee gwah'in.  
\v 2 Gihłeehilgik ts'ą' Simon Peter chan ts'ą' ch'izhii vitsyaa Jesus gooveet'iinghya' nąįį ts'ą' niinzhii ts'ą' jyaa gavahnyąą, “Kiizhit gwats'an K'eegwaadhat goonjik ts'ą' nijin nigiiyąąhchįį kwaa gaagwiindaii kwaa!” 
\p  
\v 3 Ąįįtł'ęę Peter chan ts'ą' ch'izhii Jesus vitsyaa haa ąįį kiizhit vatth'ank'it gwats'ą' gahaajil.  
\v 4 Nihłaagaagal, gaa ch'ihłak ąįį Peter iłeehilgik ts'ą' adan tr'ookit tth'ank'it k'aagak.  
\v 5 Nihdeekiintthaii ts'ą' gwach'aa ts'ik njyah kwaii nah'in, gaa nihdeiinzhii kwaa.  
\v 6 Vatąįį Simon Peter k'idik ts'ą' zhazhat kiizhit tth'ank'it nihdeiinzhii. Ąįį gwach'aa ts'ik jyah, \fig Jesus vatth'ank'it.|src="lb00329b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 20.6" \fig* 
\v 7 ąįįts'ą' Jesus viki' kat gwach'aa kwaii niił'in. Ch'izhii gwach'aa ts'ik jyah eeghaii dhidlii kwaa gaa thok tr'aandoo łee.  
\v 8 Ąįį ch'izhii ch'itsyaa ąįį kiizhit tth'ank'it tr'ookit k'idik chy'aa, adan chan nihdeiinzhii; gwąąh'ya' ąįįtł'ęę gwik'it t'igwiizhik ts'ą' gaandaii.  
\v 9 (Dęhtły'aa Choh kat niindhat ąįįtł'ęę nineeheenjyaa goo'aii varahnyąą ąįį deegwinyąą t'igwinyąą gaagiindaii kwaa.) 
\s1 Jesus, Mary Yats'ą' Igwiilkįį 
\r Matthew 28.9-10; Mark 16.9-11 
\p  
\v 10 Ąįįtł'ęę vitsyaa nąįį digizheh gwits'eegahoojil.  
\v 11 Ąįį kii tth'ank'it gokwantee Mary itree ts'ą' nadhat. Tth'aii itree gwiizhit nihdeekiintthaii ts'ą' oozhak gwąąh'in,  
\v 12 ts'ą' zheekat gwich'in neekwaii nah'in, daagąįį nagaatsuu ts'ą' Jesus nijuk iindi' izhit dagaadii, viki' eeghaii ch'ihłak dhidii, vakwai' ts'ąįį chan ch'ihłak dhidii. 
\p  
\v 13 “Tr'injaa, jaghaii iintree?” giiyahnyąą. 
\p Jyaa gavahnyąą, “Shik'eegwaadhat gihłeegihiłchįį ts'ą' nijuk nigiiyąąhchįį gaashandaii kwaa!” 
\p  
\v 14 Nijin jyaa nyąą dąį', neediil'ee akhai' Jesus zhat nadhat nigwiił'in; gaa Jesus t'inchy'aa ts'ą' yaandaii kwaa.  
\v 15 “Tr'injaa, jaghaii intree? Juu vinkeegwąh'in t'ini'in?” Jesus yuahkat. 
\p Gwanzhįh eetr'agwah'in t'inchy'aa yuunyąą, ts'ą' Mary jyaa yahnyąą, “Oodhiinjik t'inchy'aa ji' nijuk nąąhchįį shaagwandak, vats'ą' hihshyaa ts'ą' noohihdal eenjit.” 
\p  
\v 16 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Mary!” 
\p Yats'ą' neediil'ee ts'ą' Hebrew ginjik zhit jyaa nyąą, “Rabboni!” (Jii t'ee “Geech'ǫąąhtan” ginyąą t'igwinyąą.) 
\p  
\v 17 “Shakat noonjii shrǫ',” Jesus yahnyąą, “Tth'aii Shiti' vits'eehihdii kwaa geh'an. Gaa shachaa nąįį goots'eehindii' ts'ą' jii sheenjit gavaa gwandak, ‘Oodak Shiti' vats'ą' hihshyaa, nakhwan chan Nakhwati' Shivit'eegwijyąhchy'aa nilii, nakhwan chan nakhwa-Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa nilii.’” 
\p  
\v 18 Ąįįts'ą' t'ee Mary Magdalene yitsyaa nąįį ts'ą' K'eegwaadhat nah'ya' ts'ą' jii jyaa diiyaiinyą' eenjit geevaagwaandak. 
\s1 Jesus, Vitsyaa Nąįį Giits'ą' Gwigwiilkįį 
\r Matthew 28.16-20; Mark 16.14-18; Luke 24.36-49 
\p  
\v 19 Drinzhit khaiinjii tǫhtł'an gwa'an zheh gwizhit vitsyaa nąįį gindeiinvyaa gehdeech'igiintin, Jews kįh dilk'ii nąįį agąąnjat geh'an. Ąįįtł'ęę Jesus gootł'an nadhat nagwaanąįį. “Tsinehdan nakhwaa oolį', Shiti' shihił'ee gwik'it shįį chan nakhwahał'ee,” Jesus gavahnyąą.  
\v 20 Jii jyaa diinyą' ąįįtł'ęę, danli', ditsęh k'ąą haa goots'ą' agwahch'in. K'eegwaadhat gąąh'in eenjit gwintł'oo shoo giinlii.  
\v 21 Ąįįtł'ęę chan hee Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Tsinehdan nakhwaa oolį', Shiti' shihił'e' gwik'it shįį chan nakhwayinjihooł'ee!”  
\v 22 Jii jyaa diinyą', ąįįtł'ęę datthak gookat haazhee ts'ą' jyaa gavahnyąą, “Ch'anky'aa Shroodiinyąą ts'an oo'įį.  
\v 23 Dinjii nąįį atr'agwaanduu gooveenjit oo'an gahohłii ji', gooveenjit oo'an gweheedaa; gooveenjit oo'an gahohłii kwaa ji', duuyeh gooveenjit oo'an gwihijyaa.” 
\s1 Jesus, Thomas Haa 
\p  
\v 24 Jesus goots'ą' nadhat naanaii dąį' vitsyaa ch'ihłak Thomas (Didymus chan oozhii) ąįį zhat dhidii kwaa.  
\v 25 Ąįįts'ą' vitsyaa nąįį Thomas jyaa agahnyąą, “K'eegwaadhat tr'ąąh'ya'!” 
\p Thomas jyaa nyąą, “Vanli' kat gwatsak deek'it shat dha'aii akwat gwatsak deek'it naaljik akwat vitsęh k'ąą naaljik kwaa ji' duuyeh adan t'inchy'aa gwik'iinjihkhit.” 
\p  
\v 26 Ąįįtł'ęę gęhdaa drin deetik vitsyaa nąįį zheh gwizhit khaihłan nineegiijil ts'ą' Thomas zhat goovaadhidii gindeiinvyaa ihdeech'agąąhtin gaa Jesus zhat gaveeghaii nadhat naanaii ts'ą' jyaa gavahnyąą, “Tsinehdan nakhwaa oolį'!”  
\v 27 Ąįįtł'ęę Thomas jyaa ahnyąą, “Dząą nanleetth'ak niinchįį, ts'ą' shanli' nah'in; ąįįtł'ęę nanli' nihky'aa noiinjii ts'ą' dząą shitsęhk'aa naanjii. Gwik'iinjiighit ni'įį kwaa ąįį akhagoiinyąą ts'ą' gwik'iinjinghit!” 
\p  
\v 28 Thomas jyaa yahnyąą, “Shik'eegwaadhat, Shivit'eegwijyąhchy'aa!” 
\p  
\v 29 Jesus jyaa yahnyąą, “Shąąh'ya' geh'an gwizhrįh shik'iinjinghit? Juu shąąh'in kwaa gaa shik'iinjiighit nąįį shoo nakhwaa oolį'!” 
\s1 Jii Dęhtły'aa Jaghaii Danahootł'oo 
\p  
\v 30 Jesus ditsyaa nąįį andah gwinlęįį gwitr'it geegwaroolii kwaa t'iizhik gaa jii dęhtły'aa zhit valak zhrįh danahootł'oo.  
\v 31 Jii t'ee gwadanakhwatł'oo Jesus t'ee Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa Vidinji' nilii ts'ą' Christ chan nilii, gwik'iinjihinghit ji' ąįį nigwik'iinjigwiighit haa voozhri' zhit gwihiindaii geenjit. 
\c 21  
\s1 Jesus, Vitsyaa 7 Nąįį Ts'ą' Gwigwiilkįį 
\p  
\v 1 Jii ąįįtł'ęę, Jesus ch'ihłok gwizhrįh van Tiberias khyųų ditsyaa nąįį ts'ą' idineegwiilkįį. Jyąhts'ą' t'igwiizhik t'agwarahnyąą.  
\v 2 Simon Peter, Thomas, Nathaniel (Galilee nahkat gwizhit Cana goozhii goo'aii gwats'an ahaa), Zebedee vidinjii neekwaii ts'ą' Jesus ch'izhii vitsyaa neekwaii nąįį haa nihłaagiilk'ii.  
\v 3 Simon Peter jyaa gavahnyąą, “Łuk keeshi'yaa.” 
\p “Naa k'eereheedal,” giiyahnyąą. Ąįįts'ą' t'ee giiyaahaajil ts'ą' tr'ihchoo zhit giinjil; gaa zhat tǫǫ datthak łuk ch'ihłak gaa goonjik kwaa.  
\v 4 Vanh geeneech'ihii'aii gwiizhit Jesus van khyųų nadhat, gaa vitsyaa nąįį Jesus t'inchy'aa giiyaandaii kwaa.  
\v 5 Ąįįtł'ęę jyaa gavahshral ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Tsyaa nąįį, nik'ee łuk oodhoonjik?” 
\p “Ch'ihłak gaa kwaa,” giiyahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 6 Jesus jyaa gavahshral ts'ą' jyaa nyąą, “Nakhwachihvyaa tr'ihchoo eeghaii shriits'ąįį chųhtsuu, izhit łuk oohohdal t'oonchy'aa.” Ąįįts'ą' t'ee izhit chigiiyąąhtsuu akhai' khyų' khaneegiiyahtsuu, łyaa vizhit łuk lęįį geh'an. 
\p  
\v 7 Zhit vitsyaa Jesus yeet'iindhan ąįį Peter t'ahnyąą, “Diik'eegwaadhat t'inchy'aa łee!” Nijin Simon Peter Diik'eegwaadhat t'inchy'aa gwinyąą gwiitth'ak dąį', ankhii dagwach'aa nanaatsuu gwats'ą' dąį' (gihłeeyihiltsuu dhidii) ts'ą' chųų zhit oondaa hiltłee.  
\v 8 Teeghaii gwats'ą' niighit kwaa neegeekwaii. Ch'izhii vitsyaa nąįį tr'ihchoo haa teeneegohojil (Chihvyaa vizhit łuk deedąą'ąį' haa).  
\v 9 Teeneegohojil dąį' zhat gwaak'a' kǫ' zhit łuk chan ts'ą' łųhchy'aa haa ichy'aa googwąąh'in.  
\v 10 Jesus t'agavahnyąą, “Ąįį łuk dohju' gwidiinlii lat dząą nohtsit.” \fig none|src="lb00330b.tif" size="span" copy="©The British & Foreign Bible Society" ref="JHN 21.10" \fig* 
\p  
\v 11 Simon Peter ąįį tr'ihchoo zhineezhii ts'ą' chihvyaa vizhit łuk choh deedąą'ąį' ąįį teedhiluu, (153 aanchy'aa) łyaa vizhit łuk lęįį gaa chihvyaa łeedhach'aa kwaa.  
\v 12 Jesus jyaa gavahnyąą, “Aanaii ts'ą' dząą ch'oh'aa.” 
\p “Juu inlii?” giiyahaanjyaa eenjit giideetr'oaanyąą. Gook'eegwaadhat t'inchy'aa giiyaandaii geh'an.  
\v 13 Ąįįts'ą' Jesus gaveeniinzhii ts'ą' łųhchy'aa oonjik ts'ą' gavantł'eech'ąhtsit, łuk chan gwik'it t'inlik. 
\p  
\v 14 Jesus niindhat ts'ą' ninehjin ąįįtł'ęę jii zhat dąį' t'ee ditsyaa nąįį ts'ą' tik agwaanchy'aa idigweelkįį t'agwarahnyąą. 
\s1 Jesus, Peter Shitsyaa Nąįį Gwahtan Ahnyąą 
\p  
\v 15 Ch'igiin'al ąįįtł'ęę, Jesus ąįį Simon Peter jyaa yahnyąą “John vidinji', Simon, jii nąįį andaa ts'ą' łyaa sheet'iindhan?” 
\p “Shik'eegwaadhat, aahą' neet'iihthan ts'ą' gaanandaii.” Peter yahnyąą. 
\p Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Shidivii tsal nąįį gooch'ah'aa.” 
\p  
\v 16 Chan hee Jesus ąįį Peter jyaa yahnyąą, “John vidinji', Simon, łyaa sheet'iindhan?” 
\p “Shik'eegwaadhat, aahą' neet'iihthan ts'ą' gaanandaii.” Peter yahnyąą. 
\p Jesus t'iiyahnyąą, “Shidivii nąįį k'ąąhtii.” 
\p  
\v 17 Tik agwaanchy'aa chan Jesus ąįį jyaa yahnyąą, “John vidinji', Simon, sheet'iindhan?” Peter tr'igwidii dhidlit Jesus tik agwaanchy'aa “Sheet'iindhan?” yahnyąą eenjit. 
\p “Shik'eegwaadhat, łyaa jidii datthak eenjit gaanandaii; neet'iihthan gaanandaii t'oonchy'aa.” Peter yahnyąą. 
\p Jesus jyaa yahnyąą “Shidivii nąįį gooch'ah'aa.  
\v 18 Łi'didlii haa nakhwaagwahaldak, k'eejit inlii dąį' neenitł'uu ts'ą' deenoo'ya' yiindhan datthak gwik'it t'ini'in, nijin gwats'ą' hoihshi' niindhan chan gwik'it t'ini'in; gaa naghaii lęįį ji' neenigiheetł'uu ts'ą' nijin gwats'ą' hoihshi' niindhan kwaa gaa nihk'it gwats'ą' nigehęę'aa t'oonchy'aa.”  
\v 19 (Jii Jesus jyaa nyąą t'ee nats'ąą Peter niheedhaa ts'ą' Vit'eegwijyąhchy'aa vich'eegwahdrii gwahąąh'yaa t'agwarahnyąą.) 
\p Ąįįts'ą' chan yahnyąą, “Shatąįį inkhaii!” 
\s1 Jesus, Ch'izhii Vitsyaa Haa 
\p  
\v 20 Peter neediil'ee akhai' ąįį juu Jesus ditsyaa nąįį tee ch'andaa yeet'iindhan niił'in, nijin neech'aga'aa dąį' Jesus eeghaii niighit kwaa dhidii chy'aa ąįį niił'in ts'ą' Jesus oahkat. “Diik'eegwaadhat, juu diitee gwintł'ee nahahchyaa t'oonchy'aa?”  
\v 21 Nijin Peter ąįį dinjii niił'in dąį', Jesus oahkat, “Shik'eegwaadhat, jii dinjii aiiyu'?” 
\p  
\v 22 “K'ineehihdik gwats'ą' goondaii oihnyąą ji', jaghaii geenjit tr'igwiindii? Aanaii, shatąįį hinkhaii!” Jesus yahnyąą. 
\p  
\v 23 Vitsyaa nąįį ąįį gootee dinjii ch'ihłak niheedhaa kwaa łee ginyąą ts'ą' geenihłagogwaandak. Gaa Jesus ąįį dinjii niheedhaa kwaa nyąą t'inyąą kwaa jii ąįį jyaa nyąą t'inyąą; “K'ineehihdik gwats'ą' gwandaii oihnyąą ji', jaghaii geenjit tr'igwiindii?” 
\p  
\v 24 Jii deegwee'ya' gwinyąą t'ee John gwąąh'ya' ts'ą' gwadąąntł'oo; ąįįts'ą' deiinyą' datthak łi'didlii nilii ts'ą' geenjit gaagwiindaii. 
\s1 John Vidęhtły'aa Ndaanąą'ąį' 
\p  
\v 25 Jesus łyaa ants'ą' gwinlęįį vagwandak gwanlii ts'ą' gaa datthak vik'iteech'adarantl'oo ji', tr'ihkhit dęhtły'aa lęįį heelyaa ts'ą' jii nankat duuyeh yuutą'!